(1, '2025-04-19', 'GT Micro Racers', 'GT Micro Racers takes high-speed racing to a whole new scale! Control tiny but powerful GT-style cars as they speed through thrilling outdoor tracks made from everyday household objects. Race across books, cans, and wooden ramps in a sunlit backyard filled with grass, flowers, and playful obstacles. Drift through sharp turns, hit insane jumps, and outmaneuver rivals to claim victory', 'arrow keys to move', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cd033e8cf295468caa8891286b2635cb-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cd033e8cf295468caa8891286b2635cb-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cd033e8cf295468caa8891286b2635cb/', '800', '600', 'car,cartoon,dash,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'gt-micro-racers', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cd033e8cf295468caa8891286b2635cb-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cd033e8cf295468caa8891286b2635cb-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(2, '2025-04-19', 'Sprunki Lava Escape 2Player', 'Together with your friend, you must save the Sprunki characters from the rising lava. You must be very careful. The lava is rising, and you\'re in danger. Escape the lava with 6 different characters and jump as high as you can. An endless jumping and lava escape awaits you. Collect all the music notes along the way. You need the music notes.', 'Use the WASD keys to move and jump in the game.\nUse the Arrow Keys keys to move and jump in the game.\n*Mobile Control Available ', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e31d4ef8a77948959a074e286ec10133-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e31d4ef8a77948959a074e286ec10133-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e31d4ef8a77948959a074e286ec10133/', '800', '600', '1player,2d,pixel,2players,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'sprunki-lava-escape-2player', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e31d4ef8a77948959a074e286ec10133-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e31d4ef8a77948959a074e286ec10133-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(3, '2025-04-19', 'Bull Runner', 'Take control of a powerful bull as it charges forward at full speed! Smash through obstacles, knock over stickmen, and leave destruction in your wake. How far can you go before something stops you? Test your reflexes and unleash the unstoppable force of the raging bull!', 'Move Left/Right  Swipe on your phone screen or move your mouse to steer the bull.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ea59cf1812764e2bab4c628bdc093b8f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ea59cf1812764e2bab4c628bdc093b8f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ea59cf1812764e2bab4c628bdc093b8f/', '960', '600', '1player,ragdoll,runner,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bull-runner', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ea59cf1812764e2bab4c628bdc093b8f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ea59cf1812764e2bab4c628bdc093b8f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(4, '2025-04-19', 'Cross Connect Word', 'Fun and relaxing crossword puzzle!\n\nCross Word Connect is a fun but challenging word game.\nEnjoy modern word game with the combine of word search and crossword! In this fantastic crossword puzzle, you will improve your vocabulary and spelling skills.', 'Use mouse/ touch &amp; drag to connect Alphabet Letters to make correct word!', 'Puzzle,Educational', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c1c06a567d3348129ee4be8bb4cf4beb-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c1c06a567d3348129ee4be8bb4cf4beb-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c1c06a567d3348129ee4be8bb4cf4beb/', '800', '600', 'wordsearch,crossword,alphabet,wordscapes,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cross-connect-word', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c1c06a567d3348129ee4be8bb4cf4beb-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c1c06a567d3348129ee4be8bb4cf4beb-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(5, '2025-04-19', 'Darts Master:Cartoon 3D', 'Dear dart experts and those who want to become dart experts. Please showcase your talents to the fullest on this thrilling dart journey. Collect and enrich your dart warehouse with the goal of overcoming all challenges. Experience the joy of different dart competitions.', 'Winning by throwing darts.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/56e831b341064111bba5f281952a03ca-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/56e831b341064111bba5f281952a03ca-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/56e831b341064111bba5f281952a03ca/', '800', '600', 'aim,dart,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'darts-master-cartoon-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/56e831b341064111bba5f281952a03ca-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/56e831b341064111bba5f281952a03ca-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(6, '2025-04-19', 'sprunki character maker OC', 'The Sprunki Character Maker OC is an interactive tool that allows users to create their own unique characters within the Sprunki universe. Featuring a wide range of customization options, assets, and design tools, it empowers players to craft characters that match the games distinctive art style and themes. This experience encourages creativity, self-expression, and deeper engagement with the Sprunki community', ' Click Customization  Easily place and modify features with an intuitive interface.', 'Adventure,Art', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a78fb8feefd848489aa683bd6253ec5b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a78fb8feefd848489aa683bd6253ec5b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a78fb8feefd848489aa683bd6253ec5b/', '800', '600', 'avatar,creative,maker,makeup,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'sprunki-character-maker-oc', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a78fb8feefd848489aa683bd6253ec5b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a78fb8feefd848489aa683bd6253ec5b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(7, '2025-04-19', 'Grass Ranch', 'Grass Ranch is a super fun and relaxing casual game that makes you a true ranch grass-mowing master. If you like to complete simple and fun tasks in a cozy environment, then you can\'t miss this game. In this world of green grass, you will mow grass constantly. Keep mowing the lawn and feed some cute animals.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8bd204b4425b41bb80c1f68ea089e2b7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8bd204b4425b41bb80c1f68ea089e2b7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8bd204b4425b41bb80c1f68ea089e2b7/', '1334', '750', 'animal,cute,relax,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'grass-ranch', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8bd204b4425b41bb80c1f68ea089e2b7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8bd204b4425b41bb80c1f68ea089e2b7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(8, '2025-04-19', 'Mathematics Racing', 'Welcome to Mathematics Racing, the thrilling game where your math skills determine your speed on the track! Dive into a world where solving math problems propels you to victory. Here\'s what you need to know.', 'Solve examples to accelerate, try not to make mistakes, otherwise your car will slow down. Solve 5 examples in a row without mistakes to activate turbo acceleration.\n\nWith the money you win, you can buy new cars. Each car has its own acceleration and top speed characteristics. With new levels, more cars will be available to you.\n\nThe difficulty of the examples is adjusted automatically, depending on the proportion of correct answers.', 'Racing & Driving,Educational', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/090fbd107a024f28880ff1185bdbaba1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/090fbd107a024f28880ff1185bdbaba1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/090fbd107a024f28880ff1185bdbaba1/', '800', '600', 'car,chase,score,vehicle,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mathematics-racing', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/090fbd107a024f28880ff1185bdbaba1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/090fbd107a024f28880ff1185bdbaba1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(9, '2025-04-19', 'Beam Drive Car Crash Test Simulator', 'Experience thrilling car crashes with realistic physics and intense destruction! Smash, wreck, and demolish vehicles in crash tests, demolition derbies, and sandbox modes. Dive into authentic impact mechanics and explore the ultimate crash simulator for car destruction fans!', 'Driving/Walking/Flying - WASD\nRight mouse button - Rotate camera\nSpace - Handbrake\nC - Change camera\nB - Look back\nH - Horn\nJ - Hazard lights\nZ - Left turn signal\nX - Right turn signal\n\nFor mobile devices, use the in-game interface.', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0f73244bf0cd494ba3f42aee62061f83-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0f73244bf0cd494ba3f42aee62061f83-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0f73244bf0cd494ba3f42aee62061f83/', '800', '600', 'car,stunts,survival,track,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'beam-drive-car-crash-test-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0f73244bf0cd494ba3f42aee62061f83-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0f73244bf0cd494ba3f42aee62061f83-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(10, '2025-04-19', 'Steampunk Merge To Battle', 'Merge to Battle is a strategy game where the goal is to capture all the castles in your way. Unite your warriors and archers on the battlefield and fight against enemies. Build and upgrade your castle and troops. Explore the entire evolution of warriors by combining two units into an even stronger one. React quickly and use strategy and tactics to win the battle and advance to the next level.', 'Buy and merge units to conquer new castles!', 'Strategy,Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/00a625d4f067412b8c32fc0bf967c941-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/00a625d4f067412b8c32fc0bf967c941-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/00a625d4f067412b8c32fc0bf967c941/', '600', '900', 'castle,defence,real-time-strategy,arcade,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'steampunk-merge-to-battle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/00a625d4f067412b8c32fc0bf967c941-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/00a625d4f067412b8c32fc0bf967c941-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(11, '2025-04-19', 'Bubble Escape', 'Navigate the bubbles to the exit without getting popped by the spikes. More the bubbles escape, more the scores you get. Play through 30 levels. Be careful with the bubble jiggles.', 'Use WASD from keyboard or on screen joystick to move bubbles around.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d105757b4c3e4b34bc9825042165d907-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d105757b4c3e4b34bc9825042165d907-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d105757b4c3e4b34bc9825042165d907/', '800', '600', 'bubble,cartoon,control,physics,indie,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bubble-escape', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d105757b4c3e4b34bc9825042165d907-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d105757b4c3e4b34bc9825042165d907-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(12, '2025-04-19', 'Save Seafood', 'Save Seafood is an exciting puzzle game where you help sea animals escape from being trapped in a tangled mess! The goal is to move and rearrange the animals to free them from the crowd. Solve each puzzle by carefully maneuvering the creatures until theyre all safely separated. Can you untangle the sea and set the animals free?', 'Use left mouse to click', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0791197bc7004786add22512f5b32a56-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0791197bc7004786add22512f5b32a56-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0791197bc7004786add22512f5b32a56/', '720', '1280', '1player,2d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'save-seafood', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0791197bc7004786add22512f5b32a56-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0791197bc7004786add22512f5b32a56-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(13, '2025-04-19', 'Soo Match: Room Design', 'Soo Match! is a fun and engaging blast game. Players progress by tapping and matching blocks of the same color to complete levels. At the end of each level, tickets can be used to complete rooms and unlock new stages, while in-game coins can be spent to acquire new characters. With its charming graphics and diverse game modes, Soo Match! offers a dynamic and enjoyable gaming experience.', 'Click on matching blocks of the same color to clear them.\nCreate special matches to earn Bombs, Rockets, and Lightning power-ups.\nComplete the specified objectives to finish the level.\nEarn in-game coins to unlock characters and purchase puzzle pieces.\nOpen chests, complete tasks, and claim daily rewards for extra boosts.', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4fe7ce0674e049faa9a75878ddb76883-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4fe7ce0674e049faa9a75878ddb76883-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4fe7ce0674e049faa9a75878ddb76883/', '1128', '615', 'candy,decor,matching,colormatch,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'soo-match-room-design', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4fe7ce0674e049faa9a75878ddb76883-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4fe7ce0674e049faa9a75878ddb76883-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(14, '2025-04-19', 'Garden Guardians', 'Garden Guardians is a casual mobile game that merges strategic tower defense with physics-based ballistics. Players take on the role of a countryside guardian, dragging and combining fruits with unique properties to build cannons, which they upgrade to fend off relentless dragon invasions.\nWill you let the farmland fall, or will you erect an unbreakable defense with fruit-powered artillery? The joy of the harvest hinges on your firepower!', 'Follow the tutorial prompts: Click the mouse to collect fruits, then drag and combine them to create cannons. Place the cannons on the turrets to initiate combat.', 'Battle,Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9dc10bd82d1b4819859247602b19b802-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9dc10bd82d1b4819859247602b19b802-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9dc10bd82d1b4819859247602b19b802/', '1600', '850', 'archery,dragon,war,battleroyale,battlefield,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'garden-guardians', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9dc10bd82d1b4819859247602b19b802-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9dc10bd82d1b4819859247602b19b802-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(15, '2025-04-19', 'Color Block Jam', 'Color Block Jam  A Satisfying Block Puzzle Challenge! ?\n\nGet ready for a fun and brain-teasing puzzle experience! Move the colorful blocks around the board and match them correctly to clear the space. Think ahead, plan your moves, and solve tricky levels! Can you master the ultimate color sorting challenge?', 'Drag &amp; drop blocks to rearrange them ', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bea1d886820c494091bf1df4e77b956a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bea1d886820c494091bf1df4e77b956a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bea1d886820c494091bf1df4e77b956a/', '800', '600', '1player,block,color,summer,timekiller,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'color-block-jam', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bea1d886820c494091bf1df4e77b956a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bea1d886820c494091bf1df4e77b956a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(16, '2025-04-19', 'Grab Piglet', 'Grab Piglet is a delightful and engaging match-3 game centered around catching adorable cartoon piglets. In each level, a variety of toysincluding colorful balls, blocks, and the star of the show, cartoon pigletswill tumble down from the top of the screen. Your goal is to place three identical toys into a special box. Once you do, those three toys vanish in a puff of playful magic!\n', 'The game features simple and intuitive controls. Players use a mouse or touchscreen to interact: click and drag the toys on the screen to move them into the designated box. When three identical toys (such as three balls, three blocks, or three cartoon piglets) are placed in the box, they automatically disappear. ', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1801316a668742b9a8de9f40687728b5-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1801316a668742b9a8de9f40687728b5-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1801316a668742b9a8de9f40687728b5/', '1280', '720', 'animal,gifts,matching,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'grab-piglet', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1801316a668742b9a8de9f40687728b5-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1801316a668742b9a8de9f40687728b5-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(17, '2025-04-19', 'War Robots Battles', 'Enter the future battlefield, and lead your powerful robots in exciting battles. War Robots Battles lets you feel the most exciting robot action. You can attack with powerful weapons and use strategy to win. Choose your robot, equip powerful weapons, and build the strongest combat team. Choose from wind sword, imperial bow, etc.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c5837294dd8d4b29a415bc430d8e6226-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c5837294dd8d4b29a415bc430d8e6226-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c5837294dd8d4b29a415bc430d8e6226/', '1334', '750', 'attack,robot,weapons,battlefield,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'war-robots-battles', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c5837294dd8d4b29a415bc430d8e6226-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c5837294dd8d4b29a415bc430d8e6226-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(18, '2025-04-19', 'Tile Hex World: Red vs Blue', 'Build and destroy!\nTake part in an exciting battle between Blue and Red! This time, you will have to extract resources, construct buildings and even build entire islands!\nTo fight the enemy, you will need to build a path to his island.\nChop down trees, process resources into building hexes, with which you can expand your territory!\nThe winner is the one who captures the enemy flag and subjugates the enemy army!', 'PC - to move, use the WASD keys, arrows on the keyboard, or press the left mouse button and drag in the desired direction, cutting trees and shooting at the enemy occurs automatically.\nMobile - to move, press your finger on the screen and drag your finger in the desired direction, cutting trees and shooting at the enemy occurs automatically.', 'Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/68d6e37310274761b4385d150da8d656-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/68d6e37310274761b4385d150da8d656-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/68d6e37310274761b4385d150da8d656/', '800', '600', 'build,soldier,war,hexa,arcade,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'tile-hex-world-red-vs-blue', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/68d6e37310274761b4385d150da8d656-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/68d6e37310274761b4385d150da8d656-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(19, '2025-04-19', 'The Superhero League', 'Want to join the Superhero League and unlock endless puzzle fun? In The Superhero League, youll become a superhero and begin an exciting puzzle adventure. Take on various killing missions, solve puzzles, and save the world. Control your hero through challenging levels and become the strongest hero of all! This creative puzzle game combines superhero elements with rich strategy gameplay.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Adventure,Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fd9317037d2c44efb6e56d2e26f446cf-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fd9317037d2c44efb6e56d2e26f446cf-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/fd9317037d2c44efb6e56d2e26f446cf/', '750', '1334', 'endless,mission,superhero,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'the-superhero-league', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fd9317037d2c44efb6e56d2e26f446cf-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fd9317037d2c44efb6e56d2e26f446cf-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(20, '2025-04-19', 'Color It in 3D', 'Meet the best 3D coloring book!\nRelax, immerse yourself in creativity and get inspired!\nDraw and create fantasy, cartoon, funny and anime action figures!\nIf you like 3D character designs, drawing, coloring, then this coloring book is for you. ', 'The goal of the game is to paint all 3D figures in colors. The figures are collected in your personal collections.\nControl - a long-tap on the object to start drawing, a swipe for coloring, buttons with a magnifying glass for zoom, arrow buttons for rotating a 3D object.', 'Art,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/59a4c032529d478b936dcfa1490ede76-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/59a4c032529d478b936dcfa1490ede76-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/59a4c032529d478b936dcfa1490ede76/', '800', '600', 'coloring,creative,design,drawing,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'color-it-in-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/59a4c032529d478b936dcfa1490ede76-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/59a4c032529d478b936dcfa1490ede76-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(21, '2025-04-19', 'Contract Deer Hunter', 'Step into the shoes of a skilled hunter in Contract Deer Hunter, an immersive 3D hunting game where precision and strategy are key. Accept challenging contracts to hunt wild animals in various environments, including dense forests and open plains. Your mission is to take down your targets with precision to earn cash rewards. The better your aim and the more vital the hit, the greater the payout!', 'Take on challenging contracts, hunt wild animals with precision, and prove your skills in this immersive 3D hunting game!', 'Shooter,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8c6960ab0b5141cf8115c43bffd90277-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8c6960ab0b5141cf8115c43bffd90277-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8c6960ab0b5141cf8115c43bffd90277/', '1280', '720', 'animal,guns,reindeer,hunting,3d', 0, 0, 0, 'contract-deer-hunter', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8c6960ab0b5141cf8115c43bffd90277-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8c6960ab0b5141cf8115c43bffd90277-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(22, '2025-04-19', 'Bubble Shooter Billiards & Pool', 'Do you love Pool, Billiards, or Snooker? Now, imagine them combined with your favorite Bubble Shooter game! Bubble Shooter Billiard Pool brings a fresh twist to the classic bubble shooter by blending the thrill of billiards with strategic bubble-popping action. Line up your shots, swap bubbles for the perfect move, and aim for high scores in a vibrant pool hall setting. The crowd is watchingcan you master your technique and become the ultimate champion? Play now and find out!', 'Aim and shoot bubbles to match three or more of the same color and clear them from the board. The arrow at the bottom shows where your shot will go. You\'ll see two bubbles: the one ready to shoot and the next one in the bottom left for strategic swaps. Successfully popping groups keeps the board clear, but missing shots adds new rows, pushing bubbles closer to the bottom. Don\'t let them drop too low, or it\'s game over!', 'Bubble Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f64448e3486a424eb60d72827083f05b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f64448e3486a424eb60d72827083f05b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f64448e3486a424eb60d72827083f05b/', '800', '600', 'bubble,matching,arcade,singleplayer,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bubble-shooter-billiards-pool', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f64448e3486a424eb60d72827083f05b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f64448e3486a424eb60d72827083f05b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(23, '2025-04-19', 'From Nerds to Beauties', 'Two girlfriends, the Little Mermaid and Arlene, embark on a world of stylish transformation. Their appearance, full of flaws, requires magical intervention. In the first stage of the game, the girls go through a series of fun cosmetic procedures that give them glowing skin and luxurious hair. At the second stage, you will have to become a stylist, choosing hairstyles, fashionable clothes and accessories. Each of your actions brings the heroines closer to their dream of becoming real beauties!', 'Help two girl friends to transform their appearance and choose a hairstyle, clothes and accessories. Each choice is an opportunity to be creative and create a unique style that will reflect the character of each of the heroines. The most successful images can be saved at the end of the game as PNG images. Depending on the gaming device, either a click of a computer mouse or a simple touch on touchscreens is used to control it.', 'Care,Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2e9c44a2abc24a659ac8b8ce1018d91e-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2e9c44a2abc24a659ac8b8ce1018d91e-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2e9c44a2abc24a659ac8b8ce1018d91e/', '800', '600', 'fashion,hairstyle,makeup,mermaid,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'from-nerds-to-beauties', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2e9c44a2abc24a659ac8b8ce1018d91e-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2e9c44a2abc24a659ac8b8ce1018d91e-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(24, '2025-04-19', 'Mahjong Tour', 'Mahjong Tour game is a cool mahjong game with colorful graphics,  challenging levels and appealing themes. Match tiles of the same type and watch them flutter away. Once you clear the screen, the level is finished and you can move on to the next.\n', 'In Mahjong Tour game match two tiles of the same type to remove them. You win when the all the tiles are removed from the screen. If you get stuck, you have power ups that you can buy to help you continue playing. For each level you complete, you will earn extra coins. Try to save them up for the later stages of the game.\n', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ca1c8ab2b0144819b3a30c2f3ae77ab0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ca1c8ab2b0144819b3a30c2f3ae77ab0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ca1c8ab2b0144819b3a30c2f3ae77ab0/', '800', '600', 'tiles,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mahjong-tour', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ca1c8ab2b0144819b3a30c2f3ae77ab0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ca1c8ab2b0144819b3a30c2f3ae77ab0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(25, '2025-04-19', 'The Drag Racing Challenge', 'Welcome to The Drag Racing Challenge game, an exciting new arcade racing game! Race through challenging missions, unlock and upgrade over 12 cars, and compete against opponents with customizable vehicles. Test your skills in realistic maps across five cities and enjoy smooth, high-quality racing. No fuel or time limitsjust endless drag racing fun!\n', 'E: Gear Up (Shift gear up)\nQ: Gear Down (Shift gear down)\nPlayers can also use the mouse to click on the plus (+) icon in the game to shift up, and click on the minus (-) icon to shift down.\nW: Gas (Press gas pedal)\nPlayers can also use the mouse to click on the gas pedal icon in the game to accelerate.', 'Racing & Driving,Sports', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4fee373f40e54e209cf439e467da7730-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4fee373f40e54e209cf439e467da7730-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4fee373f40e54e209cf439e467da7730/', '1280', '720', 'car,challenge,drag,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'the-drag-racing-challenge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4fee373f40e54e209cf439e467da7730-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4fee373f40e54e209cf439e467da7730-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(26, '2025-04-19', 'Dynamons 11', 'Embark on a brand new Dynamons adventure in Dynamons 11! This online monster collecting game includes two fresh areas to explore; Guardian Island world and the bonus cave.\n\nSeasoned Dynamons connoisseur Jovani will tell you everything you need to know to become a true Dynamon Captain. Encounter Chyroax, Scorvenox, Axolotix, Uryndur, Skyvioru, Golunaryx and many more special Dynamons. Recruit them for your team and beat others in thrilling 1v1 battles with special attacks and power-ups.', 'Play the game using touchscreen controls or your mouse.\n\nThe game consists of spellbinding turn-based battles. You can use the action cards to attack, and catch the opposing creature when its weakened. The backpack is filled with items you can collect and use during your journeys. By selecting it during battle, you can access these special items. Use shards to level up your Dynamons, and to gain new action cards. Challenge other trainers and become the strongest Dynamon Captain!', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c2219c774f3f40649983f09931bee126-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c2219c774f3f40649983f09931bee126-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c2219c774f3f40649983f09931bee126/', '800', '600', '1player,collect,monster,rpg,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'dynamons-11', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c2219c774f3f40649983f09931bee126-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c2219c774f3f40649983f09931bee126-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(27, '2025-04-19', 'Leap and Avoid 2', 'Get ready for another thrilling journey with the white ball! \"Leap and Avoid 2\" brings new caves, lab levels, and fresh mechanics. Discover secret paths, collect coins, and unlock powerful bonuses like speed boosts and shields. Jump on white platforms, avoid black ones, and explore in all directions to find exits. The more coins you gather, the higher you rank. Compete with friends and uncover every hidden treasure!', 'Desktop controls:\n Arrows () () left and right or \"A\" and \"D\"  ball movement;\n \"R\" button  restart;\n \"ESC\" button  toggle pause;\n \"LEFT MOUSE BUTTON\"  control buttons in the menu.\n\nMobile controls:\n Tap the right and left half of the screen to move the ball;\n Tap the buttons in the menu to press them.', 'Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/97968209babf41e1b51ef8830b75c47a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/97968209babf41e1b51ef8830b75c47a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/97968209babf41e1b51ef8830b75c47a/', '800', '600', 'challenge,highscore,obstacles,platformer,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'leap-and-avoid-2', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/97968209babf41e1b51ef8830b75c47a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/97968209babf41e1b51ef8830b75c47a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(28, '2025-04-19', 'Diamond Rush 2', 'Destroy jewels in a new and stunning way in Diamond Rush 2! Just like in Diamond Rush, you beat the clock and destroy as many jewels as possible. But this time you have up to 5 Planets to discover and 15 Levels to beat. The further you go, the harder it gets, so achieve the highest combo possible! Plan ahead and become a true Jewel maniac in Diamond Rush 2!', 'Destroy jewels in a new and stunning way in Diamond Rush 2!', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f7d15bf7954342f1b47392b3574fbe0c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f7d15bf7954342f1b47392b3574fbe0c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f7d15bf7954342f1b47392b3574fbe0c/', '800', '600', 'jewels,diamonds,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'diamond-rush-2', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f7d15bf7954342f1b47392b3574fbe0c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f7d15bf7954342f1b47392b3574fbe0c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(29, '2025-04-19', 'Snow Rush 3D', 'Snow Rush 3D is a fun sledding game that tests speed and reflexes for winter sports enthusiasts, playable in both 1 and 2 players! Try to reach the longest distance by overcoming obstacles and ramps on a challenging snow-covered track, or challenge your friend!\n\nSnowmen, obstacles and tricky turns await you along the way. How far can you go and how many gifts can you collect?\n', 'PLAYER 1:\nA,D: Left/Right Movements\nW or SPACE: Jump\n\nPLAYER 2:\nRIGHT / LEFT ARROWS: Left / Right Movements\nUP ARROW: Jump\n\nOn Mobile Devices:\nOnly 1 Player mode is enabled on mobile devices. Tap left and right on the screen to move left and right. Tap with two fingers to jump.', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e1e32230bdf040d69f4e367015e1c527-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e1e32230bdf040d69f4e367015e1c527-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e1e32230bdf040d69f4e367015e1c527/', '960', '600', '1player,endless,snow,2players,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'snow-rush-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e1e32230bdf040d69f4e367015e1c527-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e1e32230bdf040d69f4e367015e1c527-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(30, '2025-04-19', 'Roblox Craft Run', 'Welcome to begin a 3D running adventure full of speed and creativity in Roblox Craft Run. In this pixel-craft game, you\'ll control your character as he runs and jumps around an exciting platform track. Jump across the bridge and walk into a new level. Start your journey through the maze. Challenge your jumping skills and strategy.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/76d5b7c9275b42a9abd90a41d35da77f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/76d5b7c9275b42a9abd90a41d35da77f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/76d5b7c9275b42a9abd90a41d35da77f/', '1280', '720', 'craft,running,skill,Kids Friendly,No Blood,jumping', 0, 0, 0, 'roblox-craft-run', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/76d5b7c9275b42a9abd90a41d35da77f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/76d5b7c9275b42a9abd90a41d35da77f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(31, '2025-04-19', 'Granny Returns 3D : Evil Destiny', 'Step into a terrifying haunted house in Granny Returns 3D Evil Destiny, where danger lurks around every corner. Trapped in a sinister mansion, your only goal is to escape before the evil granny finds you. Solve intricate puzzles, search for hidden keys, and move silently to avoid detection.\n\nWith immersive 3D graphics, eerie sound effects, and unpredictable jump scares, this game will keep you on edge.', 'W A S D to move\nO To View Objective\nLeft Shift To Run\nMouse To Look\nE to Interact/Hide\nQ to Unhide\nSpace To Jump\nC To Crouch\nG To Drop Th', 'Adventure,Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9af385361fe04fca96a502e95dddc160-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9af385361fe04fca96a502e95dddc160-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9af385361fe04fca96a502e95dddc160/', '900', '600', 'horror,roomescape,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'granny-returns-3d-evil-destiny', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9af385361fe04fca96a502e95dddc160-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9af385361fe04fca96a502e95dddc160-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(32, '2025-04-19', 'Battler', 'Immerse yourself in the world of tactical card battles, where your victory depends on the right choice and combinations of skills! You are fighting against decks of treacherous enemies. Choose one of three unique characters and immerse yourself in exciting battles. Use the character editor to fine-tune your character, adding unique abilities.', 'Put the skills one after the other and try to get an interesting combination. Super combinations are highlighted. In the character editor, choose which skills and \"clothes\" you need in battle. Upgrade by clicking the appropriate button and unlock new characters.', 'Battle,Cards', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a921c3e70c884464a0c6fc7e3d6f97b6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a921c3e70c884464a0c6fc7e3d6f97b6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a921c3e70c884464a0c6fc7e3d6f97b6/', '800', '600', 'fantasy,fighting,boys,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'battler', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a921c3e70c884464a0c6fc7e3d6f97b6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a921c3e70c884464a0c6fc7e3d6f97b6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(33, '2025-04-19', 'Kingdom Puzzles', 'Kingdom Puzzle is a relaxing brain game where you see a grid with different colored regions. Your goal is to place one king in each region while following the rules. Each region can have only one king, and kings cannot be in the same row or column. They also cannot be next to each other, meaning the nearest tiles must be empty. To win the level, you must place all kings correctly. Placing a king in the wrong spot reduces your points.', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game.', 'Puzzle,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/45408603e10348e78d7fb508fc729216-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/45408603e10348e78d7fb508fc729216-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/45408603e10348e78d7fb508fc729216/', '800', '600', 'board,king,relaxing,thinking,logical,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'kingdom-puzzles', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/45408603e10348e78d7fb508fc729216-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/45408603e10348e78d7fb508fc729216-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(34, '2025-04-19', 'Bobblehead Ball', 'Are you a guy who is a talented with skills and speed? If yes, let\'s score.\n\nBubblehead Ball is a thrilling and fast-paced football game where you can challenge your opponents and show your abilities. One more thing, all of our characters in game are not in football world.', 'Use your keyboard to play. Arrow to moving and S for jump, D for kick', 'Football,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/92797bf352a34122b97b2f950046f361-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/92797bf352a34122b97b2f950046f361-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/92797bf352a34122b97b2f950046f361/', '800', '600', '1player,sport,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bobblehead-ball', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/92797bf352a34122b97b2f950046f361-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/92797bf352a34122b97b2f950046f361-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(35, '2025-04-19', 'Chess Duel', 'Master the art of chess with three exciting modes, each offering flexible time settings to suit every player. Take your chess skills to the next level, climb the ranks from Bronze to Diamond and strive to become a top chess player.\n\n', 'Choose between Bullet, Blitz or Classic mode to begin your match. Each mode features a distinct play duration and time increment per turn. Earn ELO points with each win to advance through the ranks and strengthen your tactical gameplay.\n', 'Boardgames', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/15268ba792454d319e6c50d6fe0edcb0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/15268ba792454d319e6c50d6fe0edcb0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/15268ba792454d319e6c50d6fe0edcb0/', '800', '600', 'chess,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'chess-duel', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/15268ba792454d319e6c50d6fe0edcb0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/15268ba792454d319e6c50d6fe0edcb0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(36, '2025-04-19', 'Archer Legend', 'Archer Legend  Test Your Archery Precision! \n\nSharpen your aim and take down monsters with perfect shots! In Archer Legend, you need precise calculations to hit your targets and clear each level. Master your bow skills, adjust your angles, and strike with accuracy to become the ultimate archer!', ' Aim your bow at the monsters \n Calculate your shot for the perfect hit \n Defeat all enemies to clear the level \n Progress through challenging archery puzzles!', 'Shooter,Sports', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1b48fb404ca64716ad98b1f27f98e8da-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1b48fb404ca64716ad98b1f27f98e8da-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1b48fb404ca64716ad98b1f27f98e8da/', '800', '600', '1player,monster,shoot-em-up,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'archer-legend', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1b48fb404ca64716ad98b1f27f98e8da-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1b48fb404ca64716ad98b1f27f98e8da-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(37, '2025-04-19', 'Authentic Football', '3D modeling technology is employed to construct a lifelike football field, encompassing elements such as the green pitch, goalposts, and stands, thereby creating an immersive match atmosphere.\nThe player and football models also boast a high level of intricacy. The players\' movements are smooth and natural, and the flight path of the football adheres to the laws of physics, enabling players to feel as if they are in a real - life football match.', 'PC:\npress the W key for a long pass, \npress the S key for a short pass, \npress the D key for a shot, \npress the Q key to change players.\nMobile:\nJoystick', 'Football', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3e23038b06ea4d39b882713fe059e595-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3e23038b06ea4d39b882713fe059e595-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3e23038b06ea4d39b882713fe059e595/', '960', '600', 'ball,sport,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'authentic-football', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3e23038b06ea4d39b882713fe059e595-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3e23038b06ea4d39b882713fe059e595-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(38, '2025-04-19', 'Car Escape', 'Car Escape Game is an addictive and challenging puzzle game. It will help you train your brain. The operation of the game is very simple, move the horizontally parked cars to the left and right, move the vertically parked cars up and down, and finally drive the red fire truck to the rightmost exit of the parking lot and the game will be successful.', 'Move the horizontally parked cars to the left and right, vertically parked cars to the top and bottom, and finally drive the red fire truck to the rightmost exit of the parking lot, then the game is successful.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f566a02ae1664780b437a0a5dbc4aa14-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f566a02ae1664780b437a0a5dbc4aa14-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f566a02ae1664780b437a0a5dbc4aa14/', '750', '1334', '1player,car,minigame,relaxing,kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'car-escape', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f566a02ae1664780b437a0a5dbc4aa14-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f566a02ae1664780b437a0a5dbc4aa14-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(39, '2025-04-19', 'Snowflight', 'In this game, you control the flight of a bird, exploring snowy landscapes and enjoying the winter atmosphere. Various game modes await you: explore the world, search for hidden items, and take part in thrilling competitions. Each mode offers unique challenges, allowing you to test yourself in different aspects of the game and create unforgettable experiences.', 'Tab - Pause\nMouse Movement - Control flight direction\nLeft Mouse Button - Acceleration', 'Adventure,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6b138e97a74f46afb754a71b1d6ed23c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6b138e97a74f46afb754a71b1d6ed23c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6b138e97a74f46afb754a71b1d6ed23c/', '960', '600', 'bird,flight,winter,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'snowflight', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6b138e97a74f46afb754a71b1d6ed23c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6b138e97a74f46afb754a71b1d6ed23c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(40, '2025-04-19', 'Speen Run Maze Maps', 'run, jump, and climb to avoid direct collisions. speed run maze maps is a casual game, with a very fast runner forcing you to have a quick response to avoid obstacles, beautiful music will make you addicted to playing this game, difficult levels will stimulate tension and challenge adrenaline, complete each level to continue to improve your playing skills.', 'press space or left mouse click to jump', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/325724519e70475c85e1f13a2d43b3ee-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/325724519e70475c85e1f13a2d43b3ee-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/325724519e70475c85e1f13a2d43b3ee/', '1920', '1080', '1player,avoid,runner,parkour,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'speen-run-maze-maps', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/325724519e70475c85e1f13a2d43b3ee-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/325724519e70475c85e1f13a2d43b3ee-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(41, '2025-04-19', 'Glitch', 'Glitch is a 2D platformer game where you must solve challenging puzzles to overcome the glitching platform and reach the finish door. Get ready for a gaming experience like no other, whether youre a fan of puzzles, action, or platformers. Start your adventure!\n\nInnovative Puzzle Mechanics: Tackle a range of puzzles designed to test your problem-solving abilities. Each level offers a unique brain teaser, from classic logic challenges to cutting-edge new mechanics.', 'AD / Left Right Arrow Key = to move Left / Right\nW / Up Arrow / Space = to Jump', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1f6d777f5eeb4c7c8a2dd141e8e4dd87-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1f6d777f5eeb4c7c8a2dd141e8e4dd87-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1f6d777f5eeb4c7c8a2dd141e8e4dd87/', '960', '600', 'design,logic,platformer,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood,jumping', 0, 0, 0, 'glitch', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1f6d777f5eeb4c7c8a2dd141e8e4dd87-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1f6d777f5eeb4c7c8a2dd141e8e4dd87-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
