(42, '2025-04-19', 'Moto Trials Rush', 'Welcome to the thrilling world of Motorcycle Racing, where driving skills are essential! Dodge obstacles, avoid flying sledgehammers, and leap over spikesyour path to victory depends on it!\nEach new level presents a unique challenge, where quick reflexes and sharp focus are your best defense!', 'Use the arrows  or \"WS\" to move and  or \"AD\" to spin.\nSometimes youll need to slow down, and other times youll need to speed up to win. Try different tactics.\nIf your bike gets stuck, press  or \"AD\" to hop!', 'Adventure,Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b15f65390b444e91ab286faf3a1120f6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b15f65390b444e91ab286faf3a1120f6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b15f65390b444e91ab286faf3a1120f6/', '800', '600', 'drift,motorcycle,track,Kids Friendly,No Blood,jumping', 0, 0, 0, 'moto-trials-rush', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b15f65390b444e91ab286faf3a1120f6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b15f65390b444e91ab286faf3a1120f6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(43, '2025-04-19', 'Cat Evolution', 'Embark on a paws-itively thrilling journey of discovery and creativity in Cat Evolution! Combine adorable cats to unlock hilarious and surprising new species. From cuddly kittens to fantastical hybrids, every merge brings you closer to unveiling the ultimate evolution.\n\nMerge &amp; Unlock Cats Evolutions. \nBuild Your Cat Universe!', 'Use mouse or touch to interact with in game elements.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4ae3718c5022433a8639bb5e99d068e2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4ae3718c5022433a8639bb5e99d068e2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4ae3718c5022433a8639bb5e99d068e2/', '1920', '1080', 'cat,idle,clicker,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cat-evolution', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4ae3718c5022433a8639bb5e99d068e2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4ae3718c5022433a8639bb5e99d068e2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(44, '2025-04-19', 'Popping Sushi', 'Drop adorable sushi pieces into the field and watch them merge!\nWhen two identical pieces touch, they combine into a bigger, tastier creation.\nAim for the ultimate sushi roll and claim the top spot on the global leaderboard!', 'Move the sushi left or right with the mouse or by swiping. Click or lift your finger from the screen to drop a piece.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/64fe1e7d60c044519b261592249beefb-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/64fe1e7d60c044519b261592249beefb-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/64fe1e7d60c044519b261592249beefb/', '720', '1280', '2d,cute,relaxing,sushi,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'popping-sushi', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/64fe1e7d60c044519b261592249beefb-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/64fe1e7d60c044519b261592249beefb-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(45, '2025-04-19', 'Galaxy Carnage', 'Battle in space with countless enemies and their bosses coming in waves. Lots of weapons, lots of lasers, lots of explosions and effects. Upgrade the starship to the most powerful machine for exterminating alien invaders.', 'Controls: (WASD) - moving, LMB - shooting, SPACE - death ray, F - shield.\nThe ship is upgraded automatically.\nFor mobile devices: movement - swipe on the left side of the screen, shooting - swipe on the right side of the screen, virtual buttons on the screen.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d424e4a81925455db9e44064be0fc647-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d424e4a81925455db9e44064be0fc647-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d424e4a81925455db9e44064be0fc647/', '800', '600', '2d,arcade', 0, 0, 0, 'galaxy-carnage', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d424e4a81925455db9e44064be0fc647-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d424e4a81925455db9e44064be0fc647-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(46, '2025-04-19', 'Word Rush', 'Word Rush combines solitaire mechanics with word puzzles for a unique and addictive experience! Clear lettered cards by forming words, drawing new cards from the deck to create high-scoring combinations. Each move opens up fresh opportunities, keeping the game exciting and dynamic. With endless word possibilities, Word Rush offers fun for everyone, from casual players to word puzzle enthusiasts. Challenge your vocabulary and strategy skills in this thrilling game!', 'Use left mouse button to interact with any element', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5e44fd0e53ee4513b39f179b9e1c6576-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5e44fd0e53ee4513b39f179b9e1c6576-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5e44fd0e53ee4513b39f179b9e1c6576/', '1080', '1920', '1player,solitaire,wordsearch,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'word-rush', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5e44fd0e53ee4513b39f179b9e1c6576-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5e44fd0e53ee4513b39f179b9e1c6576-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(47, '2025-04-19', 'Gangsta Duel', 'Gangsta Duel is an exciting street duel game that brings you into a world of battles. Face off against the street Gangsta. In this game, you will fight a large wave of enemies. Use your skills to attack and destroy all your enemies. Unleash powerful combat skills and make your enemies feel the absolute blow.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/098390b832c14fd0b42a9356959a4aef-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/098390b832c14fd0b42a9356959a4aef-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/098390b832c14fd0b42a9356959a4aef/', '1280', '720', 'fighting,duel,battlefield,gangsters,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'gangsta-duel', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/098390b832c14fd0b42a9356959a4aef-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/098390b832c14fd0b42a9356959a4aef-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(48, '2025-04-19', 'Squid Game Original', 'n this game you will find the fun of all the games. We have collected the best and combined them into one whole. You will have to play all the popular games from the \"Squid Game\". However, remember: there should only be one winner left in the end.\n\nAll games are carefully recreated based on the original games. You will fully immerse yourself in the atmosphere of each of them, enjoying all the game modes.', 'The game has 7 levels, in each level you will be explained the rules of the game.\n\nControl in the game:\n\nWASD-move.\nSpace  jump (not used everywhere).\nLeft Shift  freeze (only for the game \"Red Light - Green Light\").\nMouse  action.\nEscape-pause.', 'Casual,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/52cb08b85b4f4e53a94b15a72ca7b1bc-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/52cb08b85b4f4e53a94b15a72ca7b1bc-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/52cb08b85b4f4e53a94b15a72ca7b1bc/', '800', '600', '1player,fighting,survival,squidgame,Kids Friendly', 0, 0, 0, 'squid-game-original', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/52cb08b85b4f4e53a94b15a72ca7b1bc-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/52cb08b85b4f4e53a94b15a72ca7b1bc-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(49, '2025-04-19', 'Car Simulator 3d & Car game 3d', 'In this school car parking simulator, you get to drive in the different car driving arenas skillfully with the various parking method and driving skills. Your love for 3d parking games will help you to play all levels and perform great driving in this offline parking game.\n', 'Use W,A,S,D for player movement.\nPress \"Space\" for handbrake.', '.IO,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ce2245d90f74418d9cc9c29d22d3d5ce-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ce2245d90f74418d9cc9c29d22d3d5ce-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ce2245d90f74418d9cc9c29d22d3d5ce/', '960', '600', '1player,drift,school,track,2players,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'car-simulator-3d-car-game-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ce2245d90f74418d9cc9c29d22d3d5ce-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ce2245d90f74418d9cc9c29d22d3d5ce-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
