(54, '2025-04-19', 'Nuts & Bolts Sort: Color Puzzle', 'Nuts &amp; Bolts Sort: Color Puzzle  A Satisfying Sorting Challenge! \n\nAre you ready to put your sorting and logic skills to the test? In Nuts &amp; Bolts Sort: Color Puzzle, your goal is to match and organize nuts and bolts by color to solve each puzzle. It looks easy at first, but as you progress, the challenges become increasingly tricky! Can you complete every level and become the ultimate sorting master?', ' Tap &amp; move nuts and bolts to the correct place \n Sort by color and match them correctly \n Use strategy &amp; logic to solve complex puzzles \n Complete each level and unlock exciting new challenges!', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d874888a381a4d7286bc372cb3c73c0f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d874888a381a4d7286bc372cb3c73c0f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d874888a381a4d7286bc372cb3c73c0f/', '800', '600', '1player,color,timekiller,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'nuts-bolts-sort-color-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d874888a381a4d7286bc372cb3c73c0f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d874888a381a4d7286bc372cb3c73c0f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(55, '2025-04-19', 'Link Flow', 'Enter the mesmerizing world of Link Flow, where logic meets creativity in a captivating puzzle experience! In this minimalist yet visually stunning game, your goal is simple: connect the dots with seamless lines, recreating intricate patterns that test your problem-solving skills.\n\n\n\n', 'With each level, the complexity increases, requiring you to think ahead and strategize your moves. The clean interface, calming aesthetics, and smooth mechanics make Link Flow both relaxing and challenging at the same time. Whether you\'re looking for a casual brain teaser or a deep puzzle-solving experience, this game offers endless entertainment.\n\nChallenge your mind, sharpen your logic, and enjoy the smooth, flowing gameplay of Link Flow!', 'Puzzle,Quiz', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dd697a76bf4440109a31163f09ace2d8-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dd697a76bf4440109a31163f09ace2d8-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/dd697a76bf4440109a31163f09ace2d8/', '720', '1280', 'color,drawing,logic,relaxing,sliding-puzzle,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'link-flow', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dd697a76bf4440109a31163f09ace2d8-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dd697a76bf4440109a31163f09ace2d8-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(56, '2025-04-19', 'Chess Online', 'Options:\n- Choose an opponent from 18 difficulty levels from Beginner to World Champion\n- Selection of time control modes: Unlimited, Bullet, Blitz, Rapid, Classic\n- Highlighting possible moves when choosing a piece\n- Cancel the move, if there was a yawn, you can go back\n- Interactive hints, showing the best move during the game\n- Analysis after the game, highlights mistakes and gives recommendations on how to play\n- Replay the game from the right place\n- Setting the handicap', 'Rules of the game:\n Situations in which a draw is fixed:\n- stalemate (if one of the opponents cannot make any move, but there is no checkmate on the board)\n- three-fold repetition of the position\n- 50 moves without taking and pawn movement\n- lack of figures', 'Boardgames', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b80ebde6ee1b4adfaa96398a4261db80-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b80ebde6ee1b4adfaa96398a4261db80-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b80ebde6ee1b4adfaa96398a4261db80/', '800', '600', 'board,chess,classic,logic,multiplayer,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'chess-online', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b80ebde6ee1b4adfaa96398a4261db80-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b80ebde6ee1b4adfaa96398a4261db80-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
