(58, '2025-04-19', 'Block LEGENDS!', 'Drag and match blocks!\nBlock LEGENDS! is a casual puzzle game, where you drag and arrange blocks on a board. Once you form a line, either horizontally or vertically, you clear that line, and along with that, you may find - diamonds, bombs and score multipliers! \nFinish missions - earn rewards! Missions reset every few minutes, so keep the grind on!?\nOnce you have enough diamonds, you can buy Bombs and NUKES!  You can use these powerups to breeze through levels!\n\nMade with  by Realinspirer', 'Use Touch/Mouse to control and navigate through the game', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/907ea4d6623941b0bbb5e437e4f7d5cf-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/907ea4d6623941b0bbb5e437e4f7d5cf-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/907ea4d6623941b0bbb5e437e4f7d5cf/', '1920', '1080', '1player,block,board,matching,combo,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'block-legends', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/907ea4d6623941b0bbb5e437e4f7d5cf-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/907ea4d6623941b0bbb5e437e4f7d5cf-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
