(334, '2025-04-19', 'Racing Pinball', '\"Racing Pinball\" is a fast-paced arcade game that brings the timeless thrill of pinball to your device!\nLaunch the ball into action and use flippers to keep it in play, racking up points by hitting bumpers, targets, and ramps.\n\"Racing Pinball\" needs skill and reflexes in a classic, addictive experience where the goal is simple: keep the ball rolling and aim for the high score!', 'Use space to launch the ball. \nUse arrow keys to operate the flippers.', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2a1beff87071466a90c4e30c0bfab6a2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2a1beff87071466a90c4e30c0bfab6a2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2a1beff87071466a90c4e30c0bfab6a2/', '800', '600', 'car,classic,flip,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'racing-pinball', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2a1beff87071466a90c4e30c0bfab6a2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2a1beff87071466a90c4e30c0bfab6a2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(335, '2025-04-19', 'Bank Robbery 3', 'It is time for a new robbery!\nYour new target is the most secure bank in the city.\nAccording to the inside data, the bank is equipped with the newest automated anti-robbery technologies, which makes this robbery a tough one.\nBut it shouldnt be much of a problem for a professional like you.\nAnd as always, if you succeed, a big payday awaits you.\nCome on, lets do it!', 'WASD = move\nLeft-click = shoot\nRight-click = iron sight\nMouse wheel / 1-7 = change weapons\nLeft-shift = run\nC = crouch\nE = interact', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/68cfbb1a27534d8ab6fea9c0183dfae2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/68cfbb1a27534d8ab6fea9c0183dfae2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/68cfbb1a27534d8ab6fea9c0183dfae2/', '800', '600', 'bomb,guns,police,robber,3d,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bank-robbery-3', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/68cfbb1a27534d8ab6fea9c0183dfae2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/68cfbb1a27534d8ab6fea9c0183dfae2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(336, '2025-04-19', 'Fierce Battle Breakout', 'This is a fast-paced 3D mini-game that combines survival, combat and strategy. Players will play the role of survivors striving for survival. Facing the threats from enemies, the pursuit of hostile forces and the harsh environment, they will embark on a thrilling journey of survival and defense.\nThe difficulty of the levels will keep increasing. Each level has a large number of enemies constantly swarming towards the players. Players need to eliminate all the enemies to win. ', 'Control the movement of the character through means such as virtual joysticks or touching the screen. For example, manipulate the character to move nimbly and avoid the attacks of enemies. You can also make use of the obstacles and terrain advantages in the game field to formulate strategies and tactics.\nThere are a variety of weapons and equipment available for selection in the game, including firearms, knives and so on. Each weapon has its own characteristics and advantages. ', 'Shooter,Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8f3873526b0843a28ce9e3dc6002d1f0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8f3873526b0843a28ce9e3dc6002d1f0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8f3873526b0843a28ce9e3dc6002d1f0/', '720', '1280', 'cartoon,defence,fighting,shoot-em-up', 0, 0, 0, 'fierce-battle-breakout', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8f3873526b0843a28ce9e3dc6002d1f0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8f3873526b0843a28ce9e3dc6002d1f0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(337, '2025-04-19', 'Just Slap It!', 'Just Slap It is a fun and lighthearted slap-based game where timing and accuracy are key. Compete in slap battles, perfect your timing, and climb the leaderboard to showcase your skills.\n\nWith simple controls and engaging gameplay, challenge yourself to out-slap opponents and rise to the top. Unlock upgrades and enjoy quick, casual fun anytime.', 'Just click/tap on screen to slap!', 'Battle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/163403f90400442c90dafc5d04838441-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/163403f90400442c90dafc5d04838441-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/163403f90400442c90dafc5d04838441/', '800', '900', '1player,fighting,highscore,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'just-slap-it', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/163403f90400442c90dafc5d04838441-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/163403f90400442c90dafc5d04838441-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(338, '2025-04-19', 'Youtuber Mcraft 2Player', 'You need to help the YouTuber girl and her boyfriend escape from prison. In this two-player adventure, they must collect all the YouTube plaques without getting too far apart, obtain the key and the golden plaque, and reach the chest. Open the chest and run to the door. You need to be very fast, you must escape from prison!', '*Use the \"WASD\" and \"Arrow keys\" to move.\n*Double Jump available.\n*Collect all YouTube plaques and find the key.\n*After finding the key, reach the chest.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1af135df04c44b60a54bd78b5c998c6d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1af135df04c44b60a54bd78b5c998c6d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1af135df04c44b60a54bd78b5c998c6d/', '800', '600', '2d,minecraft,platformer,tycoon,2players,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'youtuber-mcraft-2player', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1af135df04c44b60a54bd78b5c998c6d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1af135df04c44b60a54bd78b5c998c6d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(339, '2025-04-19', 'Quackventure', 'Join Quack, the brave duck, on an exhilarating journey through a magical forest brimming with wonder and hidden secrets. Explore enchanting landscapes, solve intriguing mysteries, and embark on an adventure filled with thrilling surprises and endless excitement at every corner!', 'In Quackventure, you control a charming duck using the classic WASD keys and the Spacebar. Guide the duck as it navigates obstacles and flees from a menacing giant purple monster. Along the journey, collect power-ups to boost the ducks abilities or unlock new skins to showcase your style. Can you lead the duck to safety while avoiding the hazards in your path?', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6120cf0775c44d05b9ade2ed8128c307-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6120cf0775c44d05b9ade2ed8128c307-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6120cf0775c44d05b9ade2ed8128c307/', '800', '600', '1player,escape,platformer,runner,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'quackventure', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6120cf0775c44d05b9ade2ed8128c307-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6120cf0775c44d05b9ade2ed8128c307-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(340, '2025-04-19', 'Puzzle Blocks: Fill It Completely', 'Discover the world of exciting puzzles!\n\nIn this game, you have to collect shapes by filling them with blocks of different sizes and configurations. Each task is a unique logical task that requires attention, patience and a strategic approach.\nVarious difficulty levels - from easy for beginners to difficult for real masters.\nOriginal shapes and blocks - each level is unique.\n', 'Select a level. Each level offers a shape that needs to be filled.\nMove blocks of different shapes and sizes using the mouse or touch screen.\nPlace the blocks inside the shape so that they fill it completely.\nIf a block does not fit, move it to the side and try another one.\nComplete the level by filling the shape without gaps!\n', 'Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/115829e099c140a788170a3cfa08cbe6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/115829e099c140a788170a3cfa08cbe6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/115829e099c140a788170a3cfa08cbe6/', '1920', '1080', 'block,levels,logic,tetris,fill,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'puzzle-blocks-fill-it-completely', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/115829e099c140a788170a3cfa08cbe6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/115829e099c140a788170a3cfa08cbe6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(341, '2025-04-19', 'Rush Car Driving - Race Master', 'Rush Car Driving: Race Master is a driving game that delivers thrilling action as you navigate heavy traffic. \n\nExperience the adrenaline of high-speed racing in heavy traffic, where split-second decisions can be the difference between victory and defeat. Explore a variety of immersive environments, from busy urban highways to rural roads. \n\nChoose from a wide selection of cars, from sports cars to muscle machines. Buckle up and start the race!', 'Use the left mouse button to move between lanes.\n\nEarn coins to buy new cars or upgrade existing ones.', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e5fb999a4e014f44b08edf59caea9d4f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e5fb999a4e014f44b08edf59caea9d4f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e5fb999a4e014f44b08edf59caea9d4f/', '800', '600', 'car,physics,rider,vehicle,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'rush-car-driving-race-master', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e5fb999a4e014f44b08edf59caea9d4f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e5fb999a4e014f44b08edf59caea9d4f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(342, '2025-04-19', 'Sponge Challenge', 'In Sponge Challenge, you command a bouncy, yellow sponge through a captivating 2D puzzle platform adventure. Your mission is to guide the flexible sponge in collecting precious purple diamonds while maneuvering through levels packed with obstacles and devious traps. Each stage presents a unique puzzle that requires you to leverage the sponges sticky abilities to climb walls, jump between surfaces, and discover the perfect path to the magical portal that leads to subsequent levels.', 'Sponge Challenge employs simple yet engaging controls. Tap the screen to make your sponge jump. Utilize walls and platforms strategically to alter your direction mid-air, allowing you to navigate through each levels obstacles and traps effectively.', 'Agility,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/47343e009bbf45fe9ba79bad81905853-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/47343e009bbf45fe9ba79bad81905853-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/47343e009bbf45fe9ba79bad81905853/', '1280', '720', 'cube,physics,platformer,run,diamonds,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'sponge-challenge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/47343e009bbf45fe9ba79bad81905853-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/47343e009bbf45fe9ba79bad81905853-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(343, '2025-04-19', 'Boolu Bask', 'Dunk Ball game is an exciting sports-based game that brings the thrills of basketball right to your device. The focus of the game is on scoring points by aiming each ball into the moving basket. Show off your agility, precision, and timing as you handle each ball with finesse and drop them into the basket for maximum points.', 'To play Dunk Ball, simply move your basket left or right to catch the ball as it descends from above. It requires sharp reflexes and strategy to ensure each ball falls perfectly into the basket. As you progress, the game\'s tempo increases, demanding more skill, attention, and faster reactions for scoring.', 'Basketball', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3f74a38ee3e7481c8edde3d78f6c08b9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3f74a38ee3e7481c8edde3d78f6c08b9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3f74a38ee3e7481c8edde3d78f6c08b9/', '720', '1280', 'basket,parking,physics,baseball,target,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'boolu-bask', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3f74a38ee3e7481c8edde3d78f6c08b9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3f74a38ee3e7481c8edde3d78f6c08b9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(344, '2025-04-19', 'Office Escape to Date', 'You have a date after work, but theres a catch: you need to get ready without your boss catching you! Complete your tasks, and prepare for your date before time runs out. But be careful, if the boss appears, quickly close the activity to avoid getting caught and return to work. How fast can you escape the office and be ready in time?', 'Mouse Only', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/82c50c194c6446c2b2f09ff5d62dd2c8-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/82c50c194c6446c2b2f09ff5d62dd2c8-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/82c50c194c6446c2b2f09ff5d62dd2c8/', '1280', '720', '1player,avoid,boss,timekiller,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'office-escape-to-date', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/82c50c194c6446c2b2f09ff5d62dd2c8-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/82c50c194c6446c2b2f09ff5d62dd2c8-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(345, '2025-04-19', 'Real Car Parking And Stunt', 'Welcome to Real Car Parking And Stunt, a challenging driving simulation game. Here youll control a car and put your parking and stunt skills to the test. Choose stunt mode or parking mode, each level challenges you to park your car accurately while performing exciting stunts.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Casual,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d6e56cc236f7472f825565816eb50193-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d6e56cc236f7472f825565816eb50193-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d6e56cc236f7472f825565816eb50193/', '1334', '750', 'challenge,parking,skill,stunts,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'real-car-parking-and-stunt', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d6e56cc236f7472f825565816eb50193-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d6e56cc236f7472f825565816eb50193-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(346, '2025-04-19', 'Feed the Parrot', 'Hello! In this exciting game you will have to help the cute parrot to fill up on delicious fruit. Combine identical fruit tiles to clear the playing field and open new levels, compete with other players, enjoy the bright pixel art and comfortable puzzle difficulty level.  Each game session offers unique challenges and colorful backgrounds, creating an atmosphere of fun and relaxation - the game is perfect for relaxing after a long day at work. ', 'Collect three tiles with the same fruit in a glass, keep the glass full - this way you will get more points. If the glass is completely filled with tiles, you lose.', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1d38ad75aab24f08b2a570c9d0d9e12e-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1d38ad75aab24f08b2a570c9d0d9e12e-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1d38ad75aab24f08b2a570c9d0d9e12e/', '800', '600', '2d,cute,food,relax,sorting,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'feed-the-parrot', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1d38ad75aab24f08b2a570c9d0d9e12e-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1d38ad75aab24f08b2a570c9d0d9e12e-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(347, '2025-04-19', 'Paws & Pals Diner', 'Welcome to Paws &amp; Pals Diner!\n\nStep into the paws of a diner manager and embark on a delightful 2D adventure where every customer and staff member is an adorable animal! In this charming and whimsical world, you\'ll manage a bustling diner filled with furry friends, unlock delicious foods, and attract a variety of cute customers.\n\nAre you ready to create the diner of your dreams and make every animal\'s visit a memorable one?\n\nJoin Paws &amp; Pals Diner today!', 'use mouse (or tap) to interact with buttons and in game items.', 'Cooking,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b1decdb4f2744352af9ca588a766b7a7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b1decdb4f2744352af9ca588a766b7a7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b1decdb4f2744352af9ca588a766b7a7/', '1920', '1080', 'cat,food,restaurant,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'paws-pals-diner', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b1decdb4f2744352af9ca588a766b7a7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b1decdb4f2744352af9ca588a766b7a7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(348, '2025-04-19', 'Steampunk Tower Builder', 'Build the tallest tower and touch the sky with the steampunk tower builder! Simply tap to release the blocks, making sure to release them at the right time to balance the tower. The tower will rise higher with each correctly placed block. If a block falls, youll have to start over. Use the funds youve accumulated to build as high as possible and climb the leaderboard!', 'Click when the crane holding the next floor is exactly above the top floor to build the structure evenly without tilting, otherwise it may collapse.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/76cc5bf650e84ce1907858dedb3bbea9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/76cc5bf650e84ce1907858dedb3bbea9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/76cc5bf650e84ce1907858dedb3bbea9/', '600', '900', 'block,building,physics,tower,balance,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'steampunk-tower-builder', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/76cc5bf650e84ce1907858dedb3bbea9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/76cc5bf650e84ce1907858dedb3bbea9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(349, '2025-04-19', 'BouncePop Quest', 'Guide Jumpo, a squishy and color-changing jelly creature, through over 150 vibrant levels filled with tricky obstacles, moving platforms, and environmental hazards. Charge and release powerful jumps to collect stars, dodge enemies, and unlock new worldsfrom the icy peaks to fiery lava lands. Master timing, aim for achievements, and power up in this cute, bouncy adventure!', 'Press, hold, and release to jump! \nWith double-side jump active, tap left to jump left, right to jump right!', 'Adventure,Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/eed7cbc8883e4ff1ad99a951f85c7cf6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/eed7cbc8883e4ff1ad99a951f85c7cf6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/eed7cbc8883e4ff1ad99a951f85c7cf6/', '1280', '720', '1player,2d,levels,relax,happy,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bouncepop-quest', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/eed7cbc8883e4ff1ad99a951f85c7cf6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/eed7cbc8883e4ff1ad99a951f85c7cf6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(350, '2025-04-19', 'Robbie: Become a Beast', 'Transform into a wild animal and train to become the fastest and strongest in \"Robbie: Become a Beast\"! \n\n?? Improve your endurance, compete against rivals, and prove you\'re the best runner. ???? Get pets to help you train and increase your chances of winning. ?? Enhance your skills and become faster and stronger with each victory! ?? \n\nAre you ready to be the ultimate beast? Train, compete, and win in \"Robbie: Become a Beast\"! ??', 'On the computer:\nW A S D - to move\nR - to dash\nSpace - to jump\nLeft mouse button - to train\n\nOn the phone:\nUse the joystick and buttons on the screen', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/388a6de949e74563b9e6758908bc2865-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/388a6de949e74563b9e6758908bc2865-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/388a6de949e74563b9e6758908bc2865/', '1920', '1080', 'competition,pet,run,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'robbie-become-a-beast', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/388a6de949e74563b9e6758908bc2865-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/388a6de949e74563b9e6758908bc2865-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(351, '2025-04-19', 'Bubble Up', 'Help BUB, a tiny bubble, fulfill its dream of reaching the blazing sun. Use his bubble friends, BLE, to push BUB past obstacles, rise from the ground to towering buildings, and conquer the skies!\n\nYou only need to shoot out BLE by click left mouse, good luck!', 'Left-click to shoot a new bubble. Use physics interactions to adjust the trajectory, ensuring at least one bubble can avoid obstacles and rise higher.\n\nNote: Bubbles attached to the original bubble will be given \'emotions.\' The level is only completed when at least one bubble with \'emotions\' successfully ascend.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/528f190140254420a971b79f822cffab-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/528f190140254420a971b79f822cffab-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/528f190140254420a971b79f822cffab/', '1920', '1080', '1player,2d,challenge,cute,physics,Kids Friendly', 0, 0, 0, 'bubble-up', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/528f190140254420a971b79f822cffab-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/528f190140254420a971b79f822cffab-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(352, '2025-04-19', 'Merge Car Defense', 'Prepare to battle wave upon wave of relentless enemies as you skilfully merge and upgrade the defences of your cars.\n\nBuild out a roster of cars and use them tactically in order to defeat the enemy, collect coins and be victorious!', 'Use your mouse to swipe to upgrade the cars', 'Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1340302dda4c4bf9a8dcbd443baca0d9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1340302dda4c4bf9a8dcbd443baca0d9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1340302dda4c4bf9a8dcbd443baca0d9/', '800', '600', '1player,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'merge-car-defense', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1340302dda4c4bf9a8dcbd443baca0d9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1340302dda4c4bf9a8dcbd443baca0d9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(353, '2025-04-19', 'Fill One Line', 'Dive into the world of fascinating logic and test your mind in an exciting puzzle! Your task is to draw a line across the entire playing field, filling it completely, but keep in mind: there will be obstacles on the way that you need to bypass.\n\nThe game offers many levels, from simple to incredibly difficult, allowing each player to choose a suitable challenge. \n', 'Start from the chosen starting point.\nDraw a line, connecting the cells of the field to fill them.\nAvoid obstacles and plan the route so that the line does not break.\nComplete the level by filling the entire field without gaps.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9e8efe494f36414ca2c9a4b53811960f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9e8efe494f36414ca2c9a4b53811960f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9e8efe494f36414ca2c9a4b53811960f/', '1080', '1920', '1player,block,levels,logic,fill,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'fill-one-line', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9e8efe494f36414ca2c9a4b53811960f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9e8efe494f36414ca2c9a4b53811960f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(354, '2025-04-19', 'Imposter 3D', 'Brace yourself for a thrilling challenge! Tap the screen to release balls and guide them into the holes each round. Afterward, head to the store to snag upgrades and cool items to power up your game. Complete levels, gather diamonds, and unlock permanent upgrades to boost your progress. How far can you take your skills? The further you go, the greater the rewards!', 'Desktop:\n- move around the level with the mouse.\nMobile:\n- move around the level with the joystick.\n\nControls (general):\n- to kill an enemy, just get close to him;\n- if you are a \"Hero\", avoid the enemy\'s line of sight (red cone);\n- if you are a \"Killer\", save your partner from the cage (to do this, go into the cage).', 'Battle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f53b4fb00a184b0db1082c683837bbeb-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f53b4fb00a184b0db1082c683837bbeb-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f53b4fb00a184b0db1082c683837bbeb/', '800', '600', 'impostor,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'imposter-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f53b4fb00a184b0db1082c683837bbeb-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f53b4fb00a184b0db1082c683837bbeb-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(355, '2025-04-19', 'Cyberpunk: Corporation', 'The corporation takes control of the city. You are the only one who can fight back and free the inhabitants.\nEnlist the support of local residents by completing their tasks. Activate the robot and break through the defense line.', 'WASD = move\nLeft-click = shoot\nRight-click = iron sight\nMouse wheel / 1-5 = change weapons\nLeft-shift = run\nC = crouch\nE = interact\nSpace = Jump', 'Adventure,Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/60478b5f81a64e47a159fa44ed0e885c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/60478b5f81a64e47a159fa44ed0e885c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/60478b5f81a64e47a159fa44ed0e885c/', '800', '600', 'cyberpunk,guns,police,robot,3d,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cyberpunk-corporation', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/60478b5f81a64e47a159fa44ed0e885c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/60478b5f81a64e47a159fa44ed0e885c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(356, '2025-04-19', 'Last Standing', 'Players are dropped onto a map and start without weapons. The map is scattered with a wealth of weapons and equipment. Players need to constantly explore and collect these resources to enhance their survival ability and combat power. The core goal of the game is to be the last survivor. Usually, there are multiple players in each game, and they are randomly distributed on the map. ', 'As the game progresses, the safe zone will gradually shrink, forcing players to gather towards the central area, increasing the chances of encounters. Players need to search for weapons and other items that can improve their survival ability. The game also tests players\' strategic planning and psychological quality. virtual joystick or WASD keyboard', 'Shooter,Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5879ec933bf046dabef3ef2cccbd239d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5879ec933bf046dabef3ef2cccbd239d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5879ec933bf046dabef3ef2cccbd239d/', '1136', '640', 'boy,fighting,shoot-em-up,survival,battlefield,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'last-standing', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5879ec933bf046dabef3ef2cccbd239d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5879ec933bf046dabef3ef2cccbd239d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(357, '2025-04-19', '2048 Run Gorgeous Balls', '2048 Run: Gorgeous Balls is a fun arcade game that invites you to chase high scores in a delightful environment! In this creative 2048-style game, youll control a colorful array of balls as they race along a dynamic track.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1144b9340c2a4d359b2d03cb5ff1e3b7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1144b9340c2a4d359b2d03cb5ff1e3b7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1144b9340c2a4d359b2d03cb5ff1e3b7/', '720', '1280', 'ball,track,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, '2048-run-gorgeous-balls', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1144b9340c2a4d359b2d03cb5ff1e3b7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1144b9340c2a4d359b2d03cb5ff1e3b7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(358, '2025-04-19', 'Broken City Combat', 'Immerse yourself in the chaotic battleground of Broken City Combat, a fast-paced FPS set in a desolate urban warzone. As the city crumbles under relentless attacks, you are tasked with surviving the brutal onslaught while rescuing survivors and taking down ruthless enemies. Navigate through abandoned streets, derelict buildings, and multi-floor complexes, each filled with challenges and surprises.', '- Left Mouse to Shot\n- Right Mouse button for Scope \n- E to Pick UP\n- 1,2,3,4,5 to change weapon ', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/853eef516499417e90429335d0a33ca3-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/853eef516499417e90429335d0a33ca3-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/853eef516499417e90429335d0a33ca3/', '960', '640', 'rescue,shoot-em-up', 0, 0, 0, 'broken-city-combat', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/853eef516499417e90429335d0a33ca3-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/853eef516499417e90429335d0a33ca3-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(359, '2025-04-19', 'Stickman Choosing actions', 'The Stickman character was kidnapped by a creature and locked up in prison. Your task is to escape from prison. Use an item selection or action. What should I choose? Left or right? It\'s up to you.', 'Use a computer mouse or control with a touch!\nDifferent items will appear on the left and right. You need to choose the item that will allow you to continue your gaming adventure.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bc1089b38ef24789944883a83e59b44d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bc1089b38ef24789944883a83e59b44d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bc1089b38ef24789944883a83e59b44d/', '720', '1280', 'escape,prison,stick,jailbreak,stickman,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'stickman-choosing-actions', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bc1089b38ef24789944883a83e59b44d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bc1089b38ef24789944883a83e59b44d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(360, '2025-04-19', 'Hidden Object: Clues and Mysteries', 'Hidden Object: Clues and Mysteries is a relaxing hidden object game set in cozy interiors. Solve mysteries with a detective, accompanied by soothing melodies.', 'In the game, you can freely move left and right across locations and zoom in to find hidden objects.\n\nThe game is available on both PC and mobile devices, allowing you to play anytime, anywhere.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cc01f5db481e48898014c0a8bfb802cc-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cc01f5db481e48898014c0a8bfb802cc-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cc01f5db481e48898014c0a8bfb802cc/', '800', '600', '1player,collect,detective,hidden,timekiller,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'hidden-object-clues-and-mysteries', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cc01f5db481e48898014c0a8bfb802cc-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cc01f5db481e48898014c0a8bfb802cc-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(361, '2025-04-19', 'Space Blast', 'Space Blast is a 2D game full of action arcade game where your piloting skills and strategic thinking are key to navigating relentless waves of meteors. Command a powerful spaceship equipped with advanced weapons and take on the challenge of protecting the galaxy from incoming threats.', '\nShoot the planets and upgrade your weapon', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/84306950ffed41d5a7c05093e0092e84-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/84306950ffed41d5a7c05093e0092e84-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/84306950ffed41d5a7c05093e0092e84/', '800', '600', 'airplane,space,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'space-blast', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/84306950ffed41d5a7c05093e0092e84-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/84306950ffed41d5a7c05093e0092e84-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(362, '2025-04-19', 'Escape Room Mystery Key', 'Escape Room Mystery Key is an intense escape room adventure filled with horror and puzzle elements. Choose a role to enter an abandoned school or a hospital. Uncover hidden clues and keys to find your way out. In this game, you must carefully examine every detail in the room, searching for hidden clues.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Adventure,Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/087e2873060f4ecdbb3ea47302aaf840-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/087e2873060f4ecdbb3ea47302aaf840-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/087e2873060f4ecdbb3ea47302aaf840/', '1280', '720', 'escape,highschool,horror,hospital,scary,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'escape-room-mystery-key', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/087e2873060f4ecdbb3ea47302aaf840-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/087e2873060f4ecdbb3ea47302aaf840-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(363, '2025-04-19', 'Ragdoll Bounce', 'Jump into a fun 2D challenge where you control a ragdoll launched by a bigger ragdoll. Click to bounce on platforms and keep climbing. But be carefulmissing a platform means a big fall!', 'Control a ragdoll in a 2D jumping game, bouncing on platforms to stay in the air.', 'Agility,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6514adb546b24845b1bc0ba1cbeb42ee-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6514adb546b24845b1bc0ba1cbeb42ee-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6514adb546b24845b1bc0ba1cbeb42ee/', '1280', '720', 'physics,ragdoll,skill,stickman,jumping', 0, 0, 0, 'ragdoll-bounce', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6514adb546b24845b1bc0ba1cbeb42ee-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6514adb546b24845b1bc0ba1cbeb42ee-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(364, '2025-04-19', 'Mega Lamba Ramp', 'Crazy car stunts and stunt car racing games that will give you the most thrilling experience. Perform dangerous stunts on impossible tracks in our racing and stunt simulator. Perform stunts on all the cars for your favorite characters to move to the next level!', 'To complete the level, you need to get into the car with your character and do tricks on all the cars. \n\nControls: WASD and arrows - move the car and the character, R - flip the car, Shift - accelerate the character and nitro when driving a car Space - handbrake \n\nPhone controls: move the steering wheel with your finger left and right to turn. Press the forward and backward buttons to accelerate and brake.', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/08f7196aa8c241dc81f27f118fa1f61e-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/08f7196aa8c241dc81f27f118fa1f61e-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/08f7196aa8c241dc81f27f118fa1f61e/', '1280', '720', 'car,road,truck,transport,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mega-lamba-ramp', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/08f7196aa8c241dc81f27f118fa1f61e-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/08f7196aa8c241dc81f27f118fa1f61e-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(365, '2025-04-19', 'FNF 2 Player', 'FNF 2 Player allows two players to play at the same time. Players can compete with each other by choosing the characters they want. The difficulty level can be determined by the music, thus appealing to all types of players.\n\nGame Modes: \n\n- Story Mode: You fight with new characters weekly.\n- Freeplay Mode: You can play by choosing the song you want.\n- 2 Player Mode: It\'s time to duel with your friend.', 'Controls: The first player uses the \"ARROW KEYS\", while the second player uses the \"W, A, S, D\" keys.\n\nGame Purpose: To defeat your opponent by pressing the arrows that appear on the screen at the right time. While correct moves increase your score, mistakes cause a loss of points. You should hold down the button according to the length of the arrow for long arrows.', 'Agility,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/151e89092f5a441088efc3f2e6c07e3e-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/151e89092f5a441088efc3f2e6c07e3e-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/151e89092f5a441088efc3f2e6c07e3e/', '960', '600', '1player,2d,party,music,2players,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'fnf-2-player', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/151e89092f5a441088efc3f2e6c07e3e-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/151e89092f5a441088efc3f2e6c07e3e-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(366, '2025-04-19', 'Heritage Mahjong Classic', 'Immerse yourself in a timeless Mahjong experience with Heritage Mahjong Classic. Featuring a single elegant layout, three unique tile skins, a time bonus for quick matches, and a competitive leaderboard, this game offers a simple yet captivating challenge. Perfect for players of all levels, enjoy a relaxing atmosphere as you match tiles, earn bonuses, and climb the ranks. Are you ready to test your skills and embrace the charm of classic Mahjong? Start your journey today!', 'Find and match identical tiles to remove them from the board. Ensure tiles are free on at least one side before matching. Clear all tiles to complete the layout and test your skills! Use the Hint feature to guide you through tricky situations. Enjoy a relaxing Mahjong experience with timeless gameplay, beautiful tile designs, and a competitive leaderboard!', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/10428f0c63f64674927f991b43854b1b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/10428f0c63f64674927f991b43854b1b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/10428f0c63f64674927f991b43854b1b/', '800', '600', 'classic,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'heritage-mahjong-classic', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/10428f0c63f64674927f991b43854b1b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/10428f0c63f64674927f991b43854b1b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(367, '2025-04-19', '100 Doors Puzzle Box', 'The main goal in 100 Doors Puzzle Box is to escape the room. Using all the possibilities you need to open each of 100 doors and move the elevator to the next floor. Search for hidden objects, sovle puzzles and use an items to do this!', 'Use all your skills to complete all levels and get all achievements.\n\nControl for PC: Use the left and right mouse buttons,\nMobile devices: touch input', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/63a0e0f6011e442284345f364db53d81-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/63a0e0f6011e442284345f364db53d81-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/63a0e0f6011e442284345f364db53d81/', '720', '1280', 'logic,roomescape,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, '100-doors-puzzle-box', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/63a0e0f6011e442284345f364db53d81-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/63a0e0f6011e442284345f364db53d81-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(368, '2025-04-19', 'DTA 2: Maniac', 'DTA 2: Maniac. Create chaos like GTA. Use a vast arsenal of weapons, steal bulldozers, buses, police cars, tanks and much more - destruction is all around!', 'Get out into the city and look for adventure.\nAutomatic targeting of the nearest enemy.\n\nWSDA - character control\nLeft mouse button - hit or shoot\nSpacebar - perform a roll\nE - get into the car', 'Adventure,Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/88c37f6288ea4c3f9f7ef791459b246b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/88c37f6288ea4c3f9f7ef791459b246b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/88c37f6288ea4c3f9f7ef791459b246b/', '800', '600', 'car,police,santa,weapons,3d', 0, 0, 0, 'dta-2-maniac', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/88c37f6288ea4c3f9f7ef791459b246b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/88c37f6288ea4c3f9f7ef791459b246b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(369, '2025-04-19', 'Kitty Couple Lovely Valentine', 'Celebrate love with the adorable kitty duo Angela and Tom in Kitty Couple Lovely Valentine. This charming game takes players on a delightful journey filled with fashion, hidden surprises, and puzzles. Help the cute couple prepare for their special Valentines Day by dressing them up, uncovering hidden hearts, and completing their couple photo puzzle.', 'Left Mouse Button Click', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/aadb712f85004122969606329c72e234-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/aadb712f85004122969606329c72e234-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/aadb712f85004122969606329c72e234/', '800', '600', 'couple,love,valentine,cutedressup,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'kitty-couple-lovely-valentine', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/aadb712f85004122969606329c72e234-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/aadb712f85004122969606329c72e234-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(370, '2025-04-19', 'Sprunki Beats', 'Sprunki Beats takes you on a rhythmic adventure through four exciting levels, featuring both horror and normal modes. Explore unique environments as you master the beats and uncover secrets. Fans of Sprunki will love the thrilling challenges, including hints of Mustard mods and connections to the iconic Phase 5. \n\nWhat is Sprunki? \nIts the ultimate rhythm game experience, blending mystery and excitement. Dive into Sprunki Beats and prove your skills in this must-play journey!', 'On Desktop:\nUse MOUSE and LEFT-CLICK\n\nOn Mobile:\nUse Touch Controls', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/291267b4a60e40f9951be1d193dab421-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/291267b4a60e40f9951be1d193dab421-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/291267b4a60e40f9951be1d193dab421/', '600', '800', '2d,challenge,customize,music,musical', 0, 0, 0, 'sprunki-beats', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/291267b4a60e40f9951be1d193dab421-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/291267b4a60e40f9951be1d193dab421-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(371, '2025-04-19', 'Happy Town', 'In Happy Town you have to lead your own city and make its inhabitants happy!\n\nBecoming the mayor of your happy city is very simple! Combine items, upgrade buildings, complete tasks for residents, communicate with them, expand and enjoy a vibrant style and soundtrack. Residents are waiting for you!', 'The goal of the game is to become a successful mayor, develop your city by improving buildings, completing tasks for residents, communicating with them and expanding the territory to make the city happy and prosperous.\n\nControl: left mouse button/touch.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9e4d662e9fd0466d84316a652bd7fc9e-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9e4d662e9fd0466d84316a652bd7fc9e-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9e4d662e9fd0466d84316a652bd7fc9e/', '800', '600', '1player,city,cute,story,connection,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'happy-town', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9e4d662e9fd0466d84316a652bd7fc9e-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9e4d662e9fd0466d84316a652bd7fc9e-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(372, '2025-04-19', 'Delivery Chaos', 'Delivery Chaos is a fast-paced driving game where explosions turn every delivery into a challenge! Navigate through explosive mayhem, collecting waypoints to rack up coins and boost your score. Outmaneuver destruction, and unlock powerful new vehicles and exciting map areas. Can you survive the chaos and become the ultimate delivery driver?', 'Driving - WASD/Arrow keys / Right trigger, Left Trigger, Left stick\nHandbrake - Spacebar / Triangle\nUnlock cursor - V\nReturn to menu - Tab / Circle', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/99bd3235337748819b763aa490db7c72-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/99bd3235337748819b763aa490db7c72-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/99bd3235337748819b763aa490db7c72/', '1920', '1080', 'car,drift,explosion,speed,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'delivery-chaos', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/99bd3235337748819b763aa490db7c72-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/99bd3235337748819b763aa490db7c72-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(373, '2025-04-19', 'Easy Obby Jump and Run Challenge Online', 'Easy Obby: Jump and Run Challenge Online is a highly dynamic game where you jump across platforms, climbing higher and higher! Overcome tricky traps, avoid dangerous obstacles and prove that your reflexes are at their best. Can you make it to the top? ', 'PC:\nWASD - move\nSpace - jump\nTAB - pause\nF - dash  \nShift - show cursor \nMouse wheel forward/backward - zoom in/out the camera\nHold RMB to rotate the camera \n\nMobile: \nUse the game interface', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d414ff5e4e1d4dbaa67e7e3ddd1364b9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d414ff5e4e1d4dbaa67e7e3ddd1364b9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d414ff5e4e1d4dbaa67e7e3ddd1364b9/', '800', '600', 'platformer,climbing,3d,multiplayer,Kids Friendly,No Blood,jumping', 0, 0, 0, 'easy-obby-jump-and-run-challenge-online', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d414ff5e4e1d4dbaa67e7e3ddd1364b9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d414ff5e4e1d4dbaa67e7e3ddd1364b9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(374, '2025-04-19', 'Submarine Attack', 'Command a submarine, destroy enemy ships with torpedoes, unlock new weapons, and conquer the ocean. Engage in thrilling naval battles, use unique abilities, face numerous enemies, and wield powerful armaments to achieve victory.', 'Mobile: Hold your finger and drag in different directions to aim at the enemy. Press the red button to attack.\nPC (mouse): Hold the mouse button and drag in different directions to aim at the enemy. Press the red button to attack.\nPC(keyboard): Use w,a,s,d or arrows to aim and space to shoot. Use shift to speed up the camera.', 'Shooter,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/210ba7afd4ad4871b05f4c178b061064-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/210ba7afd4ad4871b05f4c178b061064-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/210ba7afd4ad4871b05f4c178b061064/', '1920', '1080', 'battleship,sea,ship,submarine,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'submarine-attack', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/210ba7afd4ad4871b05f4c178b061064-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/210ba7afd4ad4871b05f4c178b061064-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
