(418, '2025-04-19', 'Madness Cars Destroy', 'The game features 6 unique modes:\n\nFunnel: Push cars into the abyss as the funnel narrows!\nRotating Cube: Stay on the spinning cube, which speeds up over time!\nDeadly Arena: Dodge falling bombs and collapsing floorsor shoot players instead!\nRight Color: Inspired by Roblox, but with cars!\nDeadly Bouncers: Avoid spinning mines in a gladiator-style arena!\nHot Potato: Pass the bomb or explode!\nChoose from foreign or Russian cars and dive into the action!', 'Computer controls:  TAB - pause W, A, S, D - control the car on the ground Space - brake  Mobile device controls: Clicking on the touch game buttons on the screen', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2f5c17b7d11f449c9224f09041d1c312-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2f5c17b7d11f449c9224f09041d1c312-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2f5c17b7d11f449c9224f09041d1c312/', '1280', '720', 'car,destroy,survival,3d,multiplayer,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'madness-cars-destroy', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2f5c17b7d11f449c9224f09041d1c312-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2f5c17b7d11f449c9224f09041d1c312-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(419, '2025-04-19', 'Water Dig Rescue', 'Dive into the captivating world of \"Water Dig Rescue,\" a physics-based puzzle game where strategy and water manipulation go hand-in-hand. Players carve their way through sand to guide streams of water, aiming to fill a waiting truck at each level\'s end. With a touch of ingenuity and the laws of physics, can you solve the puzzles and achieve a triumphant splash?', 'Objective: Your goal is to collect enough water in the destination truck to win the level.\nInteract: Click and drag on the sand to dig a path for the water to flow.\nCollect: Guide the water to collect golden balls for extra points.\nSolve: Navigate through a variety of obstacles and utilize the environment to lead water to the truck.\nAdvance: Complete the level to move onto the next, with each stage increasing in complexity.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4e840a9a7b45449d8655dbbc86b42bf3-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4e840a9a7b45449d8655dbbc86b42bf3-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4e840a9a7b45449d8655dbbc86b42bf3/', '371', '660', '1player,water,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'water-dig-rescue', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4e840a9a7b45449d8655dbbc86b42bf3-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4e840a9a7b45449d8655dbbc86b42bf3-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(420, '2025-04-19', 'Scary BanBan Escape', 'Scary Players of the realistic survival horror game BanBan Escape will need to devise a plan to get out of a terrifying kindergarten inhabited by terrifying creatures. The game\'s intriguing storyline and tense atmosphere have garnered a lot of attention in the gaming community, and it all started with Euphoric Brothers.\n\nIn Banban Kindergarten, the protagonist is huggy, who plays the role of the searcher. Not only is this school deserted, but it also hides several perils and mysteries.\n\n', 'Instructions :\nMove around the map to try to escape each level before the monsters find you and you can\'t escape.\n\nControls:\n\nWASD to move around the map\nSpacebar to jump\nMouse to move the camera\nF to interact with items', 'Adventure,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/30d4395dc90648258f773e9ed5432689-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/30d4395dc90648258f773e9ed5432689-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/30d4395dc90648258f773e9ed5432689/', '800', '600', 'escape,levels,roomescape,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'scary-banban-escape', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/30d4395dc90648258f773e9ed5432689-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/30d4395dc90648258f773e9ed5432689-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(421, '2025-04-19', 'Ice Skating Ballerina', 'Dive into a winter wonderland and help Ellie and Ben prep for an exciting ice skating competition. Customize skates, curate dazzling outfits, and make a style statement on the ice. Browse through a vast collection of colorful ballerina and glam outfits, chic accessories, and shoes. Glide, twirl, and experience the fun-filled, fashion-centric icy adventure with this engaging dress-up game for girls.', 'Use your mouse to play this game on a desktop, tap to play on mobile devices. ', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cdfe8e38787e49e7a654f9175714d6d0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cdfe8e38787e49e7a654f9175714d6d0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cdfe8e38787e49e7a654f9175714d6d0/', '1024', '768', 'couple,decoration,fashion,winter,cutedressup,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'ice-skating-ballerina', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cdfe8e38787e49e7a654f9175714d6d0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cdfe8e38787e49e7a654f9175714d6d0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(422, '2025-04-19', 'Cute Relaxing Matching 3 Tiles', 'Fun Farm Wonderland is a light but extremely fun game from our team\n\nFun Farm Wonderland is a puzzle game combined with a Farm theme, to create a feeling of lightness and relaxation for all players participating in them.\n\nHave you ever played a match 3 tiles game with such cute design and interface? If not, don\'t skip our game, for the following reasons', 'Use your mouse to play and make the match 3', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6a09b4a2d2674f95b79f4f209affa1af-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6a09b4a2d2674f95b79f4f209affa1af-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6a09b4a2d2674f95b79f4f209affa1af/', '800', '600', '1player,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cute-relaxing-matching-3-tiles', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6a09b4a2d2674f95b79f4f209affa1af-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6a09b4a2d2674f95b79f4f209affa1af-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(423, '2025-04-19', 'Fairy Wingerella', 'Soar through the skies with Fairy Wingerella in this action-packed arcade adventure! Meet Wingerella, a fearless and ambitious fairy striving to become the most powerful of her kind. Embark on her magical journey, navigating enchanting skies and conquering exciting challenges. With captivating visuals and engaging gameplay, this adventure promises endless fun and excitement!', 'Master the art of flight with Wingerella by using your keyboard or touch screen controls. Steer clear of obstacles while gathering power-ups to enhance her strength and magical abilities. Each level introduces fresh challenges and trials, pushing you to soar higher and achieve greatness!', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4ab1284e27394b1c95d210248e2ba752-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4ab1284e27394b1c95d210248e2ba752-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4ab1284e27394b1c95d210248e2ba752/', '800', '600', 'fairy,platformer,runner,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'fairy-wingerella', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4ab1284e27394b1c95d210248e2ba752-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4ab1284e27394b1c95d210248e2ba752-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(424, '2025-04-19', 'Warfare 1942 - online shooter', 'Immerse yourself in the atmosphere of World War II, where every battle is a unique fight for survival!\nThe game is designed for military enthusiasts and those who love intense online battles. Its the perfect choice for players who prefer shooters with detailed gameplay, a variety of characters, and customization. Suitable for both seasoned fighters and newcomers.', 'In the game, you can connect with other players and participate in session-based battles. The winner is the one who scores the most points by the end of the match!\n\nControls for keyboard and mouse:\nTAB - pause menu\nWASD - movement\nSPACE - jump\nC - crouch\nM - open map\n1 - 5 - select item\nLMB - shoot\nRMB - aim\nR - reload\nU - use dog ability\nT - type in chat', 'Shooter,Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8cc62e5427cf443dab15634e5dfe7937-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8cc62e5427cf443dab15634e5dfe7937-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8cc62e5427cf443dab15634e5dfe7937/', '800', '600', 'pet,tank,war,weapons,3d', 0, 0, 0, 'warfare-1942-online-shooter', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8cc62e5427cf443dab15634e5dfe7937-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8cc62e5427cf443dab15634e5dfe7937-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(425, '2025-04-19', 'Valentine\'s Day Couple Date', 'Experience the charm of Paris in Valentine\'s Day Couple Date, an amazing couple dress-up game for girls. Start with a picturesque breakfast and help Ellie glam up. Next, keep their fitness streak alive with a couple\'s workout as you dress them both in fashionable gym outfits and accessories. Later, style Ellie &amp; Ben for a dreamy rooftop dinner. Choose from trendy clothing, accessories, and chic hairstyles to create the perfect romantic ambiance. Stay tuned for a special surprise from Ben.', 'Use your mouse to play this game on a desktop, or tap to play to mobile devices. ', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/27ad571356914b3094dd021e7d0e8bf9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/27ad571356914b3094dd021e7d0e8bf9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/27ad571356914b3094dd021e7d0e8bf9/', '1024', '768', 'couple,date,fashion,holiday,valentine,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'valentine-s-day-couple-date', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/27ad571356914b3094dd021e7d0e8bf9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/27ad571356914b3094dd021e7d0e8bf9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(426, '2025-04-19', 'Minicraft Winterblock', 'Winter has arrived, and everything is covered in snow. In the snow-covered forest, you must be very careful to survive. You need to find two chests and collect all the snowballs. But be cautious, there are monsters everywhere waiting to eat you. You must defeat the monsters and reach the hidden portal at the end of the level. You must leave the house safely and pass through the portal.', '*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys. \n*Mobile touch control is available.\n**Jump on monsters and crush them to kill them', 'Adventure,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b6c394d79f9e4948a8e13ec2cf7899ca-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b6c394d79f9e4948a8e13ec2cf7899ca-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b6c394d79f9e4948a8e13ec2cf7899ca/', '800', '600', '1player,2d,minecraft,pixel,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'minicraft-winterblock', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b6c394d79f9e4948a8e13ec2cf7899ca-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b6c394d79f9e4948a8e13ec2cf7899ca-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(427, '2025-04-19', 'Bird Sort Challenges', 'Bird Sort Challenges  is a fun and relaxing game where you sort colorful birds perched on branches, arranging them by matching colors.\nTest your problem-solving skills as you strategize to ensure no branch overflows and complete each puzzle efficiently.\nWhether youre looking to unwind or sharpen your mind, Bird Sort: Color Sort Puzzle offers endless entertainment in a cheerful and visually pleasing world.\nGood luck!', 'Tap or mouse click to play!', 'Puzzle,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/316134996d6440048b500131cf4f27d1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/316134996d6440048b500131cf4f27d1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/316134996d6440048b500131cf4f27d1/', '720', '1280', 'bird,birds,color,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bird-sort-challenges', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/316134996d6440048b500131cf4f27d1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/316134996d6440048b500131cf4f27d1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(428, '2025-04-19', 'Strategy of war. Tanks and helicopters.', '\"Strategy of war\" is an exciting strategy war game where the player has to control squads of tanks and helicopters, develop his base, choose battle tactics and fight the enemy.\n\nThe game offers a wide range of equipment and weapons, a variety of missions and tasks, as well as the opportunity to improve and develop their forces. It is important to properly allocate resources, as well as use tactical techniques to defeat the enemy.\n\n\n\n', 'The game \"Strategy of war\" is the implementation of a modern RTS game with the necessary game mechanics, such as base management, command of troops, military tactics (including both defensive and offensive tactics), base capture, ground and air battles.\n\nThe main goal of the game is to capture and hold all enemy bases.\n\nYour base is green. Enemy bases are red and yellow. Neutral bases are gray.\nThe combat units in the game are tanks and helicopters.\n\n\n', 'Battle,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bf7c408186694fcf9f63024901828d81-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bf7c408186694fcf9f63024901828d81-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bf7c408186694fcf9f63024901828d81/', '800', '600', 'helicopter,logic,math,tank,logical,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'strategy-of-war-tanks-and-helicopters', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bf7c408186694fcf9f63024901828d81-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bf7c408186694fcf9f63024901828d81-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(429, '2025-04-19', 'Extreme Real Car Driving 2025', 'This ultimate car racing 3D lets you experience real car driving simulator like highway racing with its realistic car damage, accurate car driving physics and many other features. Car driver may use steering wheel, accelerator meter or buttons to control the car. Enjoy the best car driving simulator game and drag racing game that has an addictive game play with endless fun. Now you can modify your any sports race cars from garage according to your interest.', 'Use \"W,A,S,D\" for player movement.', 'Racing & Driving,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/79c7a49fba6441a8899c011b1ea8b6e0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/79c7a49fba6441a8899c011b1ea8b6e0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/79c7a49fba6441a8899c011b1ea8b6e0/', '960', '600', 'city,desert,drift,stunts,track,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'extreme-real-car-driving-2025', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/79c7a49fba6441a8899c011b1ea8b6e0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/79c7a49fba6441a8899c011b1ea8b6e0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(430, '2025-04-19', 'Dice Fusion', 'Dice Fusion is a casual game with puzzle content. The game is easy to understand and use the game mechanism, as well as highly strategic gameplay, colorful vision and with a leisurely background sound, to bring users visual and auditory dual enjoyment, so as to achieve the relaxation of the user\'s physical and mental needs.', 'Drag the mouse dice to merge, and complete the goal of each level to get a reward', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/80da184b1371492795babd5433354483-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/80da184b1371492795babd5433354483-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/80da184b1371492795babd5433354483/', '800', '600', '1player,dice,levels,relaxing,2048,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'dice-fusion', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/80da184b1371492795babd5433354483-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/80da184b1371492795babd5433354483-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(431, '2025-04-19', 'Bouncy Barn', 'Bouncy Barn is a lively farm simulation game where players explore the charming world of farm life. Care for cute animals like chickens, cows, and goats. \n\nFeed and nurture your animals to keep them happy, and in return, theyll provide valuable produce like eggs and milk. Harvest these goodies and sell them at the market to earn profits for expanding and upgrading your farm. With vibrant graphics and engaging gameplay, Bouncy Barn provides a fun escape to create your dream farm!', 'Mouse to Play', 'Casual,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c01a7e40762d4f0f9aef1be852a487df-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c01a7e40762d4f0f9aef1be852a487df-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c01a7e40762d4f0f9aef1be852a487df/', '1280', '720', 'animal,business,farm,activity,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bouncy-barn', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c01a7e40762d4f0f9aef1be852a487df-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c01a7e40762d4f0f9aef1be852a487df-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(432, '2025-04-19', 'Jailbreak. Roblox jumper', 'In this thrilling game with a cubic style, the character attempts to escape from prison by progressing through levels, each represented as a separate platform. On each level, you\'ll need to collect coins that help speed up your escape, but be careful: dangerous traps and obstacles await at every turn. A wrong move or misstep could cost you your life. Navigate through each level, avoid the threats, and move closer to freedom!', 'PC: WSAD or Arrows.\nMobile: Swipes.\nTablet: Swipes.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bfb0d572f25c4ab6874b350d5c340815-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bfb0d572f25c4ab6874b350d5c340815-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bfb0d572f25c4ab6874b350d5c340815/', '800', '450', '1player,escape,roblox,arcade,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'jailbreak-roblox-jumper', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bfb0d572f25c4ab6874b350d5c340815-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bfb0d572f25c4ab6874b350d5c340815-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(433, '2025-04-19', 'Harvesting Veggies', 'Players will take on the role of a farmer, planting vegetables and achieving a full row or column to harvest. The game is based on a cartoon style, with a fresh and cute overall aesthetic, making it fun and addictive to play.', 'After starting the game, drag the fruit blocks to the empty spaces on the grid. Completing a row or column will eliminate the blocks. Each level ends when the top objectives are completed, unlocking the next level.', 'Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d0fb36f56a7247e79f795deea5e04177-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d0fb36f56a7247e79f795deea5e04177-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d0fb36f56a7247e79f795deea5e04177/', '850', '1600', '1player,tetris,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'harvesting-veggies', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d0fb36f56a7247e79f795deea5e04177-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d0fb36f56a7247e79f795deea5e04177-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(434, '2025-04-19', 'Brain Challenge', 'This game will challenge your mind, think out of the box\nUnexpected and mind-blowing answers will amaze you\n250 Fun levels.\n\nFeatures:\n- Solve fun &amp; mind-challenging puzzles\n- Think out of the box\n- Simple &amp; addictive gameplay\n\n** Credits:\n\"Ukulele\"\n\"Royalty Free Music from Bensound\"\n\n\"Forest\" &amp; \"calm-bgm\"\nMusic by \"BandCamp - syncopika\"\n\nMenu vector created by jcomp - www.freepik.com\nMenu vector created by upklyak - www.freepik.com', 'Drag and Drop, Click', 'Puzzle,Quiz', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4536069b05bb4bdc937e3ae18ba631e1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4536069b05bb4bdc937e3ae18ba631e1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4536069b05bb4bdc937e3ae18ba631e1/', '960', '540', 'logic,thinking,trivia,kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'brain-challenge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4536069b05bb4bdc937e3ae18ba631e1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4536069b05bb4bdc937e3ae18ba631e1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(435, '2025-04-19', 'Geometry Open World', 'Geometry Open World is a fast-paced 2D action game where players pilot a ship through perilous obstacles, engage in thrilling battles against diverse enemies, and take on epic boss fights. With a vibrant and dynamic open world, strategic upgrades, and powerful abilities, you can chart your own path to triumph. Will you conquer the challenges, defeat the bosses, and rise to become the ultimate champion in this open-world geometric action adventure?', 'Controls\nA or left arrow key = move left\nD or right arrow key = move right\nQ = use shield\nE = use cannons\nLeft mouse button = interact with in-game UI', 'Battle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/57281179dd58447ab2bd5ddee722da2f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/57281179dd58447ab2bd5ddee722da2f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/57281179dd58447ab2bd5ddee722da2f/', '800', '600', 'dash,geometry,shoot-em-up,music,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'geometry-open-world', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/57281179dd58447ab2bd5ddee722da2f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/57281179dd58447ab2bd5ddee722da2f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(436, '2025-04-19', 'Sprunki Coloring Book', 'Dive into a colorful adventure with Sprunki Coloring Book, a delightful game designed for kids and adults alike. Choose from a wide variety of adorable Sprunki characters, captivating landscapes, and fun designs to color your way. Whether you\'re a budding artist or simply looking to relax, Sprunki Coloring Book offers endless possibilities for self-expression.\nStart coloring today and discover the joy of creativity with Sprunki Coloring Book!', 'Mouse Click', 'Art,Educational', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c6a247522ac147a48c602cd87558dccc-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c6a247522ac147a48c602cd87558dccc-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c6a247522ac147a48c602cd87558dccc/', '1920', '1080', 'coloring,drawing,watercolor,girls,boys,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'sprunki-coloring-book', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c6a247522ac147a48c602cd87558dccc-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c6a247522ac147a48c602cd87558dccc-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(437, '2025-04-19', 'Mahjong Slide Puzzle', 'Experience the thrill of Mahjong puzzles! Strategically match tiles, clear the board, and conquer challenging levels to achieve high scores!', 'In the game, you need to move cards by tapping or sliding the screen, ensuring that cards with the same pattern are unobstructed horizontally or vertically.', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/10d9f5e5cec04793806e91e5d58db9da-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/10d9f5e5cec04793806e91e5d58db9da-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/10d9f5e5cec04793806e91e5d58db9da/', '720', '1334', '2d,logic,matching,sliding,logical,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mahjong-slide-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/10d9f5e5cec04793806e91e5d58db9da-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/10d9f5e5cec04793806e91e5d58db9da-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(438, '2025-04-19', 'Save the cats - Bubble shooter', 'Think strategically, aim, shoot and get rid of all the bubbles.\n\nExplore hundreds of levels with different levels of difficulty.\n\nBe as accurate as possible to free all the cats.\n\nBuy and use boosters on challenging levels.\n\nTo win - clear the field of all the balloons.', '- Use the guide line to aim and explode the bubbles. Balls may ricochet off walls - take this into account when aiming.\n- You will see the next color of balloon in the cart. Use this in your strategy.\n- Don\'t forget about the shot counter!', 'Bubble Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ea1e352d227b4291baf854c2fa0f2e48-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ea1e352d227b4291baf854c2fa0f2e48-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ea1e352d227b4291baf854c2fa0f2e48/', '800', '600', 'bubble,cat,cute,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'save-the-cats-bubble-shooter', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ea1e352d227b4291baf854c2fa0f2e48-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ea1e352d227b4291baf854c2fa0f2e48-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(439, '2025-04-19', 'Racing Car Destroying Zombie', 'Zombie Racing Car fast-paced physics-based racing game. Youre in for the ride of your life through a zombie apocalypse!\n\nDrive your car through deserts, forests, abandoned city,...surrounded by zombies, earn cash, upgrade your car powerful ones. Steer your car to keep balance on the hills while trying to smash zombies into debris. It\'s you against a boatload of super-strong zombies!', 'Use Left Arrow, Right Arrow and press the shooting button, rotation button to control the car', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e5b1ceb6771f4109a4eded908659a1e5-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e5b1ceb6771f4109a4eded908659a1e5-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e5b1ceb6771f4109a4eded908659a1e5/', '1920', '1080', 'car,destroy,zombie,Kids Friendly', 0, 0, 0, 'racing-car-destroying-zombie', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e5b1ceb6771f4109a4eded908659a1e5-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e5b1ceb6771f4109a4eded908659a1e5-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(440, '2025-04-19', 'Solitaire L\'Amour', 'Love is in the air. And so is Solitaire! Enter an enchanting world as you fall head over heels for this charming new Solitaire adventure!', 'Remove all cards from the tableau. Play any face-up card that is one higher or lower than the stock card.', 'Cards', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/24dce1b06e4246f193be7115a854dba2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/24dce1b06e4246f193be7115a854dba2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/24dce1b06e4246f193be7115a854dba2/', '1920', '1080', 'relaxing,romance,solitaire,klondike,tripeaks,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'solitaire-l-amour', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/24dce1b06e4246f193be7115a854dba2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/24dce1b06e4246f193be7115a854dba2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(441, '2025-04-19', 'Farmer Pedro', 'Get ready to till the soil and reap the rewards in Farmer Pedro!\n\nIn this charming 3D farming simulator, youll take on the role of Pedro, a humble farmer with a big dream - to build the most bountiful farm in the countryside. Start by driving your trusty tractor around the initial plot of land, harvesting a variety of crops like corn, tomatoes, carrots, and more.\n\nAs you grow and harvest your crops, youll earn cash that can be used to expand your farmland and unlock access to new crops.', 'Harvest crops and turn them into cash. Grow your farmland.', 'Casual,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b73b4f183efd41459b1baba4c4ee08f5-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b73b4f183efd41459b1baba4c4ee08f5-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b73b4f183efd41459b1baba4c4ee08f5/', '1280', '720', 'business,construction,farm,food,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'farmer-pedro', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b73b4f183efd41459b1baba4c4ee08f5-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b73b4f183efd41459b1baba4c4ee08f5-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(442, '2025-04-19', 'Flag Puzzle Jam: Collect Flags', 'Immerse yourself in Flag Jam, a unique blend of puzzle-solving, flags collecting, and visual ASMR effects! Tap to match banner pieces, watch them glide smoothly into place, and clear the board as you complete each flag. With easy-to-learn mechanics and stunning visual effects, Flag Jam is the perfect game to help you unwind.', 'The navigation in this is very simple.\nJust use mouse on desktop or your finger tap on mobile devices.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/44f351c4975946469730dfc6dc3dc1ef-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/44f351c4975946469730dfc6dc3dc1ef-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/44f351c4975946469730dfc6dc3dc1ef/', '800', '600', 'logic,matching,flags,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'flag-puzzle-jam-collect-flags', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/44f351c4975946469730dfc6dc3dc1ef-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/44f351c4975946469730dfc6dc3dc1ef-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(443, '2025-04-19', 'Witch & Fairy BFF', 'Two unusual girlfriends - a Fairy and a Witch - study together, although they are so different. Fairy, with her delicate pink outfits and impeccable sense of style, is always ready to offer fashion tips and create vivid images. Her girlfriend-Witch, who prefers a Gothic style, chooses mysterious and gloomy outfits. Players will be able to help both heroines choose outfits for various events. Join magical friends in their exciting fashion adventure where style and magic go hand in hand!', 'Meet the unusual students of the magic school and help each of them create their own unique fashionable style. The most successful images can be saved at the end of the game as PNG images. Depending on the gaming device, a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touchscreens is used to control it.', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/85dff0e878384388b23bc0892c2b08c7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/85dff0e878384388b23bc0892c2b08c7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/85dff0e878384388b23bc0892c2b08c7/', '800', '600', 'fairy,fashion,hairstyle,magic,witch,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'witch-fairy-bff', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/85dff0e878384388b23bc0892c2b08c7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/85dff0e878384388b23bc0892c2b08c7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(444, '2025-04-19', 'Stickman Prison and Love', 'In Stickman Prison and Love, help Stickman escape from jail after a daring heist for love! With a mysterious package from his sweetheart, carefully choose your tools to plan his escape. Every decision shapes the twists of this story-driven adventurecan Stickman reunite with his true love?', 'Find a single, successful way to escape from prison.Use a computer mouse to control the game. If you have a mobile device, then use a stylus or a finger.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e3079cf2973e4960bf948fce7574e098-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e3079cf2973e4960bf948fce7574e098-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e3079cf2973e4960bf948fce7574e098/', '800', '600', 'escape,story,stickman,Kids Friendly,No Blood,point-and-click', 0, 0, 0, 'stickman-prison-and-love', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e3079cf2973e4960bf948fce7574e098-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e3079cf2973e4960bf948fce7574e098-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
