(498, '2025-04-19', 'Winter Wolf', 'Winter has come, and the snowfall has begun. Since it\'s Christmas time, the wolf must find three stars during the winter. The wolf needs to carefully hunt and catch three sheep, take their stars, and gather all the bones on the path to avoid starving. It must also be cautious of the hunters in the forest. At the end of the level, it must reach the dark portal to teleport to its desired location.', '*Use the \"WASD\" keys to move. \n*Double Jump is active. \n*Collect all 3 stars and bones to activate the dark portal.', 'Battle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cb801674259e4640b677139a1427f768-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cb801674259e4640b677139a1427f768-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cb801674259e4640b677139a1427f768/', '800', '600', '1player,2d,christmas,minecraft,pixel,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'winter-wolf', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cb801674259e4640b677139a1427f768-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cb801674259e4640b677139a1427f768-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(499, '2025-04-19', 'Squid Escape But Blockworld', 'You need to escape from the Squid competition, but while running away, you fell into the Block world. Its a bit hard to escape from the Block world, but dont stop and keep running. Never stop running until you reach the purple portal. Dont forget to collect the money you see on the way. Be careful of the big monsters chasing you from behind; they want to catch you, and if they do, youll lose.', '*Use the \'WASD\' and \'Arrow keys\' to move. \n*To survive, run to the portal at the end of the level and be careful of obstacles.', 'Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cdef60f561614a7991fa5b0b3515ed85-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cdef60f561614a7991fa5b0b3515ed85-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cdef60f561614a7991fa5b0b3515ed85/', '800', '600', '2d,minecraft,2players,arcade,squidgame,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'squid-escape-but-blockworld', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cdef60f561614a7991fa5b0b3515ed85-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cdef60f561614a7991fa5b0b3515ed85-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(500, '2025-04-19', 'Nubik Courier An Open World', 'Become a top pizza delivery expert! Race through city streets, dodge obstacles, and switch between vehicles to deliver pizzas on time. Earn money, upgrade your gear, and master exciting challenges. Fast-paced, fun, and addictivestart delivering now!', 'Moving around on the computer using the keyboard. Movement on mobile devices using the appropriate buttons and joystick. Deliver orders to customers and buy new modes of transport with the money you earn!', 'Adventure,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4748ebf577bb47bb9913ce908571377a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4748ebf577bb47bb9913ce908571377a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4748ebf577bb47bb9913ce908571377a/', '800', '600', 'city,delivery,3d,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'nubik-courier-an-open-world', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4748ebf577bb47bb9913ce908571377a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4748ebf577bb47bb9913ce908571377a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(501, '2025-04-19', 'Bubble Shooter Candy Wheel Level Pack', 'Bubble Shooter Candy Wheel Level Pack is a fun and challenging game where you shoot candy bubbles to match three or more on a rotating wheel. Use power-ups like the Bomb to blast nearby candies and the Stopwatch to freeze time for unlimited moves. Earn coins by clearing levels and use them to unlock more exciting levels. With increasing difficulty and sweet rewards, this game promises endless fun. Spin, aim, and conquer the candy wheel!', 'Use your mouse or touchpad to playsimply tap aim and shoot candy bubbles onto the rotating wheel. It\'s easy, intuitive, and fun!', 'Bubble Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d4a4258e68d54e2ba75fc3b29805571d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d4a4258e68d54e2ba75fc3b29805571d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d4a4258e68d54e2ba75fc3b29805571d/', '600', '800', 'bubble,candy,levels,matching,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bubble-shooter-candy-wheel-level-pack', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d4a4258e68d54e2ba75fc3b29805571d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d4a4258e68d54e2ba75fc3b29805571d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(502, '2025-04-19', 'Mini Games Puzzle Collection', 'Mini Games: Puzzle Collection is an addictive collection of mini games, including 3 of the most popular puzzle games. You need to use limited wooden planks to build a bridge to help doge eat\nbones on the other side of the river, draw lines to send donuts to doge. You can also experience the day of a stall owner, satisfying the needs of customers exactly. These fresh and interesting challenges require you to use your brain and solve them one by one through logical thinking.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/47b72fc202d146708eae844eda608e60-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/47b72fc202d146708eae844eda608e60-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/47b72fc202d146708eae844eda608e60/', '1334', '750', 'minigame,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mini-games-puzzle-collection', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/47b72fc202d146708eae844eda608e60-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/47b72fc202d146708eae844eda608e60-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(503, '2025-04-19', 'Spider-Noob obstacle course', 'Noob was bitten by a creeper-spider and became a spider-noob! Help Noob train in the big city, fly on webs, collect badges, unlock new costumes, and complete challenges. Unlock new levels. \n\nComplete all the levels and turn Noob into a Pro-spider', 'The game features very simple controls, with badges scattered throughout the level. When near a badge, hold down the tap or mouse button to grab onto it, then release at the right time to continue your flight.\n\nThere is also a hidden icon on each level, see if you can find it.\n\nEach badge collected earns points, try to collect as many as possible on each level.\n\nUse your points and badges to purchase new costumes for Nubika, try to collect them all.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/75be36a35a6e4c298be61a0b8c229a97-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/75be36a35a6e4c298be61a0b8c229a97-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/75be36a35a6e4c298be61a0b8c229a97/', '800', '600', 'minecraft,spiderman,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'spider-noob-obstacle-course', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/75be36a35a6e4c298be61a0b8c229a97-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/75be36a35a6e4c298be61a0b8c229a97-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(504, '2025-04-19', 'Robot Terminator T Rex', 'Ready for an adventure in Robot Terminator T-Rex! Enter the wonderful world where robot dinosaurs and zombies collide in a nervous battle. You\'ll control a terrifying robotic T-Rex, equipped with powerful weapons and amazing abilities. ', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/92077d70d5414b3ab766c7e896ea1444-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/92077d70d5414b3ab766c7e896ea1444-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/92077d70d5414b3ab766c7e896ea1444/', '1334', '750', 'robot,zombie,battlefield,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'robot-terminator-t-rex', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/92077d70d5414b3ab766c7e896ea1444-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/92077d70d5414b3ab766c7e896ea1444-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(505, '2025-04-19', 'Digit Shooter', 'Digit Shooter! plays like a vertical-version shooting running arcade game. With 3D green numbers, you can launch green numbers to shoot green numbers and numbered walls. You can shoot them and collect them to make your number bigger. Don\'t waste bullets and time on red walls while avoiding them. When you reach the finish line, try to focus on one line to shoot, then you will collect more rewards', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0b4d89e469fd48859cdb46a52cb7d362-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0b4d89e469fd48859cdb46a52cb7d362-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0b4d89e469fd48859cdb46a52cb7d362/', '720', '1280', 'arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'digit-shooter', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0b4d89e469fd48859cdb46a52cb7d362-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0b4d89e469fd48859cdb46a52cb7d362-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(506, '2025-04-19', 'SnakeMaxx', 'Dive into thrilling PvP battles or solo runs! Unlock avatars, skins, and boosters to power up your snake in this fast-paced action runner.', 'Playing SnakeMaxx is easy and intuitive! \n-On mobile, simply swipe or drag with one finger to guide your snake through the fast-paced levels. \n-On a computer, control the snake effortlessly by moving your mouse!\n\nCollect power-ups, avoid obstacles, and outmaneuver your opponents in PvP mode or aim for a high score in solo play. ', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d5a03822f6cd4807a9f8d1d65212efe2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d5a03822f6cd4807a9f8d1d65212efe2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d5a03822f6cd4807a9f8d1d65212efe2/', '480', '854', '1player,runner,snake,speed,2players,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'snakemaxx', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d5a03822f6cd4807a9f8d1d65212efe2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d5a03822f6cd4807a9f8d1d65212efe2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(507, '2025-04-19', 'Mahjong Connect Cookware', 'Help your chef to clean his kitchen and remove all cookware by connecting them with a line that can change it\'s direction no more than 2 times!', 'use your mouse to connect cookware', 'Cooking,Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a4bdaa15542d4c37b89f947d2b946b9f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a4bdaa15542d4c37b89f947d2b946b9f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a4bdaa15542d4c37b89f947d2b946b9f/', '960', '540', 'chef,cook,highscore,timer,connection,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mahjong-connect-cookware', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a4bdaa15542d4c37b89f947d2b946b9f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a4bdaa15542d4c37b89f947d2b946b9f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(508, '2025-04-19', 'Pixel Mini Golf', 'Mini Golf is a complete game, with 400 different levels, and an addictive system. Have fun exploring the games green hills and plains while listening to the birds and enjoying its beautiful views, collect as many coins as possible and try to hit all the holes to achieve the highest score.\n\nAmong the game mechanics are levels with: Portals, Boxing Gloves, Cannons, Burners, Impulses, Mill, Sand, Mole Holes, Spikes and Movement Blocks that will help or hinder your game!', 'Compatible with all devices (Mouse and touch controls)', 'Sports,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d8c6861f8a324e87998f43f16c2eb4c6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d8c6861f8a324e87998f43f16c2eb4c6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d8c6861f8a324e87998f43f16c2eb4c6/', '720', '1280', 'golf,pixel,sport,minigolf,singleplayer,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'pixel-mini-golf', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d8c6861f8a324e87998f43f16c2eb4c6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d8c6861f8a324e87998f43f16c2eb4c6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(509, '2025-04-19', 'Checkers', 'Immerse yourself in classic checkers on the go! \nEnjoy strategic moves, challenging AI, and hot-seat multiplayer fun in this classic checkers game!\nDive into the timeless fun of Checkers! Experience sleek design, smart AI opponent, and thrilling hot-seat multiplayer matches in this classic board game. Master strategy and make every move count!', 'Follow on screen instructions.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ef73cd7e03d04cc5bab800afff2b11cb-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ef73cd7e03d04cc5bab800afff2b11cb-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ef73cd7e03d04cc5bab800afff2b11cb/', '800', '600', '2d,board,chess,2players,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'checkers', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ef73cd7e03d04cc5bab800afff2b11cb-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ef73cd7e03d04cc5bab800afff2b11cb-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(510, '2025-04-19', 'Skating Park', 'Welcome to Skating Park, where skateboards meet high-speed racing madness! Dive into a world of adrenaline-fueled stunts and fierce competition as you shred through gravity-defying tracks. Master insane ramps, outmaneuver opponents, and conquer the leaderboard. Feel the thrill as you jump off the track, taking daring shortcuts to gain the edge. Get ready to grind and glide your way to victory!', '- Move the player left/right by dragging the mouse left/right.\n- Jump off the track and find another track for a shortcut\n- Throw enemies off the track by hitting them', 'Racing & Driving,.IO', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d648419e573946be98a32bde0c905f14-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d648419e573946be98a32bde0c905f14-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d648419e573946be98a32bde0c905f14/', '350', '650', 'competition,skate,stunts,track,skateboard,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'skating-park', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d648419e573946be98a32bde0c905f14-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d648419e573946be98a32bde0c905f14-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(511, '2025-04-19', 'Sword Play! Ninja Slice Runner', 'Become a legendary kunai master in this thrilling combination of dynamic gameplay and classic ninja action. Play offline and enjoy the freedom to dive into the adventure whenever you want. Slice through foes, overcome obstacles, and set out on an epic ninja quest without boundaries.\n\nWill you seize the blade and claim your place as the ultimate ninja warrior?', 'Navigating the game is easy and intuitive. Use your mouse on a desktop or simply tap with your finger on mobile devices.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f37e6802a81944d7bbe172e496b79eb9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f37e6802a81944d7bbe172e496b79eb9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f37e6802a81944d7bbe172e496b79eb9/', '800', '600', '1player,ninja,ragdoll,runner,sword,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'sword-play-ninja-slice-runner', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f37e6802a81944d7bbe172e496b79eb9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f37e6802a81944d7bbe172e496b79eb9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(512, '2025-04-19', 'Uno Online', 'UNO Online is a strategy card game. In the game, the first player to clear his hand will become the winner. In order to win, you need to guess the deck of cards in your opponent\'s hands and  arrange your card order reasonably. There are also function cards in the game. When you draw a function card, think about how to turn the situation to your advantage. You can use color cards to\nchange the color of the game, or use +2 cards to make your opponent\'s cards never run out.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/791507585c1047ada5e2c58a338ae257-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/791507585c1047ada5e2c58a338ae257-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/791507585c1047ada5e2c58a338ae257/', '1920', '1080', 'number', 0, 0, 0, 'uno-online', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/791507585c1047ada5e2c58a338ae257-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/791507585c1047ada5e2c58a338ae257-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(513, '2025-04-19', 'Stickman Duo: Escape The Tomb', '- Stickman Duo: Escape The Tomb is an addictive puzzle game where you have to synchronize two characters. Control both stickmen at the same time and use the buttons to move, push boxes and collect coins to reach the exit in the maze.', '- Move red boy and blue girl by arrows and avoid obstacles. Red boy must avoid the blue water while Blue girl must avoid the red water.\n- Just tap the button \"Change\" to change from Blue girl stick to Red boy.\n- Collect coin as many as possible.', 'Adventure,Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dc4acc1d53294ba4a265674820c51e31-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dc4acc1d53294ba4a265674820c51e31-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/dc4acc1d53294ba4a265674820c51e31/', '1920', '1080', '2d,logic,arcade,stickman', 0, 0, 0, 'stickman-duo-escape-the-tomb', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dc4acc1d53294ba4a265674820c51e31-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dc4acc1d53294ba4a265674820c51e31-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(514, '2025-04-19', 'Mobile Legends Slime 3v3', 'Mobile Legends Slime 3v3 will bring you into a fun arena of exciting battles! In this 3v3 PvP game, you can unblock many slime characters. Enter a variety of colorful battle scenes. Each character has unique skills and fighting styles, ensuring you find the best gameplay.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f4d128de33f14bea95d3fe2382270bb4-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f4d128de33f14bea95d3fe2382270bb4-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f4d128de33f14bea95d3fe2382270bb4/', '1334', '750', 'fighting,battleroyale,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mobile-legends-slime-3v3', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f4d128de33f14bea95d3fe2382270bb4-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f4d128de33f14bea95d3fe2382270bb4-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(515, '2025-04-19', 'Shape Transform Blob Racing', 'Shape Transform: Blob Racing is a casual running game. In this game, you will control a little Blob, running, shape-shifting, and go through various challenges! It would help if you quickly switched the Blobs shape while running to navigate various obstacles. For example, turning into a ball helps you roll through narrow passages. When you become a square, it helps you cross flat areas more  easily.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ad1cd79d850e4a678bef640cb51ffa75-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ad1cd79d850e4a678bef640cb51ffa75-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ad1cd79d850e4a678bef640cb51ffa75/', '720', '1280', '1player', 0, 0, 0, 'shape-transform-blob-racing', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ad1cd79d850e4a678bef640cb51ffa75-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ad1cd79d850e4a678bef640cb51ffa75-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(516, '2025-04-19', 'Brick Breaker Chipi Chipi Chapa Chapa Cat', 'Break bricks, collect power-ups for more fun breaking bricks and watch Chipy Chipy Chipa Cat and El Primo Bara Bere dancing. Go through interesting and exciting levels in the fun game about Chippy Chippy Chippy Chappa Chappa Cat and El Primo.\nPass levels of different difficulty and set a personal record.', 'Control the bottom area and hit the balls into the green blocks. Once all the green blocks are destroyed, the level will be completed. Collect falling bonuses in order to increase the number of balls and gain extra life.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6fe210242c6e45a68a4d78293eb91086-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6fe210242c6e45a68a4d78293eb91086-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6fe210242c6e45a68a4d78293eb91086/', '800', '600', '2d,levels,brickbreaker,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'brick-breaker-chipi-chipi-chapa-chapa-cat', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6fe210242c6e45a68a4d78293eb91086-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6fe210242c6e45a68a4d78293eb91086-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(517, '2025-04-19', 'Hook Master Mafia City', 'Hook Master: Mafia City is a casual puzzle game that combines puzzle solving, escape and collecting elements. In this dangerous city, you have to solve puzzles with your smart mind and use a cool grappling hook and swing skills, like a secret agent\'s flexible dodge, precise strike\nand successfully escape the enemy hunt! There are two kinds of gameplay: grappling and swinging. Use the grapple for flexible movement, quickly across the city by snagging walls, buildings and so on. ', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2be9e4a6f9904542a68aa8941283a19e-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2be9e4a6f9904542a68aa8941283a19e-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2be9e4a6f9904542a68aa8941283a19e/', '640', '1136', 'combine,escape,fighting', 0, 0, 0, 'hook-master-mafia-city', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2be9e4a6f9904542a68aa8941283a19e-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2be9e4a6f9904542a68aa8941283a19e-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(518, '2025-04-19', 'DriftClicker', 'Race Clicker: DRIFT MAX is an action clicker that immerses you in the world of thrilling drift races, demanding lightning-fast reflexes and the ability to make decisions at high speed. Participate in dynamic drift where every turn is a high-speed challenge.\n- Open containers to obtain unique parts and enhance your car.\n- Participate in high-stakes races to earn keys for containers and unlock new possibilities.\n- Upgrade your car to dominate races and defeat all your rivals.', 'Clicker controls:\n1. Click on the car or use space to gain speed and earn money.\n2. Spend money on leveling up your car to drive faster.\n\nRace controls:\n1. Gain as much speed as possible by tapping or clicking the mouse or using space key at the beginning of the race.\n2. Control using the keys \"A\", \"D\" or swipes on the screen.\n3. Aim at the racers, catch up and knock them down.', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a02de4821afa46c3b69dd95385c314db-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a02de4821afa46c3b69dd95385c314db-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a02de4821afa46c3b69dd95385c314db/', '800', '600', 'car,drift,street,arcade,clicker', 0, 0, 0, 'driftclicker', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a02de4821afa46c3b69dd95385c314db-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a02de4821afa46c3b69dd95385c314db-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(519, '2025-04-19', 'Digital Circus Find The Differences', 'Step into the whimsical and wacky world of Digital Circus: Find The Differences, where fun meets challenge! Explore vibrant and surreal circus scenes filled with unique characters and zany details, all while sharpening your observation skills. Can you spot the subtle changes between two seemingly identical pictures?\nPut your eyes to the test and discover how many differences you can find in this exciting puzzle adventure!', 'Mouse click', 'Puzzle,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8c8d1391a74d44fbb34f0da1a9cf5739-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8c8d1391a74d44fbb34f0da1a9cf5739-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8c8d1391a74d44fbb34f0da1a9cf5739/', '1920', '1080', 'circus,detective,find,hidden,differences,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'digital-circus-find-the-differences', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8c8d1391a74d44fbb34f0da1a9cf5739-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8c8d1391a74d44fbb34f0da1a9cf5739-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(520, '2025-04-19', 'The Office Escape', 'The Office Escape is an exciting adventure where every step towards freedom becomes a test for the Regime and the thinking factor!', 'You need to shoot at enemies, close cranes and destroy doors.\nPC - shooting is carried out with the left mouse button\nMobile devices - shooting is carried out by tapping on the screen', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8ff61fb901c34b909af5f15b3558b212-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8ff61fb901c34b909af5f15b3558b212-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8ff61fb901c34b909af5f15b3558b212/', '800', '600', 'aim,escape,guns,3d,boys,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'the-office-escape', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8ff61fb901c34b909af5f15b3558b212-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8ff61fb901c34b909af5f15b3558b212-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(521, '2025-04-19', 'Drive Ahead Sports', 'Want to begin a pixelated sports showdown like no other? In Drive Ahead! Sports, youll be behind the wheel of amazing vehicles, engaging in exciting soccer matches! Enjoy the rush of driving and the fun of the game! Use your skills to kick the ball, attack the opponent\'s goal, and aim for victory!\n', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Sports', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3fa215490c4a43e18bb21c0f52a35a1c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3fa215490c4a43e18bb21c0f52a35a1c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3fa215490c4a43e18bb21c0f52a35a1c/', '1336', '640', 'fighting,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'drive-ahead-sports', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3fa215490c4a43e18bb21c0f52a35a1c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3fa215490c4a43e18bb21c0f52a35a1c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(522, '2025-04-19', 'Sprunki Jigsaw Puzzle', 'Sprunki Jigsaw Puzzle is a fun jigsaw puzzle game. You can select one of the fifteen images and then select one of the four modes (16, 36, 64 and 100 pieces). Select your favorite picture and complete the jigsaw in the shortest time possible! Have fun and enjoy!', 'Use mouse or touch on the screen to solve the puzzle!', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e46c8867676648d1b62d4f29fffba94b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e46c8867676648d1b62d4f29fffba94b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e46c8867676648d1b62d4f29fffba94b/', '1920', '1080', 'cartoon,skill,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'sprunki-jigsaw-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e46c8867676648d1b62d4f29fffba94b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e46c8867676648d1b62d4f29fffba94b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(523, '2025-04-19', 'Squishy: Taba Paw ASMR', 'A cute collection of relaxing taba paws and other squishes on your smartphone! Relax by sipping squishes in different directions and enjoy sound of squishing!', 'Stretch the squishes in different directions and collect coins.\n\nOn a PC with the mouse, and on a smartphone with the touch of your fingers!\n\nCollect the whole collection of bright and realistic squishes!', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dae3a6ea18594335bb4c8c9400833747-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dae3a6ea18594335bb4c8c9400833747-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/dae3a6ea18594335bb4c8c9400833747/', '800', '600', 'cat,cute,relax,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'squishy-taba-paw-asmr', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dae3a6ea18594335bb4c8c9400833747-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dae3a6ea18594335bb4c8c9400833747-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(524, '2025-04-19', 'Zombie Raft', 'Zombie Raft is a survival game. The zombie apocalypse is coming and it\'s time for a raft survival game! Protect yourself and other survivors from the looming zombie tsunami, and push them all back, it\'s your responsibility to survive on the raft! Squeeze the vehicles forward and push them if necessary! Keep going, escape the zombie tsunami, and conquer the barren land! If stranded survivors are found, you need to rescue them! Join us and experience the best zombie game!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b12491a3179c48de88a3ecd42e22c9ac-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b12491a3179c48de88a3ecd42e22c9ac-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b12491a3179c48de88a3ecd42e22c9ac/', '720', '1280', 'survival,zombie', 0, 0, 0, 'zombie-raft', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b12491a3179c48de88a3ecd42e22c9ac-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b12491a3179c48de88a3ecd42e22c9ac-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(525, '2025-04-19', 'Winter Mahjong', 'You can test your pattern detection skills in this relaxed mahjong &amp; connect puzzle game with winter christmas theme. You can eliminate pair of same tiles. The line connecting the two clicked tiles can\'t have more than 2 corners. Some levels the tiles can auto slide( to left, to right, to up, to bottom). Can you clear the board before time runs out? Enjoying matching winter tiles with 32 levels in this game.', 'You mouse or tap to play this christmas mahjong game.', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7a25a32aab5a43fa8eebbd8baa9aaccd-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7a25a32aab5a43fa8eebbd8baa9aaccd-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/7a25a32aab5a43fa8eebbd8baa9aaccd/', '1280', '768', 'christmas,tiles,link,connection,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'winter-mahjong', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7a25a32aab5a43fa8eebbd8baa9aaccd-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7a25a32aab5a43fa8eebbd8baa9aaccd-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(526, '2025-04-19', 'Rift of Hell-Demons War', 'Hordes of insidious demons are lurking in the hellish catacombs! Can you challenge hundreds of hellish creatures and destroy them all as you descend closer to the citadel?\nYou have several types of weapons at your disposal and an almost endless supply of ammo along the way!\nWith each step, collecting gold that falls from enemies, you will become stronger and stronger, strength, speed of movement, arsenal of deadly weapons, armor - all this will depend on your actions.', 'Use mouse or WASD to move.\nRotate - mouse.\nShoot - spacebar or left mouse button.', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/12d1e34f438d4531ae3847ea1e8beee7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/12d1e34f438d4531ae3847ea1e8beee7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/12d1e34f438d4531ae3847ea1e8beee7/', '800', '600', '1player,horror,monster,weapons,3d', 0, 0, 0, 'rift-of-hell-demons-war', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/12d1e34f438d4531ae3847ea1e8beee7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/12d1e34f438d4531ae3847ea1e8beee7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(527, '2025-04-19', 'Bubble Ball', 'Bubble Ball is an untimed bubble-popping strategy game with a classic interface and arcade special effects noises. The player uses an arrow shooter to pop clusters of three or more matching bubbles to earn points and special gifts.', 'Using mouse, click the left one to shoot', 'Bubble Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0ab5e8c3851e4d1e9515e3571ace4709-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0ab5e8c3851e4d1e9515e3571ace4709-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0ab5e8c3851e4d1e9515e3571ace4709/', '800', '600', '1player,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bubble-ball', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0ab5e8c3851e4d1e9515e3571ace4709-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0ab5e8c3851e4d1e9515e3571ace4709-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(528, '2025-04-19', 'Eco Block Puzzle', 'Unleash your creativity in a classic block puzzle game, then collect pets like in farming games! You are commanding the team of ecologists who are restoring the valley after an environmental catastrophe.', 'It\'s a classic block puzzle game with additional meta. Players should clean the environment after an ecological catastrophe. Expand cleaned land and purchase animals and lifeforms.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/05e9a710e98f481ea38aaa58a1aa61b9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/05e9a710e98f481ea38aaa58a1aa61b9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/05e9a710e98f481ea38aaa58a1aa61b9/', '800', '600', 'animal,block,farm,logical,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'eco-block-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/05e9a710e98f481ea38aaa58a1aa61b9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/05e9a710e98f481ea38aaa58a1aa61b9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(529, '2025-04-19', '2 Player Online Chess', 'Enjoy the classic game of chess with 2 Player Online Chess! Play solo against the computer or challenge a friend in 2-player mode. Easy to use, with no distractionsjust simple, fun chess for everyone. Start playing today!', 'Use your mouse or swipe with your finger to control the action', 'Boardgames,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6c943823fcb94f53a8a0c51f796736aa-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6c943823fcb94f53a8a0c51f796736aa-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6c943823fcb94f53a8a0c51f796736aa/', '1280', '768', 'chess,logic,thinking,2players,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, '2-player-online-chess', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6c943823fcb94f53a8a0c51f796736aa-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6c943823fcb94f53a8a0c51f796736aa-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(530, '2025-04-19', 'Tsunami Race', 'Have you ever faced the thrill of escaping a giant tsunami? In this action-packed game, youll choose from a variety of unique characters and race to stay ahead of your opponents. The game offers three exciting modes: outrun a tsunami in Tsunami Race, dodge flying fruits in Fruit Run, and slide to glory in Water Slidesknocking down opponents and collecting boosters along the way. Only the fastest and most strategic players will emerge as champions!', 'Tap and Hold on the screen to move character', '.IO,Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2e2d22d1aa92421397c32b1802be416d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2e2d22d1aa92421397c32b1802be416d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2e2d22d1aa92421397c32b1802be416d/', '800', '600', 'challenge,competition,platformer,parkour,roblox,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'tsunami-race', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2e2d22d1aa92421397c32b1802be416d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2e2d22d1aa92421397c32b1802be416d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(531, '2025-04-19', 'Battle Of Tank Steel', 'Are you ready to enter the world of tank battles? In Battle of Tank Steel, youll drive powerful tanks into intense battles. Experience endless action and shooting fun! This game puts you on a battlefield filled with challenges and strategy. You can unblock various types of tanks, each with unique capabilities and weapons.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Adventure,Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/11c672f8740c44438e35fe75f7078129-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/11c672f8740c44438e35fe75f7078129-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/11c672f8740c44438e35fe75f7078129/', '1334', '750', 'shoot-em-up,tank,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'battle-of-tank-steel', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/11c672f8740c44438e35fe75f7078129-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/11c672f8740c44438e35fe75f7078129-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(532, '2025-04-19', 'Dirty Money The Rich Get Rich', 'Dirty Money: The Rich Get Rich is a money clicker relaxation game. You are permitted to make money by tapping. When you earn some money and level up on the corresponding level, you can speed up by upgrading in the Growth, using the Invest, and making the Assets. The more money you make, the more functions you can unlock and use. I hope you will complete the target and make 100 million!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8673fbf6ca0443d594e1930c36d20235-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8673fbf6ca0443d594e1930c36d20235-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8673fbf6ca0443d594e1930c36d20235/', '750', '1334', 'clicker,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'dirty-money-the-rich-get-rich', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8673fbf6ca0443d594e1930c36d20235-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8673fbf6ca0443d594e1930c36d20235-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(533, '2025-04-19', 'Hero Tower Wars Merge Puzzle', 'Join the exciting world of Hero Tower Wars - Merge Puzzle! Here is filled with tower defense strategy and merging games. Being careful of strategy and quick thinking are important. You\'ll play as a brave hero, battling enemies in layers of towers by mergers and digital strategies. Each tower has a different number of enemies. Use every number and a stronger sword to defeat enemies. ', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4d3b78ee36534ab68ec5ef9f26733fcf-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4d3b78ee36534ab68ec5ef9f26733fcf-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4d3b78ee36534ab68ec5ef9f26733fcf/', '720', '1280', 'defence,real-time-strategy,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'hero-tower-wars-merge-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4d3b78ee36534ab68ec5ef9f26733fcf-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4d3b78ee36534ab68ec5ef9f26733fcf-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(534, '2025-04-19', 'Hard Rock Zombie Truck', 'We ride on the roof of a truck, shoot, blow up and crush zombies!\nThis is a 2D shooter where you need to destroy crowds of zombies and monsters by shooting, crushing and exploding them. At the same time, it is necessary to save living people. We also upgrade our weapons and abilities! Lots of funny sounds, lots of blood (cartoonish!!!) and humor.', '(WASD + mouse) or (Virtual joystick) A/D - drive slower/faster, S - grenade, W - air support, Spacebar - rocket engine, Mouse - shoot.', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/00de367efb50493a83540a70c5a55763-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/00de367efb50493a83540a70c5a55763-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/00de367efb50493a83540a70c5a55763/', '800', '600', '2d,monster,zombie,activity', 0, 0, 0, 'hard-rock-zombie-truck', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/00de367efb50493a83540a70c5a55763-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/00de367efb50493a83540a70c5a55763-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(535, '2025-04-19', 'Hide And Seek Blue Monster', 'Enter a world full of mystery and fun. In Hide And Seek: Blue Monster, you will experience a unique hide-and-seek adventure. The game combines casual games with puzzle challenges. You should keep running away to prevent being caught by the blue monster, and when the blue monster is staring at you, hold stop in front of the fruit, in front of the coke, or front of the water glass, etc. ', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/36f5e684800144bfb35f1d8a2c28fb09-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/36f5e684800144bfb35f1d8a2c28fb09-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/36f5e684800144bfb35f1d8a2c28fb09/', '640', '1334', 'running,hide,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'hide-and-seek-blue-monster', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/36f5e684800144bfb35f1d8a2c28fb09-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/36f5e684800144bfb35f1d8a2c28fb09-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(536, '2025-04-19', 'Build A Rich Queen', 'Make the most accurate choice and become the most beautiful queen! In Build A Rich Queen, you will bring your credit card. When you encounter a POS machine on the road, you can directly swipe the card to buy clothes and other decorations. These decorations will allow you to pass obstacles without directly failing the game, but you will lose these decorations. But pay attention to the road under your feet, don\'t fall suddenly, otherwise, you will directly fail the game. ', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7d24956868024368a690e26822b75dc5-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7d24956868024368a690e26822b75dc5-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/7d24956868024368a690e26822b75dc5/', '750', '1334', 'parkour,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'build-a-rich-queen', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7d24956868024368a690e26822b75dc5-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7d24956868024368a690e26822b75dc5-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(537, '2025-04-19', 'Block Puzzle Travel', 'The goal of the game is to destroy as many blocks as possible. By doing so, you will earn points for completing the game perfectly.\nBy solving puzzles, you train your attention, thought processes and brain.\nIn this game you have to achieve the maximum result, and pass all levels.', 'Destroy diamond blocks, earn points, pass level after level until you pass the game completely. The more blocks destroyed in one turn, the more points the player gets.\n', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9bb63ed68fb248299c4b8d22c814ef1e-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9bb63ed68fb248299c4b8d22c814ef1e-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9bb63ed68fb248299c4b8d22c814ef1e/', '800', '600', 'cute,logic,tetris,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'block-puzzle-travel', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9bb63ed68fb248299c4b8d22c814ef1e-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9bb63ed68fb248299c4b8d22c814ef1e-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(538, '2025-04-19', 'Perfect Piano Magic', 'Perfect Piano Magic is a fun casual game. If you are a big fan of Piano Magic games, then this is a game you can\'t afford to miss! The gameplay of this game is extremely similar to Piano Magic, you need to shoot the blocks with a gun to capture the beat. You have three chances per game, start now and feel the real music when you click the blocks, enjoy the beats, and get ready to experience the delightful music and become a rhythm master!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Shooter,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1de0e17bc5374b849c7ac01581d6189d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1de0e17bc5374b849c7ac01581d6189d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1de0e17bc5374b849c7ac01581d6189d/', '750', '1334', '1player', 0, 0, 0, 'perfect-piano-magic', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1de0e17bc5374b849c7ac01581d6189d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1de0e17bc5374b849c7ac01581d6189d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(539, '2025-04-19', 'Horror Minecraft Partytime', 'Horror Minecraft Partytime is a spooky and interesting horror survival game. This time you will enter a familiar world of blocks. In this hide-and-seek mode, you will be the pursuer, looking for every corner. Find the weirdo in disguise and catch him.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3c2a5af31a50409da0e7df5742fcf05b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3c2a5af31a50409da0e7df5742fcf05b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3c2a5af31a50409da0e7df5742fcf05b/', '1336', '540', 'horror,survival,hide,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'horror-minecraft-partytime', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3c2a5af31a50409da0e7df5742fcf05b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3c2a5af31a50409da0e7df5742fcf05b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(540, '2025-04-19', 'Emoji Smasher - Smiley Game', 'Emoji Smasher is a Hyper Casual game to make you smile while playing!\nGuess the emoticon expressions in this fast-paced challenge! Tap on emojis and win this lively, emoji-filled adventure.', 'Tap on the Sad and Angry Smileys and make them happy. One-tap easy-to-play with stunning visual effects and addictive game-play mechanics.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/949529aaea9841cf8f410b19e6d71619-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/949529aaea9841cf8f410b19e6d71619-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/949529aaea9841cf8f410b19e6d71619/', '540', '960', 'angry,cute,smash,kidgames,emojis,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'emoji-smasher-smiley-game', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/949529aaea9841cf8f410b19e6d71619-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/949529aaea9841cf8f410b19e6d71619-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(541, '2025-04-19', 'Robocarpoli', 'In Brooms Town, you must solve four amazing adventures:\n\nProblems with the pipes: \nIn Brooms Town, a water pipe broke and the road is getting flooded. Help the Rescue Team to solve these situations completing 6 games: \n     Connect the wires in Jins invention\n     Block the water leaks as soon as possible.\n     Solve Polis maze.\n     Work in a team with Micky.\n     Help Roy with the hoses.\n     Make Bruner as clean as a whistle.', 'Follow the instructions given to finish the adventure', 'Adventure,Educational', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8a6c8e55d57941b99a3a6f2f5ce946c8-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8a6c8e55d57941b99a3a6f2f5ce946c8-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8a6c8e55d57941b99a3a6f2f5ce946c8/', '1920', '1080', 'kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'robocarpoli', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8a6c8e55d57941b99a3a6f2f5ce946c8-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8a6c8e55d57941b99a3a6f2f5ce946c8-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
