(599, '2025-04-19', 'Among Squid Challenge Online', 'All players, get ready. They are hiding in a maze. To win the game, you must defeat all the other players. You have a knife and must defeat everyone. Catch the players one by one and make sure they are eliminated. Dont worry, they wont find you. If they try to find you, hide in the ventilation holes. Defeat all the players. Be careful, and whatever you do, don\'t reveal yourself. If they catch you, you will lose and they will defeat you.', '*Use the \"Arrow keys\" to move.\n*The game is playable on both mobile and PC.\n*Press the \"Space\" key to kill players.\n*Use the buttons to hide and view the map.', 'Battle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d145682158474d24a68759c6a8d668cf-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d145682158474d24a68759c6a8d668cf-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d145682158474d24a68759c6a8d668cf/', '800', '600', '2d,battleroyale,amongus,arcade,squidgame,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'among-squid-challenge-online', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d145682158474d24a68759c6a8d668cf-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d145682158474d24a68759c6a8d668cf-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(600, '2025-04-19', '8 Ball Billiards Classic', 'Train your billiard skills and play against the computer or your friend in this 8-ball Pool sports game! Select a difficulty that matches your abilities and start pocketing the balls. The higher the difficulty, the higher the bonus points you receive when you win a match.', 'Aim carefully and use the zoom to adjust the spin of the cue ball. Drag the billiard cue to control the power and try to earn as many points as possible! ', 'Agility,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/226fcd551eac4a0889d5cd18ab627674-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/226fcd551eac4a0889d5cd18ab627674-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/226fcd551eac4a0889d5cd18ab627674/', '800', '600', '1player,2players,multiplayer,singleplayer,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, '8-ball-billiards-classic', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/226fcd551eac4a0889d5cd18ab627674-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/226fcd551eac4a0889d5cd18ab627674-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(601, '2025-04-19', 'Block Blasty Saga', 'Place the blocks on the board and crush them all! Complete the lines with the various block shapes and blast them all! Get ready to become the block master!\n\nPlay the game in two modes: classic way and adventure mode. Try to achieve the highest score in Classic mode by blasting the most block amount, it is an infinite game mode and increases the fun with ASMR sounds. In Adventure mode, complete the tens of chapters and improve your block-crushing skills step by step. Join the saga now!', 'Use MOUSE and LEFT-CLICK to drag and drop the blocks.\n\nUse touch controls on mobile devices/tablets.', 'Boardgames', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b8baa6d9a89046aaac921582683597b7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b8baa6d9a89046aaac921582683597b7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b8baa6d9a89046aaac921582683597b7/', '600', '900', 'block,colorful,crush,tetris,blast,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'block-blasty-saga', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b8baa6d9a89046aaac921582683597b7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b8baa6d9a89046aaac921582683597b7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(602, '2025-04-19', 'Wonders of Egypt Mahjong', 'Wonders of Egypt Mahjong transports you to the mystical world of Ancient Egypt in this brand-new Solitaire Mahjong game. Play through beautifully designed hand-drawn tiles featuring Egyptian motifs and captivating backgrounds inspired by the wonders of Egypt. With 40 unique new layouts and three smaller tutorial layouts, its perfect for both beginners and Mahjong experts. Dive into hours of challenging gameplay and uncover the secrets of the Pharaohs!', 'Find and match identical tiles, making sure theyre free on at least one side to remove them from the board. Clear all tiles to complete each layout and unveil the mysteries of Egypt! Use Shuffle, Torch, or Hint if youre stuck, and earn stars as you progress through endless puzzles. Relax and enjoy the beauty of Ancient Egypt in this captivating Solitaire Mahjong journey!', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e07f57a52e994a4c802e595bc77a788c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e07f57a52e994a4c802e595bc77a788c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e07f57a52e994a4c802e595bc77a788c/', '800', '600', 'board,egypt,tiles,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'wonders-of-egypt-mahjong', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e07f57a52e994a4c802e595bc77a788c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e07f57a52e994a4c802e595bc77a788c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(603, '2025-04-19', 'Carnage Battle Arena', 'Get Carnage now and discover a new kind of racing game! Driving fast and getting to the finish line is only one of the multiple challenges that await you. Wreak havoc on the streets thanks to the extensive destruction model that lets you not only damage vehicles, but also cause visible changes in the environment. After a long battle, the location will look nothing like it used to at the start!\n\nWhichever mode you choose, get ready for loads of adrenaline-pumping action! Play Carnage now!', 'Use mouse and keyboard for controls. Gamepad controllers supported on Chrome browser.', 'Racing & Driving,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/50d128ddf56542d3a53589121fff975e-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/50d128ddf56542d3a53589121fff975e-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/50d128ddf56542d3a53589121fff975e/', '1920', '1080', 'car,challenge,drift,stunts,combat,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'carnage-battle-arena', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/50d128ddf56542d3a53589121fff975e-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/50d128ddf56542d3a53589121fff975e-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(604, '2025-04-19', 'Jewel Miner Quest', 'The dazzling world of gems awaits! Participate in thrilling events within limited moves or time. Solve captivating puzzles, complete fun tasks, and enjoy daily bonuses. Discover many terrific surprises with every move and see how far you can go.\n', 'The game features limitless match-3 levels. Players connect three or more jewels to clear levels and progress. Four unique boosters help overcome challenges. Daily login rewards, the Lucky Wheel, and special tasks offer opportunities to earn prizes and enhance the gameplay experience.\n', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/913789b18a784d2e8fe991880a0ec5c0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/913789b18a784d2e8fe991880a0ec5c0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/913789b18a784d2e8fe991880a0ec5c0/', '800', '600', 'combine,logic,matching,quest,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'jewel-miner-quest', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/913789b18a784d2e8fe991880a0ec5c0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/913789b18a784d2e8fe991880a0ec5c0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(605, '2025-04-19', 'Tower Crash 3D', 'Crash the Tower! Only the best crashers will be able to destroy all towers in this 3D physics game.Try to let all towers collapse with the amount of given balls. But you will only destroy the shapes with the same colour as you ball. Use the powerful earthquake or shotgun power ups, to create huge chain reactions, which will lead into the towers destruction. Beautiful designed levels and shapes will await you, so dont waste any second and become the greatest tower crasher of em all!', 'Shoot the blocks of the tower with balls that match them in color. Try to destroy as many blocks as you can at the same time to get combos!', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b375b05ea29b40abaaf3606a2ff215ad-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b375b05ea29b40abaaf3606a2ff215ad-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b375b05ea29b40abaaf3606a2ff215ad/', '800', '600', '1player,aim,tower,colormatch,singleplayer,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'tower-crash-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b375b05ea29b40abaaf3606a2ff215ad-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b375b05ea29b40abaaf3606a2ff215ad-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
