(792, '2025-04-19', 'Horror Forest Bear', 'Imagine an angry bear that has escaped from its cave in the forest. It\'s very hungry and wants to eat honey. You must help the bear. The bear is starving, and it needs to eat all the honey. You need to be very carefulit\'s a dark and dangerous forest, full of traps and hunters. The hunters have become much stronger because they can shoot with guns now. You must avoid the hunters. Escape from them, collect all the honey, and return to the bear\'s cave.', 'Use the \"WASD\" keys to move.\nPlayable on both mobile and PC.\nDouble jump is available.\nEat all the honey, avoid the hunters, and safely return to the cave.', 'Agility,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8622c7f82e7a41bd9eaaf64c9caa46df-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8622c7f82e7a41bd9eaaf64c9caa46df-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8622c7f82e7a41bd9eaaf64c9caa46df/', '800', '600', '1player,2d,animal,minecraft,pixel,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'horror-forest-bear', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8622c7f82e7a41bd9eaaf64c9caa46df-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8622c7f82e7a41bd9eaaf64c9caa46df-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(793, '2025-04-19', 'Kick and Ride', 'Kick and Ride is a physics-based puzzle game consisting of two game modes. Drag and drop the block to make path for the soccer as well as for the vehicle. Enjoy the vibrant and colorful beach themed game.', 'Follow In Game Instructions.', 'Puzzle,Sports', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9429a58f3cd64d87beb7120477bba3c1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9429a58f3cd64d87beb7120477bba3c1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9429a58f3cd64d87beb7120477bba3c1/', '1280', '720', 'logic,penalty,physics,sport,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'kick-and-ride', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9429a58f3cd64d87beb7120477bba3c1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9429a58f3cd64d87beb7120477bba3c1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(794, '2025-04-19', 'Word Mine', 'Word Mine takes you on a thrilling journey where letters are your treasure! Dive into a world of scrambled chaos and uncover hidden words buried in the grid. With every move, youll strike gold, revealing secrets that push you closer to victory. Sharpen your mind, follow the clues, and let the adventure unfoldone word at a time!', '1.Rearrange Letters:\nDrag and drop the scrambled letters on the grid to form meaningful words.\n2.Follow Color Hints:\nGreen Tile: The letter is in the correct position.\nYellow Tile: The letter is in the correct row or column but not the exact spot.\nWhite Tile: The letter is in the wrong position entirely.\n3. Find All Words:\nEach level has a set of valid words hidden in the grid.\n4. Unlock New Levels:\nProgress through increasingly challenging puzzles, with more complex grids.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b0cc3d7cdae0458eb371d8665eb31b8f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b0cc3d7cdae0458eb371d8665eb31b8f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b0cc3d7cdae0458eb371d8665eb31b8f/', '1080', '1920', 'wordsearch,crossword,wordscapes,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'word-mine', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b0cc3d7cdae0458eb371d8665eb31b8f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b0cc3d7cdae0458eb371d8665eb31b8f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(795, '2025-04-19', 'Christmas Candy Escape 3D', 'Christmas Candy Escape 3D is a casual puzzle in which you have to fall safely. It is deceptively simple, yet profoundly deep. Play through the extensive stages, sharpening your wits as you have fun. Have a try!', 'Slide to move', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9512252809e54926ac54f092ce6b52cd-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9512252809e54926ac54f092ce6b52cd-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9512252809e54926ac54f092ce6b52cd/', '750', '1334', 'candy,christmas,collect,escape', 0, 0, 0, 'christmas-candy-escape-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9512252809e54926ac54f092ce6b52cd-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9512252809e54926ac54f092ce6b52cd-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(796, '2025-04-19', 'Gun Racing', 'Here you cannot just race with other cars, but destroy them with the help of numerous weapons. Improve your riding skills and take first places in tournaments!', 'Pass the skill test levels and unlock new content!\n\nFor completing a level you are given money and tickets, for which you can buy and improve weapons and cars.\nFor completing the grand tournament and timed battles, increased rewards are given out!\nAlso, for completing the game, experience is awarded, which unlocks bonuses in the seasons. For 25 experience levels you are guaranteed to get a new car!', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f1d26823646c4078a6db03221f8e05d1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f1d26823646c4078a6db03221f8e05d1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f1d26823646c4078a6db03221f8e05d1/', '800', '600', '3d,boys,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'gun-racing', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f1d26823646c4078a6db03221f8e05d1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f1d26823646c4078a6db03221f8e05d1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(797, '2025-04-19', 'Archery Ragdoll', 'Embark on an adrenaline-pumping adventure in this action-packed online game featuring thrilling ragdoll archer physics. Master the art of archery and prove your prowess!', 'Control the archer using the mouse or by touching the screen on the left highlighted part of the screen. Hold the mouse (finger) behind the archer\'s back to draw the bow (no need to pull it horizontally). Keeping the bow drawn, aim and release.', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1ebba0a58564412f9a6be21511f86b48-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1ebba0a58564412f9a6be21511f86b48-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1ebba0a58564412f9a6be21511f86b48/', '800', '600', 'archery,christmas,fighting,ragdoll,winter', 0, 0, 0, 'archery-ragdoll', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1ebba0a58564412f9a6be21511f86b48-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1ebba0a58564412f9a6be21511f86b48-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(798, '2025-04-19', 'Spaceflight Simulator', 'Do you have a space dream? Spaceflight Simulator is a challenging spaceflight simulation game suitable for boys who love to build and launch rockets. The game has real-life conditions in space.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/59e9362f0f9f4bb4b94ab698bf0a557a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/59e9362f0f9f4bb4b94ab698bf0a557a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/59e9362f0f9f4bb4b94ab698bf0a557a/', '750', '1334', 'space,boys,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'spaceflight-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/59e9362f0f9f4bb4b94ab698bf0a557a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/59e9362f0f9f4bb4b94ab698bf0a557a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(799, '2025-04-19', 'Merge TikTok Gravity Knife', 'This is an addictive elimination merge puzzle game. If you like synthetic elimination games, then this game is for you. They can remove a portion of the weapons that didn\'t merge, but there\'s only one free shot. Be careful, you have to score as many points as possible within the time limit, otherwise, you will have to start another game. Now join the challenging world of the game.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4aba6c4801684d8aa1e8d5f32ad9b936-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4aba6c4801684d8aa1e8d5f32ad9b936-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4aba6c4801684d8aa1e8d5f32ad9b936/', '720', '1280', 'sliding-puzzle,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'merge-tiktok-gravity-knife', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4aba6c4801684d8aa1e8d5f32ad9b936-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4aba6c4801684d8aa1e8d5f32ad9b936-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(800, '2025-04-19', 'Cars Merge', 'Feel the thrill as racing cars zoom by at lightning speed on the track!\n\nGet your hands on these incredible cars and watch them blaze across the raceway. Show off your passion for speed and excitement by collecting them all!\n\nHow many will you collect? Play now and find out!', 'Use coins to purchase a car. Tap and drag the cars together to create a more flashy car. Continue merging cars to discover new, more exciting cars. Cars on the race track will start gathering coins for you as time passes.  ', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6124b63ea76a4c7bb77c2fa500286b5f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6124b63ea76a4c7bb77c2fa500286b5f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6124b63ea76a4c7bb77c2fa500286b5f/', '1080', '1920', 'car,idle,track,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cars-merge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6124b63ea76a4c7bb77c2fa500286b5f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6124b63ea76a4c7bb77c2fa500286b5f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(801, '2025-04-19', 'Pengu Slide', 'Join our cute penguin hero on a ride down the icy slopes. With an avalanche hot on your tail, it\'s up to you to skillfully navigate the terrain by sliding, jumping and flying your way to safety. Experience heart-pumping excitement as you collect fish, and booster while trying to outrun the avalanche. With easy controls and addictive gameplay, Pengu Slide is the perfect game for players of all ages. Strap on your snow boots and join the adventure in Pengu Slide - the coolest game on the block!', 'Slide to survive and fly to thrive in Pengu Slide - the ultimate penguin adventure game!', 'Agility,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bf4aeb8dd4d44f6e850b72419cebc575-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bf4aeb8dd4d44f6e850b72419cebc575-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bf4aeb8dd4d44f6e850b72419cebc575/', '800', '600', 'animal,cute,slide,snow,speed,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'pengu-slide', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bf4aeb8dd4d44f6e850b72419cebc575-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bf4aeb8dd4d44f6e850b72419cebc575-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(802, '2025-04-19', 'Cannon Balls 3D', 'Try to be the master of destruction, heat up the buildings neatly and show no mercy! In \'Cannon Balls 3D\' it depends on how skillfully you place the shots so that the structures collapse as efficiently as possible. Watch your ammo, because it\'s limited. But don\'t worry. There will also come a time when you will bring the cannon to the edge of functionality. Especially when the great bombs are used. So what are you waiting for?', 'Destroy the given structures and use your limited ammunition supply as efficiently as possible!', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8839fa09044843dc8e4f8db901ffa369-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8839fa09044843dc8e4f8db901ffa369-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8839fa09044843dc8e4f8db901ffa369/', '800', '600', 'ball,cannon,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cannon-balls-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8839fa09044843dc8e4f8db901ffa369-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8839fa09044843dc8e4f8db901ffa369-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(803, '2025-04-19', 'Crazy Hen', 'Bring the Hen through endless amounts of levels in Crazy Hen! Be crazy and try to reach your chicks in this crazy adventure. With an endless amount of levels, it will only get crazier! But don\'t worry if you get hit, you can always revive! So get this Crazy Hen across the Road and get as much score as possible!', 'Tap to make the hen move one step forward and avoid obstacles like cars, trains, and more! When you tap consecutive you will eventually get into Fire Mode for 3 Seconds. In that mode, you are invincible, so tap as fast as you can in those 3 seconds.', 'Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/953b033dd4814daa8498d57d3fd2c4d6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/953b033dd4814daa8498d57d3fd2c4d6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/953b033dd4814daa8498d57d3fd2c4d6/', '800', '600', '1player,animal,colorful,speed,timing,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'crazy-hen', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/953b033dd4814daa8498d57d3fd2c4d6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/953b033dd4814daa8498d57d3fd2c4d6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(804, '2025-04-19', 'Stick Boy: Bazooka Ragdoll', 'Unleash chaos in Stick Boy: Bazooka War! Blast through levels with a variety of powerful bazookas, each with unique abilities. Obliterate enemies, destroy bases, and demolish everything in your path. Choose the perfect ammo to send ragdoll foes flying and experience thrilling destruction as you crush their strongholds. Help Stick Boy annihilate all adversaries and conquer every level in this explosive adventure!', 'Hold down your finger on the screen or press and hold the Left Mouse Button to take aim. Release to fire.', 'Shooter,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0c93ae8fb4eb4604b6e3d0d5ea5eb449-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0c93ae8fb4eb4604b6e3d0d5ea5eb449-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0c93ae8fb4eb4604b6e3d0d5ea5eb449/', '800', '600', 'explosion,ragdoll,war,stickman', 0, 0, 0, 'stick-boy-bazooka-ragdoll', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0c93ae8fb4eb4604b6e3d0d5ea5eb449-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0c93ae8fb4eb4604b6e3d0d5ea5eb449-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(805, '2025-04-19', 'Day of Atrocity', 'Day of Atrocity is a voxel action game where you play as the hero, battling a relentless swarm of enemies that spawn at an increasing pace. Your objective is to stop them from overtaking the map by wiping them out before they dominate the entire space.', 'Controls: Control movement with WASD keys\nDash with L key\nAttack with O and P keys\nTab key to change character', 'Battle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5a0d2c83bf7f4ed9b3b4b06670e31f95-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5a0d2c83bf7f4ed9b3b4b06670e31f95-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5a0d2c83bf7f4ed9b3b4b06670e31f95/', '800', '600', 'endless,survival,battlefield,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'day-of-atrocity', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5a0d2c83bf7f4ed9b3b4b06670e31f95-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5a0d2c83bf7f4ed9b3b4b06670e31f95-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(806, '2025-04-19', 'Geometry Arrow', 'Dive into an exhilarating journey through a treacherous cave! Your mission: reach the portal at the end of each level while avoiding deadly spikes and obstacles. With six progressively harder levels, youll need sharp reflexes and spot-on timing to survive. Can you conquer every challenge and make it out of the cave? Put your skills to the test in this high-speed action game!', 'PC controls:\nLEFT MOUSE BUTTON or SPACEBAR  arrow movement\n\nMOBILE controls:\nTOUCHING THE SCREEN  arrow movement', 'Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9ee26ba4405c456094c70af7dc31a524-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9ee26ba4405c456094c70af7dc31a524-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9ee26ba4405c456094c70af7dc31a524/', '800', '600', 'dash,geometry,platformer,music,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'geometry-arrow', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9ee26ba4405c456094c70af7dc31a524-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9ee26ba4405c456094c70af7dc31a524-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(807, '2025-04-19', 'Zombie Space Episode II', 'There has been an outbreak of a zombie virus on a space station. The first group of mercenaries has disappeared. Your task is to find survivors among the zombies and find out the cause of the zombie apocalypse. You will have to fight with a horde of zombies, using different types of weapons. Look for hidden weapons in chests. Upgrade characters and weapons! Use your characters\' abilities in heated battles against zombies. Play with a friend on the same device or alone!', 'The goal of the game is to destroy all zombies and monsters.\nFind new weapons in the boxes.\nUpgrade characters and weapons to defeat strong enemies.\n\nQ (K) - change weapons;\nW, A, S, D (arrows) - move;\nE (M) - apply / activate;\nF (J) - super weapon.\nLeftCntrl, Space (RightControl, KeyPad 0) - shooting;\nMouse - look / shoot;\nFor mobile devices, use touch input.', 'Shooter,Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e32d46008d7846578887c08660b7382f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e32d46008d7846578887c08660b7382f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e32d46008d7846578887c08660b7382f/', '800', '600', 'fighting,space,survival,zombie', 0, 0, 0, 'zombie-space-episode-ii', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e32d46008d7846578887c08660b7382f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e32d46008d7846578887c08660b7382f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(808, '2025-04-19', 'Cosmo Puzzle', 'Cosmo Puzzle is a colorful puzzle game about a robot who dreams of collecting a collection of minerals from all over the Solar System.', 'Collect pictures by rotating and swapping puzzle pieces. Use hints if you are confused. New levels become available as you progress through the story.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/95c294b7d2ba48f380e96c6c77478fb0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/95c294b7d2ba48f380e96c6c77478fb0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/95c294b7d2ba48f380e96c6c77478fb0/', '800', '600', 'matching,robot,space,sliding-puzzle,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cosmo-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/95c294b7d2ba48f380e96c6c77478fb0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/95c294b7d2ba48f380e96c6c77478fb0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(809, '2025-04-19', 'Donut Run', 'This thrilling arcade game is designed for adventure enthusiasts and fans of active gameplay. Step into the role of a fearless rolling character, racing through dynamic levels filled with vibrant settings and exhilarating obstacles. With easy-to-master controls, youll quickly dive into the action, experiencing a blend of tension and adrenaline. Each level features diverse obstacles and traps, ensuring every run feels fresh and exciting.', 'Controls for computer:\n\n-Left mouse button - move forward\n- Right mouse button - move backward\n\nControls for phone:\n\n- Right side of the screen - move forward\n- Left side of the screen - move backward', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ada0802bb30d4baf85d2004865724077-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ada0802bb30d4baf85d2004865724077-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ada0802bb30d4baf85d2004865724077/', '800', '600', 'challenge,donuts,obstacles,runner,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'donut-run', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ada0802bb30d4baf85d2004865724077-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ada0802bb30d4baf85d2004865724077-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(810, '2025-04-19', 'Cube in Cube', 'Play the new 2048 game with unique mechanics! Develop strategies to clear cubes in endless mode or rescue the monkey. Challenge yourself now!', 'Click on any cube and then on the same cube next to it. The cubes will connect into a cube of the best level. Save the monkey or just get into the top of the best.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/247c60b9f2de4f33bc010f5cddf627a3-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/247c60b9f2de4f33bc010f5cddf627a3-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/247c60b9f2de4f33bc010f5cddf627a3/', '800', '600', 'challenge,logic,2048,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cube-in-cube', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/247c60b9f2de4f33bc010f5cddf627a3-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/247c60b9f2de4f33bc010f5cddf627a3-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(811, '2025-04-19', 'Mushroom blocks', 'Meet colorful and diverse mushrooms! Collect mushroom blocks, earn points and win the rankings! On the way you will encounter all kinds of obstacles: lightning, bombs, frozen cells and others. Try to overcome all obstacles and hold out as long as possible, plunging into the cozy atmosphere of mushroom picking, accompanied by pleasant music!', 'Move the blocks with your finger or mouse. The row will be destroyed if all the cells in it are filled. Use boosters to make it easier to play, and also keep a close eye on the special mushroom blocks! You will lose if the blocks reach the topmost row.\n\nHave a good game!', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/709143e7f3074904802f64cd5f3be910-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/709143e7f3074904802f64cd5f3be910-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/709143e7f3074904802f64cd5f3be910/', '800', '600', 'block,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'mushroom-blocks', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/709143e7f3074904802f64cd5f3be910-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/709143e7f3074904802f64cd5f3be910-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(812, '2025-04-19', 'Pursuit Rampage', 'In Pursuit Rampage, youre behind the wheel of a police car in an endless, high-speed chase. Navigate through busy streets, dodge obstacles, and close in on criminals while keeping your cool under pressure. The game constantly pushes your reflexes to the limit, with each second offering a new challenge. Whether you\'re weaving through traffic or speeding down back alleys, the action never lets up. ', 'WASD/Arrow to Drive\nH for Horn \nC for Camera', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/17dd3831198c42d29feb07c6313d3838-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/17dd3831198c42d29feb07c6313d3838-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/17dd3831198c42d29feb07c6313d3838/', '960', '640', '1player,endless,police,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'pursuit-rampage', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/17dd3831198c42d29feb07c6313d3838-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/17dd3831198c42d29feb07c6313d3838-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(813, '2025-04-19', 'Stickman Halloween Survive', 'Now that Halloween is here, the gloomiest day of the year, it\'s time to bring back the courageous white stickman who is an expert at vanquishing monsters. Stop procrastinating and start enjoying Stickman Halloween Survive right now on your preferred mobile device. It\'s a fun and free online game. \nEvery living thing on Earth is frightened to death when monsters emerge from their underground lairs on Halloween night.', 'Instructions:\nHelp the stickman aim his weapon at the right time to shoot the monsters located on different mobile platforms.\n\nControls:\n\nUse the mouse to aim and shoot or touch and drag on mobile screens.', 'Adventure,Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f026d2bf0d8a4e72a14d0db48bbd7bf1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f026d2bf0d8a4e72a14d0db48bbd7bf1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f026d2bf0d8a4e72a14d0db48bbd7bf1/', '900', '600', 'guns,halloween,run,stickman,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'stickman-halloween-survive', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f026d2bf0d8a4e72a14d0db48bbd7bf1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f026d2bf0d8a4e72a14d0db48bbd7bf1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(814, '2025-04-19', 'Monster Dash', 'Sprint, Jump and Blast your way through Monster Dash, an action-packed game by the creators of Jetpack Joyride and Fruit Ninja.\n\nJoin Barry Steakfries and his iconic Machine Gun Jetpack in a world full of menacing monster mayhem, as you run and gun your way through hordes of zombies, vampires and more with the most explosive and powerful weapons you can find!', 'Experience the classic game resurrected from the dead! With simple controls, just two buttons, making it easy-to-learn but hard to master.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/04999de1c09c4ec2af0d7f390de7ab03-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/04999de1c09c4ec2af0d7f390de7ab03-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/04999de1c09c4ec2af0d7f390de7ab03/', '800', '600', 'halloween,platformer,run,arcade,singleplayer', 0, 0, 0, 'monster-dash', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/04999de1c09c4ec2af0d7f390de7ab03-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/04999de1c09c4ec2af0d7f390de7ab03-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(815, '2025-04-19', 'Pumpking vs Mummy', 'Are you ready for a competitive game between the mummy and the pumpkin king on Halloween? Yes, someone has to win on Halloween! Team up with a friend and choose to be either the mummy or the pumpkin king. Collect as many flying pumpkins as you can! You can earn money by eating candies, and by gathering all the pumpkins, you can win the game. Catch the balloons and take them to the treasure chest. The one who collects and brings them back the fastest wins.', '*Use the \'WASD\' keys and the \'Arrow Keys\' to move. \n*Playable on both mobile and PC. \n*Four different hats available in the shop. \n*The player who collects 10 pumpkins the fastest wins.', 'Casual,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3613bbd2f9d44ef798718dc2a8972037-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3613bbd2f9d44ef798718dc2a8972037-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3613bbd2f9d44ef798718dc2a8972037/', '800', '600', 'halloween,pixel,2players,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'pumpking-vs-mummy', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3613bbd2f9d44ef798718dc2a8972037-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3613bbd2f9d44ef798718dc2a8972037-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(816, '2025-04-19', 'Shopaholic Black Friday', 'Experience fashion fun like never before with the Shopaholic Black Friday game! Navigate through makeup products, and indulge in chic fashion pieces. Hit the mall, shop as many items as you can before the time runs out, and then return for another styling adventure. Explore an array of lipstick hues, experiment with smoky eyes, or go for colorful shadows, and browse through fashionable dresses, trendy tops, and stylish shoes. Complete the look with dazzling accessories and designer bags.', 'Use your mouse to play this game on desktops or tap to play on mobile devices. ', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/69de81b728dc4781a3ced10950c686ab-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/69de81b728dc4781a3ced10950c686ab-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/69de81b728dc4781a3ced10950c686ab/', '1024', '768', 'dressing,fashion,makeup,shopping,blackfriday,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'shopaholic-black-friday', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/69de81b728dc4781a3ced10950c686ab-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/69de81b728dc4781a3ced10950c686ab-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(817, '2025-04-19', 'Ink Inc Tattoo', 'Ink Inc Tattoo is a free online simulation game for boys played on PuzzleGame. In the game, you can experience the satisfaction of a tattoo artist drawing various artistic tattoos for clients. You need to draw the correct lines and colors to complete the image given by the customer. Mobile, Tablet, and Desktop are playable. Come and get a new entertainment experience.', 'Mouse or tap to play', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/566d727ed5b345169b06a85e0431ea4f-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/566d727ed5b345169b06a85e0431ea4f-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/566d727ed5b345169b06a85e0431ea4f/', '720', '1280', 'coloring,drawing,skill,tattoo,3d,boys,Kids Friendly,No Blood,No Cruelty', 0, 0, 0, 'ink-inc-tattoo', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/566d727ed5b345169b06a85e0431ea4f-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/566d727ed5b345169b06a85e0431ea4f-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(818, '2025-04-19', 'Hidden Objects Bakery', 'Explore 6 charming bakery shops in this fun hidden object game! With 24 exciting levels, find 6 hidden bakery items in each shop before time runs out. Perfect for all ages, enjoy the challenge and discover delicious treats in every corner. Can you find them all before time runs out?', 'Use your mouse or tap the screen to select hidden bakery items scattered throughout the shop. Scroll with your mouse to explore different sections of the shop and discover all the hidden treats.', 'Puzzle,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0c9ec29a395b4801bc9cba1f9b767f37-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0c9ec29a395b4801bc9cba1f9b767f37-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0c9ec29a395b4801bc9cba1f9b767f37/', '1280', '720', 'bakery,food,hidden,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood,point-and-click', 0, 0, 0, 'hidden-objects-bakery', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0c9ec29a395b4801bc9cba1f9b767f37-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0c9ec29a395b4801bc9cba1f9b767f37-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(819, '2025-04-19', 'Color Maze', 'In Color Maze your mission is to light up all the paths on the map to complete a level. Make the right move, avoiding obstacles or just pay attention to not get stuck in a corner. Beat all the 20 levels with increasing difficulty to show yourself that you are the real king of Color Maze.  Remember, if a level is to hard for you, you can always skip it clicking or touching the reward button in the up right corner of the screen.     ', 'WASD or ARROWS to move', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0f294f81b50b4dbfb00a4c30df3573b9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0f294f81b50b4dbfb00a4c30df3573b9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0f294f81b50b4dbfb00a4c30df3573b9/', '1280', '720', '1player,2d,color,maze,arena,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'color-maze', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0f294f81b50b4dbfb00a4c30df3573b9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0f294f81b50b4dbfb00a4c30df3573b9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(820, '2025-04-19', 'Brain Test: One Line Draw Puzzle', 'In this engaging one-line puzzle game, challenge your brain by drawing shapes in a single stroke without lifting your finger. Each level presents a unique shape that must be drawn in one continuous line, testing your logic and creativity. With increasing difficulty, youll need to plan your moves carefully to solve each puzzle. Perfect for players of all ages, this game offers hours of fun while improving problem-solving skills. Can you master the art of drawing each shape in one go?', '1-Tap and hold to start drawing.\n2-Draw the shape in one continuous line.\n3-Do not lift your finger until the shape is complete.\n4-If you make a mistake, restart and try again.\n5-Complete each level by finishing the shape in one stroke.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/65f1c84c76324e198314706dedd4aa09-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/65f1c84c76324e198314706dedd4aa09-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/65f1c84c76324e198314706dedd4aa09/', '1920', '1080', 'drawing,maze,painting,school,kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'brain-test-one-line-draw-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/65f1c84c76324e198314706dedd4aa09-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/65f1c84c76324e198314706dedd4aa09-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(821, '2025-04-19', 'Overprotective Boyfriend', 'Imagine the beautiful Princess Marie standing in front of a mirror, looking at her reflection. Her eyes are shining, and a sly smile plays on her lips. She is ready to put on an outfit that will emphasize her grace and charm. But then her lover appears and frowns: My dear, are you really going to wear such an open dress? Marie knows that her faithful knight sometimes takes too much care of her, but today she intends to look dazzling!', 'Help Princess Marie create a bright and daring outfit, but do not quarrel with her jealous lover. Combine bold challenge and quiet modesty in a single fashionable look! The result can be saved as a PNG image. Depending on the gaming device, a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touch screens is used to control it.', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/42b044e1138b4d0ab06a540c153023ef-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/42b044e1138b4d0ab06a540c153023ef-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/42b044e1138b4d0ab06a540c153023ef/', '800', '600', 'boyfriend,dress,hairstyle,makeup,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'overprotective-boyfriend', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/42b044e1138b4d0ab06a540c153023ef-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/42b044e1138b4d0ab06a540c153023ef-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(822, '2025-04-19', 'Ball Dunk Fall', 'In Ball Dunk Fall, your challenge is to guide a constantly falling ball through hoops of varying difficulties by tapping the screen. Test your precision and reflexes as you navigate through tricky obstacles. With each successful dunk, experience the thrill of victory and aim for high scores!\n', 'Objective: Pass the ball through as many hoops as possible while avoiding obstacles.\n\nControls: Tap the screen to control the ball\'s direction as it falls.\n\nGameplay: Time your taps to aim for the hoops.\nAvoid falling out of bounds and hitting obstacles to keep the game going.', 'Football,Basketball', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1f6162f5ac0541cca72f77a833acde86-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1f6162f5ac0541cca72f77a833acde86-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1f6162f5ac0541cca72f77a833acde86/', '800', '600', '1player,ball,basket,fall,dunk,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'ball-dunk-fall', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1f6162f5ac0541cca72f77a833acde86-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1f6162f5ac0541cca72f77a833acde86-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(823, '2025-04-19', 'Cute Sheep SkyBlock', 'Two cute sheep must jump from island to island in the sky to escape from the farmers and reach the portal. They need to work together as a team to overcome obstacles. You must help them. Be careful of the obstacles that fall from the ground and sky. The farmers are looking for you, and they want to catch you, so jump over them to escape. If the path is clear, eat all the hay you find. Gather all the hay and safely reach the portal.', '*Move using the \"WASD\" keys and \"Arrow Keys.\" \n*You can jump twice in a row. \n*Safely guide both sheep to the portal. \n*Playable on both mobile and PC.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/856fcda2826d449bae34cc9d3efe90ce-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/856fcda2826d449bae34cc9d3efe90ce-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/856fcda2826d449bae34cc9d3efe90ce/', '800', '600', 'animal,minecraft,2players,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cute-sheep-skyblock', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/856fcda2826d449bae34cc9d3efe90ce-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/856fcda2826d449bae34cc9d3efe90ce-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(824, '2025-04-19', 'Block Craft 3d', 'Block Craft 3D is a first-person RPG game with 3D pixel Minecraft models. Starting from a block base, you can attack the monsters outside to claim diamonds with weapons. I strongly suggest you build bombs to destroy terrains or build blocks to make yourself safe. When you earn enough diamonds, you can unlock and use 4 Melee weapons, 11 guns, and 8 bombs in the store. Glad you will have a good time in this block world.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dea0d13d63fb4eb1b8c1b8971fe75635-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dea0d13d63fb4eb1b8c1b8971fe75635-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/dea0d13d63fb4eb1b8c1b8971fe75635/', '1920', '1080', 'minecraft,rpg,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'block-craft-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dea0d13d63fb4eb1b8c1b8971fe75635-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dea0d13d63fb4eb1b8c1b8971fe75635-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(825, '2025-04-19', 'Bottle challenge', 'This is a puzzle game, the game provides different volumes of the kettle, according to the game level prompts each kettle needs a different magnitude, to reach the required magnitude of the prompt can be cleared', 'The main control of the game is to click on the water bottle to pour water into another water bottle', 'Puzzle,Educational', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a03c94a59c2b4fcb8e3fe862f99f15d6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a03c94a59c2b4fcb8e3fe862f99f15d6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a03c94a59c2b4fcb8e3fe862f99f15d6/', '1080', '1920', '1player', 0, 0, 0, 'bottle-challenge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a03c94a59c2b4fcb8e3fe862f99f15d6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a03c94a59c2b4fcb8e3fe862f99f15d6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(826, '2025-04-19', 'Merge Gun Fps Shooting Zombie', 'Merge Gun: FPS Shooting Zombie\'s main mission is to shoot down all coming undead creatures before they kill you. Before you join the battle, you can buy more guns and merge the same guns into new advanced ones. With more powerful and fast ammo in the clip, you can deal with incoming enemies more easily. Both zombies and crows will move forward to you even if you are still reloading. Keep calm and shoot the explosive oil cans on the ground if necessary.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a299af92e23148ae8cc80731ca3fb229-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a299af92e23148ae8cc80731ca3fb229-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a299af92e23148ae8cc80731ca3fb229/', '720', '1280', 'shoot-em-up,zombie,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'merge-gun-fps-shooting-zombie', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a299af92e23148ae8cc80731ca3fb229-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a299af92e23148ae8cc80731ca3fb229-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(827, '2025-04-19', 'Mobile Phone Case Diy', 'This is a mobile phone case game that was designed. Have you ever wanted to create a fashion phone case of your own? In the game, you can show your creativity, enjoy the art of customisation and see your phone evolve the way you like. You can choose your favourite colours, draw, mix, and spray paint your phone case.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dc2bc449cf124a5b8dc3ed2c8dc0c405-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dc2bc449cf124a5b8dc3ed2c8dc0c405-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/dc2bc449cf124a5b8dc3ed2c8dc0c405/', '504', '800', 'phone,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mobile-phone-case-diy', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dc2bc449cf124a5b8dc3ed2c8dc0c405-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dc2bc449cf124a5b8dc3ed2c8dc0c405-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(828, '2025-04-19', 'Screw Puzzle Master', 'Pull out the nuts and bolts and release the woods. Get ready for a fluent and entertaining screw puzzle! It is time to do some brain practice. Many game levels, entertaining puzzles, and super power-ups await you!  Challenge a friend and complete chapters as fast as you can. Place the bolts as strategically as you can. Buy different skins and play in a different ambient.', 'On desktop devices:\nUse MOUSE and LEFT-CLICK\n\nOn mobile devices:\nUse Touch Controls to interact with the Nuts and Bolts.', 'Boardgames', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2e9883c74b1f4e0f94b507753eb92947-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2e9883c74b1f4e0f94b507753eb92947-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2e9883c74b1f4e0f94b507753eb92947/', '600', '760', '1player,board,challenge,colorful,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'screw-puzzle-master', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2e9883c74b1f4e0f94b507753eb92947-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2e9883c74b1f4e0f94b507753eb92947-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(829, '2025-04-19', 'Texas Holdem Poker', 'Players compete for winning combinations of cards using their skills and intuition. The game has the ability to bet, bluff and recognize the bluff of other players. Players can choose different difficulty levels and customize their own game rules. The unique interface design and realistic atmosphere allow you to immerse yourself in the world of card games and enjoy the excitement anytime and anywhere. ', 'PC control: lmb\nControl on a mobile device: Touch', 'Cards', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a3a72cf8d87b4c2187dfa84046da9ddf-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a3a72cf8d87b4c2187dfa84046da9ddf-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a3a72cf8d87b4c2187dfa84046da9ddf/', '800', '600', 'logic,poker,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'texas-holdem-poker', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a3a72cf8d87b4c2187dfa84046da9ddf-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a3a72cf8d87b4c2187dfa84046da9ddf-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(830, '2025-04-19', 'Royal Bubble Blast', 'Welcome to Royal Bubble Blast, where you\'ll be transported to a majestic castle to enjoy a royal Bubble Shooter experience! Featuring vibrant, handcrafted designs and a colourful, lively theme, this game offers endless, relaxing gameplay accompanied by a beautiful soundtrack. Play as a King or Queen in the most exclusive Bubble Shooter enjoyed by royalty. Dive into a world of colourful bubbles and endless fun. So, what are you waiting for? Join the royals and start popping!', 'The goal of Royal Bubble Blast is to clear the board by matching three or more bubbles of the same colour. Aim using your mouse or finger, then shoot to pop the bubbles. The more you pop in a single shot, the higher your score. Avoid too many misses, as fouls will add a new line of bubbles at the top. Keep the bubbles from reaching the bottom of the screen for as long as you can. Keep popping and enjoy the fast-paced fun!', 'Bubble Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/48583ddbe6f74c5f8a16653b555914e3-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/48583ddbe6f74c5f8a16653b555914e3-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/48583ddbe6f74c5f8a16653b555914e3/', '800', '600', 'bubble,blast,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'royal-bubble-blast', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/48583ddbe6f74c5f8a16653b555914e3-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/48583ddbe6f74c5f8a16653b555914e3-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(831, '2025-04-19', 'Gladiator Fights', 'An action game based on battles with gladiators, where players can plunge into the world of ancient Rome and become real warriors. The game offers an exciting and dynamic gameplay where players have to go through many challenges and defeat a number of dangerous opponents.', 'On mobile devices, the movement of a fighter is controlled by a joystick, attacks are activated by buttons.on the screen\n\nOn a PC, the movement is carried out using the arrows on the keyboard or the WASD keys.\nAttacks are activated by mouse and keyboard buttons:\nA simple attack is the left mouse button or the \"Space\" key.\nPowerful attack - right mouse button or \"Shift\" key (any)\nLong-range attack - right mouse button or \"Shift\" key (any)\nKick - clicking on the mouse wheel or the \"Z\" or \"/\" key', 'Battle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5a1779d9068445689598a76b6412bde3-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5a1779d9068445689598a76b6412bde3-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5a1779d9068445689598a76b6412bde3/', '800', '600', 'fighting,gladiator,activity,3d', 0, 0, 0, 'gladiator-fights', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5a1779d9068445689598a76b6412bde3-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5a1779d9068445689598a76b6412bde3-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(832, '2025-04-19', 'Sorting frogs', 'A game in the sorting genre, but in the form of sorting frogs, great graphics, very many levels, and a large variety of frogs. Several variations of levels. Pass levels, get achievements, unlock new kinds of frogs!', 'Frogs scattered all over the logs, you need to collect 4 identical frogs on the same log. \n\nTo do this, click or tap on the desired log to select the desired frogs, they will be highlighted. Next, click on another log on which you want to move the frog. \n\nIf the conditions are met, the frog will jump to the new location. \n\nWhen 4 identical frogs gather on the log, they will run away and you will get a reward. ', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0e3f6ccb98794b62b71b394d64652c95-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0e3f6ccb98794b62b71b394d64652c95-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0e3f6ccb98794b62b71b394d64652c95/', '800', '600', '2d,animal,cute,logic,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'sorting-frogs', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0e3f6ccb98794b62b71b394d64652c95-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0e3f6ccb98794b62b71b394d64652c95-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
