(957, '2025-04-19', 'Farm Triple Match', 'Looking for a fun tile-matching puzzle game? Try Farm Triple Match, a fresh take on tile-matching for puzzle lovers! This mahjong-inspired game is easy to learn but offers exciting challenges.\nBeat levels and build your own farm with cute animals and a lovely garden.\nClassic gameplay with a modern twist for relaxing brain training.\nExplore a variety of tiles featuring fruits, veggies, animals, and more.\nUse boosters to conquer tough puzzles and keep progressing. No time limitsplay anytime!', 'Match three tiles in a row by removing them from the board and adding them to the bottom of the screen. You can only select tiles that have no others stacked on top of them. Be strategic to avoid running out of space in your collection row! If you get stuck, use a booster to help. Play with your mouse or touchscreen.', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a2ccc7fecd4b4e61bb4c57503c79863d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a2ccc7fecd4b4e61bb4c57503c79863d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a2ccc7fecd4b4e61bb4c57503c79863d/', '800', '600', 'animal,farm,logic,connection,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'farm-triple-match', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a2ccc7fecd4b4e61bb4c57503c79863d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a2ccc7fecd4b4e61bb4c57503c79863d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(958, '2025-04-19', 'Obby Draw to Escape', 'Have a blast in Obby illustrating your way to victory! Play the fun and relaxing casual game Draw to Escape and see if you can overcome the levels\' issues using just your creativity.\n\nYou may earn money as you go through the levels, and you can earn even more coins when you reach the end of each level for every star you find. Things may vanish or explode and kill you, so be sure to check every level thoroughly.\n', 'Instructions:\n\nDraw with your pencil the platforms on which you can walk and avoid the dangerous obstacles in the levels. Collect coins so you can buy new skins for your character.\n\nControls:\nUse the mouse to draw\nA Move left\nD Move right\nSpacebar to make a small jump\nUse the game buttons to erase what you have drawn.', 'Adventure,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d38ea6bc2dfb434da419992997a6c7f3-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d38ea6bc2dfb434da419992997a6c7f3-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d38ea6bc2dfb434da419992997a6c7f3/', '800', '600', 'drawing,escape,run,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'obby-draw-to-escape', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d38ea6bc2dfb434da419992997a6c7f3-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d38ea6bc2dfb434da419992997a6c7f3-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(959, '2025-04-19', 'G Wagon City Driver', 'Dive into city driving with four game modes. Navigate busy morning streets, managing fuel and realistic traffic. Venture beyond the city to tackle rugged offroad terrain. Stunning morning graphics bring the city and landscapes to life, while unpredictable pedestrians and police chases add excitement. Customize your G-Wagon\'s look and performance, and enjoy the ride with your loyal dog. Whether evading cops or exploring trails, G-Wagon City Driver offers a thrilling experience.', 'W, A, S, D/Arrow Keys: Drive/Steer/Brake\nLeft Shift: Nitro\nC: Change Camera\nG: Slow Motion', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0db7851406a542f1a82d4000d1410d00-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0db7851406a542f1a82d4000d1410d00-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0db7851406a542f1a82d4000d1410d00/', '800', '600', '1player,car,drift,stunts,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'g-wagon-city-driver', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0db7851406a542f1a82d4000d1410d00-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0db7851406a542f1a82d4000d1410d00-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(960, '2025-04-19', 'Unscrew Them All', 'Unscrew Them All is a challenging  puzzle game where players must strategically unscrew all the screws securing large wooden planks to the board. After removing each screw, place it into the correct open slot. Unscrew all the planks before time runs out to complete each level. Master every level to win the game!', '1. Select a Screw: Click on a screw to unscrew it from the wooden plank.\n2. Place the Screw: Tap on an open hole that is unobstructed by planks.\n3. Remove the Plank: When all screws are removed, the plank drops down, revealing new holes. If a plank has only one screw, it may rotate, revealing additional holes.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/511d7a96252748d1acc32402d6fc4498-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/511d7a96252748d1acc32402d6fc4498-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/511d7a96252748d1acc32402d6fc4498/', '600', '800', '1player,highscore,physics,wood,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'unscrew-them-all', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/511d7a96252748d1acc32402d6fc4498-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/511d7a96252748d1acc32402d6fc4498-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(961, '2025-04-19', 'Spooky Link', 'Spooky Link is a relaxing Halloween-themed game where you connect matching spooky tiles. Tap a tile, then tap its match. If the path between them has two or fewer turns, the tiles are cleared. Each cleared tile creates more space to connect others. Enjoy many levels of fun with Halloween surprises!', 'Tap or click on a spooky tile, then find and select its matching tile. If the path between them has two or fewer turns, they will be cleared. Clear all tiles to complete the level. Use your mouse or touchpad to play!', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9877dfa80bef4ea1ae3d9031bcc39c99-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9877dfa80bef4ea1ae3d9031bcc39c99-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9877dfa80bef4ea1ae3d9031bcc39c99/', '1280', '720', 'halloween,matching,tiles,link,clicker,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'spooky-link', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9877dfa80bef4ea1ae3d9031bcc39c99-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9877dfa80bef4ea1ae3d9031bcc39c99-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(962, '2025-04-19', 'Town Run', 'Town Run is an excellent option if you enjoy games that require you to run continuously. It combines action-packed gameplay, vibrant graphics, and infinite running! Catching the raccoon is the goal. You\'ll need to sprint, leap, avoid obstacles, gather cash, and more in order to accomplish that!', 'Use the arrow keys to move, jump, and slide.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9eb56423bafe4f2a9d3298de4846440e-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9eb56423bafe4f2a9d3298de4846440e-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9eb56423bafe4f2a9d3298de4846440e/', '800', '600', 'endless,run,runner,kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'town-run', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9eb56423bafe4f2a9d3298de4846440e-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9eb56423bafe4f2a9d3298de4846440e-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(963, '2025-04-19', 'Pin Puzzle Save The Sheep', 'Pin Puzzle: Save The Sheep is an exciting pin-pulling game. You will test your brain intelligence and have endless fun. In this game, you have to make the sheep eat food and save them from their predicament. You have many other tasks like pulling the pin to make the dog eat the food. But be aware that you may meet a lot of obstacles like bombs, lava, etc. and you need to avoid them. There are many interesting levels to play in this crazy puzzle game. Come and join the game.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8e3649c06c984868a79891ba60f3971c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8e3649c06c984868a79891ba60f3971c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8e3649c06c984868a79891ba60f3971c/', '720', '1280', '1player,escape,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'pin-puzzle-save-the-sheep', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8e3649c06c984868a79891ba60f3971c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8e3649c06c984868a79891ba60f3971c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(964, '2025-04-19', 'Dino Survival: 3D Simulator', 'Survive in this prehistoric Jurassic park. Tame and grow dinosaurs, fight dinos, explore uncharted territories and incredible areas. Build your settlement. Sail to distant islands. Go to Raid! Conquer! Defeat raptors and the huge T-Rex!', 'Control:\n\nFor PC.\nCharacter control - \"WASD\", Arrow keys or hold down the left mouse button and drag the mouse in the desired direction.\nAttack - the hero attacks automatically.\n\nFor Mobile devices.\nCharacter control - press your finger on the screen and drag your finger in the desired direction.\nAttack - the hero attacks automatically.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4eeda043a7084082ba5c76a9488d3b5b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4eeda043a7084082ba5c76a9488d3b5b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4eeda043a7084082ba5c76a9488d3b5b/', '800', '600', 'dinosaurs,guns,idle,arcade,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'dino-survival-3d-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4eeda043a7084082ba5c76a9488d3b5b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4eeda043a7084082ba5c76a9488d3b5b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(965, '2025-04-19', 'Little master of assembly', 'The gameplay of this game is puzzle assembly type, mainly according to the room suggested by the picture, according to the objects in the room, the use of parts to splice the room objects', 'The main gameplay click on the furniture of the room and then the entire room parts are assembled', 'Puzzle,Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0ee365644093436e8669690149503051-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0ee365644093436e8669690149503051-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0ee365644093436e8669690149503051/', '720', '1280', '1player', 0, 0, 0, 'little-master-of-assembly', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0ee365644093436e8669690149503051-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0ee365644093436e8669690149503051-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(966, '2025-04-19', 'Nightmare Couple Halloween Party', 'Nightmare Couple Halloween Party is a spooky and stylish dress-up game where you can help the ultimate nightmare couple prepare for their eerie Halloween bash. Select from a variety of creepy costumes, haunting accessories, and makeup styles to give the couple their perfect spine-chilling look. Unleash your creativity and fashion sense to make this Halloween party an unforgettable one for the nightmare couple!', 'Left Mouse Button Click Or Tap to Play', 'Casual,Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/07f359342fed4cfebbdfd5eba605dba2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/07f359342fed4cfebbdfd5eba605dba2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/07f359342fed4cfebbdfd5eba605dba2/', '800', '600', 'couple,halloween,cutedressup,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'nightmare-couple-halloween-party', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/07f359342fed4cfebbdfd5eba605dba2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/07f359342fed4cfebbdfd5eba605dba2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(967, '2025-04-19', 'Spooky Halloween Hidden Pumpkin', 'In Spooky Halloween Hidden Pumpkin, youll explore haunted locations like creepy graveyards, abandoned houses, foggy forests, and more. Each level is uniquely designed with eerie Halloween-themed settings full of tricks and illusions. Your challenge is to locate 10 pumpkins hidden in plain sight within each scene. The faster you find them, the better your score!', 'Explore Each Scene: Every level introduces a new Halloween-themed location full of details. Use your sharp eyes to scan the scene and uncover the pumpkins.\nFind the Hidden Pumpkins: There are 10 pumpkins hidden in each level. They may be cleverly disguised among other spooky elements, so pay close attention!\n', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/788389c811fa4a2a91c85295affd8d49-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/788389c811fa4a2a91c85295affd8d49-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/788389c811fa4a2a91c85295affd8d49/', '1280', '720', 'halloween,hidden,hide,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'spooky-halloween-hidden-pumpkin', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/788389c811fa4a2a91c85295affd8d49-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/788389c811fa4a2a91c85295affd8d49-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(968, '2025-04-19', 'Animerge', 'Animerge is a cute, fun and cozy casual game where players merge cute adorable animals, starting from the tiniest mouse, all the way to the majestic elephant! \n\nCombining these animals playing solo or battling with friends, the cozy Lo-Fi music and hand drawn art create the perfect atmosphere for unwinding. \n\nMerge, strategize, and relax in this fun and laid-back adventure!', 'LMB or Tap to drop.\nPress and hold to drag animals.\nPress the Cyclone icon at top right corner of the window to swirl animals and make space.\nPress the radio to change the Lo-fi music.\nOpen the docker at the right hand side by clicking on its handle.\nYou get a cyclone as reward every 500 points, which can be used from the docker.\nSelect your Lo-fi vibe from the inside the radio in the Main Menu.', 'Casual,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c5d0a0e50b0f4dedb1ebdcfc940dafa5-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c5d0a0e50b0f4dedb1ebdcfc940dafa5-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c5d0a0e50b0f4dedb1ebdcfc940dafa5/', '1128', '615', 'animal,idle,relaxing,arcade,multiplayer,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'animerge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c5d0a0e50b0f4dedb1ebdcfc940dafa5-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c5d0a0e50b0f4dedb1ebdcfc940dafa5-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(969, '2025-04-19', 'Cat Life Merge Money', 'Experience the life of a stray cat, beg from humans, earn money to buy food, and merge the money you beg to get more money. Only by acting quickly can you enter the rich cat life! First of all,all you need to do is click on the cat and let it beg all the time. Otherwise, it will be lazy. ', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/25330011429846999effc9f00e39add4-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/25330011429846999effc9f00e39add4-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/25330011429846999effc9f00e39add4/', '750', '1334', 'cat,clicker,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cat-life-merge-money', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/25330011429846999effc9f00e39add4-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/25330011429846999effc9f00e39add4-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(970, '2025-04-19', 'Space Shift', 'It\'s a game where you travel in space for as long as possible without hitting any obstacles- meteorites or missiles. Your ship moves automatically and you can slow it down to ensure it doesn\'t hit anything. There are different galaxies to travel through different in appearance and the type of obstacles to appear. If you travel far enough, you may encounter even an alien ship!', 'Windows-Press space to slow down, control to use secondary ability.\nAndroid/Touch-Touch Left side of the screen to slow down, Right side to use secondary ability.', 'Agility,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/25a9cabb062640209571dd2b13948ee1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/25a9cabb062640209571dd2b13948ee1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/25a9cabb062640209571dd2b13948ee1/', '1600', '900', '1player,avoid,space,bullet,reflex,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'space-shift', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/25a9cabb062640209571dd2b13948ee1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/25a9cabb062640209571dd2b13948ee1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(971, '2025-04-19', 'Destruction of Stickman Zombie', 'Take a weapon and destroy the zombie stickmen! \"Destruction of Stick Zombie\" is an exciting game in which you will fight against hordes of stickman zombies using your skills and strategies. You have to fight zombies to earn coins and improve your weapons.\nYou start the game as a regular player, but as you progress in the game, you become more experienced and skilled in combat. The more coins you earn, the more weapons and ammo you can buy.', 'The goal of the game is to destroy all the zombie stickmen on each level. It is necessary to clear every room from enemies. As the game progresses, you need to buy new weapons and do not forget about ammo.\nDesktop control: WASD - control, weapon selection - space.\nControl on a mobile device: swipe/touch.', 'Shooter,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c7991112492c4f408b159217f1e811b9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c7991112492c4f408b159217f1e811b9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c7991112492c4f408b159217f1e811b9/', '800', '600', 'characters,endless,guns,zombie,stickman,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'destruction-of-stickman-zombie', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c7991112492c4f408b159217f1e811b9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c7991112492c4f408b159217f1e811b9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(972, '2025-04-19', 'Ninja dash Cozy tactic puzzle', 'Get ready to immerse yourself in a tactical puzzle adventure where you\'ll feel like a stealthy ninja and master strategist! Your mission: clear locations of enemies with a limited number of attacks. Plan your moves carefully and use the environment to your advantage by bouncing off walls and objects to change your trajectory.\nPlan your tactics, execute perfect maneuvers, and become the ultimate ninja strategist!', 'PC: mouse to control the character, AD to rotate the camera.\nMobile: on-screen buttons.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/096146cf258d4000a0ac904766059294-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/096146cf258d4000a0ac904766059294-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/096146cf258d4000a0ac904766059294/', '960', '540', '1player,aim,anime,attack,ninja,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'ninja-dash-cozy-tactic-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/096146cf258d4000a0ac904766059294-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/096146cf258d4000a0ac904766059294-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(973, '2025-04-19', 'Merge Hotel Empire', 'You can generate and collect different new items by synthesizing the same items, and then use them to create and decorate a new mansion for the hotel empire of the story.', 'Click to interact and drag items to synthesize or merge!', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/793bc519272e4f46be6cedec1842c257-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/793bc519272e4f46be6cedec1842c257-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/793bc519272e4f46be6cedec1842c257/', '750', '1334', 'food,matching,tycoon,styling,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'merge-hotel-empire', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/793bc519272e4f46be6cedec1842c257-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/793bc519272e4f46be6cedec1842c257-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(974, '2025-04-19', 'Ghostly Graveyard Halloween Special', 'This Halloween, experience the thrill of Ghostly Graveyard is a spooky platformer adventure where you explore a haunted graveyard and unravel its mysteries. Navigate challenging levels, collect coins, and avoid ghostly encounters. Can you solve the graveyard\'s secrets?\nA Halloween Special Spooky Puzzle Adventure.', 'Arrow keys Or Touch conroller', 'Adventure,Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/509c2fda23ed43d7b90ab08ecae4bebc-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/509c2fda23ed43d7b90ab08ecae4bebc-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/509c2fda23ed43d7b90ab08ecae4bebc/', '854', '480', 'forest,ghost,halloween,story,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'ghostly-graveyard-halloween-special', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/509c2fda23ed43d7b90ab08ecae4bebc-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/509c2fda23ed43d7b90ab08ecae4bebc-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(975, '2025-04-19', 'Princesses at Horror School', 'In this game you will meet two charming monster girls who study at a school for young monsters. Every morning, the girls carefully think over their images, mixing elements of a classic princess and a creepy monster. Girls have different fashion preferences, but they have one thing in common - these two unusual girlfriends always attract the admiring glances of classmates. After all, they are not just princesses, but real monsters whose terrifying style makes even the bravest tremble!', 'We help two girls-students of an unusual educational institution, prepare for Halloween: we apply bright makeup; create complex hairstyles with colorful strands and choose terribly beautiful tops, skirts and dresses from the wardrobe. The result can be saved as a PNG image. Depending on the gaming device, a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touch screens is used to control it.', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b6b7cf8e5a2048c0899bbca57925f7b7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b6b7cf8e5a2048c0899bbca57925f7b7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b6b7cf8e5a2048c0899bbca57925f7b7/', '800', '600', 'halloween,monster,schoolgirl,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'princesses-at-horror-school', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b6b7cf8e5a2048c0899bbca57925f7b7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b6b7cf8e5a2048c0899bbca57925f7b7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(976, '2025-04-19', 'Pumpkin Patch', 'Immerse yourself in the mysterious world of a magical pumpkin farm, where pumpkins are so diverse and full of surprises that it\'s hard to tell one from the other! Your task is to carefully observe each pumpkin character and remember as many details as possible. Can you recognize and find two identical pumpkins among many others?', '- At the beginning, one pumpkin will appear on the screen. Take a close look at it  remember its shape and other details.\n- When you\'re ready, click the \"next\" arrow. The pumpkin will disappear, and several new pumpkins will appear. Your task is to find the one you saw earlier. Select it by clicking on it.\n- It\'s worth recognizing all or as many pumpkins as possible, because at the end of the game, a special Halloween surprise awaits you!', 'Educational,Quiz', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d959ad497ef44f7db9369e34906b4fb7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d959ad497ef44f7db9369e34906b4fb7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d959ad497ef44f7db9369e34906b4fb7/', '600', '1110', 'farm,find,halloween,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'pumpkin-patch', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d959ad497ef44f7db9369e34906b4fb7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d959ad497ef44f7db9369e34906b4fb7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(977, '2025-04-19', 'NoobHood HalloweenCraft', 'Noobhood is actually a folk hero. Of course, that\'s how he is in our game too. He has one main goal: to dress in a Halloween costume, prepare his horse for Halloween, and collect all the Halloween coins. Gather all the Halloween coins. You must be very careful; surviving in this dark and scary forest is truly difficult. There are pumpkin monsters in this forest, and you must defeat them with your sword. Throw your sword at the monsters to defeat them all.', '*Move with the \"WASD\" keys.\n*Double jumping is available in the game.\n*Can be controlled from both mobile and PC.\n*Press the \"P\" key to throw the sword and defeat monsters.\n*Press the \"P\" key to throw the sword and break doors.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/edec3f0a547a4e88985fcb91554b8664-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/edec3f0a547a4e88985fcb91554b8664-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/edec3f0a547a4e88985fcb91554b8664/', '800', '600', '1player,halloween,minecraft,pixel,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'noobhood-halloweencraft', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/edec3f0a547a4e88985fcb91554b8664-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/edec3f0a547a4e88985fcb91554b8664-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(978, '2025-04-19', 'Canasta Royale Offline', 'Canasta is the most traditional and loved card game by all. It is an exciting mix of strategy, luck and skill.Canasta uses two complete decks of 52 playing cards (French Deck) plus the four Jokers. All the Jokers and twos are wild cards.\n\nGame Features:\n 2 or 4 players\n Clockwise or Counter-Clockwise\n Game is automatically saved each turn, so you can close it and continue playing later\n Undo function so you can cancel mistaken melds', 'Left mouse button', 'Boardgames,Cards', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2f140d7d57f748059c22c415053a33c5-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2f140d7d57f748059c22c415053a33c5-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2f140d7d57f748059c22c415053a33c5/', '800', '600', '1player,casino,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'canasta-royale-offline', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2f140d7d57f748059c22c415053a33c5-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2f140d7d57f748059c22c415053a33c5-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(979, '2025-04-19', 'Pizza Maker - Cooking Games For Kids', 'Become a pizza master by creating delicious pizzas from scratch with 15 unique recipes. Choose ingredients, slice vegetables, shred cheese, and prepare toppings. Knead and roll the dough, spread the sauce, add toppings, and bake. Once ready, box your pizza for delivery! Fun, engaging, and perfect for kids to develop cooking skills.', 'Use the left mouse button on the desktop and tapping the screen on the phone. Follow the prompts to make pizza!', 'Cooking,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/118281804b924706a9a10b300d62fe53-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/118281804b924706a9a10b300d62fe53-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/118281804b924706a9a10b300d62fe53/', '1920', '1080', 'chef,kitchen,pizza,restaurant,fastfood,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'pizza-maker-cooking-games-for-kids', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/118281804b924706a9a10b300d62fe53-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/118281804b924706a9a10b300d62fe53-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(980, '2025-04-19', 'Woodland Slide', 'Embark on a relaxing journey in Woodland Slide! Slide the colorful jewels across wooden planks to create perfect matches and clear the board.\n\nWith every move, a new row of gems disappears, adding to the challenge. Use your strategy and unlock powerful abilities to remove gems, split them into smaller pieces, or clear entire rows.\n\nExplore a serene, nature-inspired setting while testing your puzzle-solving skills. How far can you go in this addictive quest for the perfect match?', 'Slide the pieces to fill the lines', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d24e5685531e4e9fbab904d0c6180e47-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d24e5685531e4e9fbab904d0c6180e47-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d24e5685531e4e9fbab904d0c6180e47/', '720', '1280', 'sliding-puzzle,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'woodland-slide', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d24e5685531e4e9fbab904d0c6180e47-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d24e5685531e4e9fbab904d0c6180e47-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(981, '2025-04-19', 'Fashion Princess Dress Up', 'Fashion Princess: Dress Up is a casual game. With beautiful animations and sound effects, this game is sure to keep you hooked. Swipe left and right to control the character and choose the corresponding dress up according to the task to show off your matching trendy outfits, hairstyles, and make-up, you need to consider the theme of the fashion show, and the judge\'s preference. If your score is higher, you will win the battle and become the ultimate fashionista.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fc419fe8405640cbb7759e9af92aef23-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fc419fe8405640cbb7759e9af92aef23-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/fc419fe8405640cbb7759e9af92aef23/', '720', '1280', 'parkour,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'fashion-princess-dress-up', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fc419fe8405640cbb7759e9af92aef23-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fc419fe8405640cbb7759e9af92aef23-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(982, '2025-04-19', 'Push The Frog', 'Control your little frog to eat all the mosquitoes. Master the length of the frog\'s tongue and make the frog reach the appropriate position to eat the mosquitoes. Think carefully about planning the route. The game has a simple and interesting style, and the gameplay is educational and novel. It is very suitable for playing when killing time.', 'WASD or arrows to move, Spacebar pops out the frog\'s tongue', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/39aea9d774bf4c208d705cd56637071d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/39aea9d774bf4c208d705cd56637071d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/39aea9d774bf4c208d705cd56637071d/', '1334', '750', '2d,animal,logic,timekiller,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'push-the-frog', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/39aea9d774bf4c208d705cd56637071d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/39aea9d774bf4c208d705cd56637071d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(983, '2025-04-19', 'Monster High Spooky Fashion', 'In Monster High Spooky Fashion, step into the world of ghouls and ghosts as you style your favorite Monster High characters! Choose spooky outfits, eerie accessories, and haunting makeup to create the ultimate creepy-cool look. Mix and match from a wide range of outfits to give each character a unique spooky style perfect for any Monster High event. Whether its for a Halloween party or a night out in the graveyard, bring out your inner fashionista with Halloween Spooky Fashion!', 'Left Mouse Button Click or Tap to Play', 'Casual,Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bfd6006ffb1d4605845483de02650ccd-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bfd6006ffb1d4605845483de02650ccd-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bfd6006ffb1d4605845483de02650ccd/', '800', '600', 'fashion,halloween,cutedressup,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'monster-high-spooky-fashion', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bfd6006ffb1d4605845483de02650ccd-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bfd6006ffb1d4605845483de02650ccd-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(984, '2025-04-19', 'Crazy Bunnies', 'An exciting platformer about super bunnies in which you have to go through levels created in the style of Minecraft. There is a single and cooperative mode.', 'Computer control:\n\nR - restart level\nPlayer 1\nA / D - character rotation left / right\nF - grab / let go\nSpace - jump\nPlayer 2\nJ / L - character rotation left / right\nH - grab / let go\nN - jump\n\nManagement on mobile devices is carried out by pressing buttons on the screen.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4a73cd3206ca46f58f28895377ff6624-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4a73cd3206ca46f58f28895377ff6624-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4a73cd3206ca46f58f28895377ff6624/', '800', '600', 'animal,physics,platformer,arcade', 0, 0, 0, 'crazy-bunnies', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4a73cd3206ca46f58f28895377ff6624-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4a73cd3206ca46f58f28895377ff6624-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(985, '2025-04-19', 'My Hospital Learn Care', 'This is a doll placement simulation game. Have you ever wanted to run a hospital by yourself? Do you want to be a doctor? This game of ours can fulfill your wish. You can build a hospital Avatar world of your own.', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Casual,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/33347defdabc4460ae5a4f22663af813-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/33347defdabc4460ae5a4f22663af813-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/33347defdabc4460ae5a4f22663af813/', '1334', '750', 'doctor,doll,hospital,kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'my-hospital-learn-care', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/33347defdabc4460ae5a4f22663af813-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/33347defdabc4460ae5a4f22663af813-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(986, '2025-04-19', 'Space Survivor', 'Jump right into the action, fighting dangerous aliens and executing amazing maneuvers! Sharpen your weapons and skills, you will need them to last as long as possible.\n', 'Move your character around on the screen to attack and defeat enemies. Make sure not to get hit when you pick up the gems dropped. Upgrade your weapons and abilities. Use the power-ups if you\'re in a tough spot.\n', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/da9fbff0f8534c15b27dd7174a3e284f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/da9fbff0f8534c15b27dd7174a3e284f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/da9fbff0f8534c15b27dd7174a3e284f/', '800', '600', 'alien,space,survival,weapons', 0, 0, 0, 'space-survivor', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/da9fbff0f8534c15b27dd7174a3e284f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/da9fbff0f8534c15b27dd7174a3e284f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(987, '2025-04-19', 'Checkers Deluxe Edition', 'It\'s a clash on the battlefield! Draw up your plan and defeat your opponents with finesse!\n\nIt is also known as the draughts game, and it is an interesting test of strategy. Compete with an opponent and dominate their pieces as best you can.\n\nWhat happens when you manage to move a piece to the other end? Come play now and let\'s find out!', 'Take turns to move your pieces diagonally on the board. You can remove an opponent\'s piece by jumping over it if there is a space behind it. The goal is to remove all of your opponent\'s pieces from the field.', 'Boardgames', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cc314a3c4ebd4c33a46d8bd0de8e5374-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cc314a3c4ebd4c33a46d8bd0de8e5374-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cc314a3c4ebd4c33a46d8bd0de8e5374/', '1920', '1080', 'checkers,2players,singleplayer,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'checkers-deluxe-edition', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cc314a3c4ebd4c33a46d8bd0de8e5374-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cc314a3c4ebd4c33a46d8bd0de8e5374-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(988, '2025-04-19', 'Idle Lunch', 'Idle Lunch is a fun and casual idle game where your mission is to take big bites and earn coins! Start your journey with a simple burger, tapping to take each bite and build your fortune. As you accumulate coins, unlock new delicious foods to keep the fun going, from pizzas to fancy desserts. The more you bite, the more you earn! Invest your coins in powerful upgrades that boost your earnings, allowing you to munch faster and grow your wealth even quicker.', 'Take big bites and earn coins to unlock new food and upgrades in Idle Lunch!', 'Casual,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/50fa296480f34938a39b3ac76982e74a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/50fa296480f34938a39b3ac76982e74a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/50fa296480f34938a39b3ac76982e74a/', '1280', '720', '1player,idle,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'idle-lunch', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/50fa296480f34938a39b3ac76982e74a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/50fa296480f34938a39b3ac76982e74a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(989, '2025-04-19', 'Bolts and Nuts - Puzzle', 'An educational and exciting game in which you can test your logical and strategic thinking.\nSolve unique puzzles to while away the time and relax with excellent soundtrack. A bright and exciting game is perfect not only for children, but will also give you the opportunity to test your skills in solving difficult problems for adults.', 'Release all the wooden parts so that they fall down!\nUnscrew the bolts by pressing on them, and screw them into the free holes. When there are no wooden planks left, the level will be completed.\nUse auxiliary tools:\n- screwdriver: removes the bolt you press;\n- freeze time: stops the timer for 30 seconds.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/579d648da6a3459da02bead6a4d3e7f5-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/579d648da6a3459da02bead6a4d3e7f5-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/579d648da6a3459da02bead6a4d3e7f5/', '800', '600', '2d,block,halloween,logic,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bolts-and-nuts-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/579d648da6a3459da02bead6a4d3e7f5-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/579d648da6a3459da02bead6a4d3e7f5-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(990, '2025-04-19', 'Duet Cats Halloween Cat Music', 'Welcome to Duet Cats Halloween Cat Music, a game feast for 2 players filled with fun and music!Join your friends in this Halloween-inspired game to challenge the cat\'s music and have fun! With the rhythm of the music, control the cute cat to move. Let them eat more ice cream. You can choose a different musical challenge. You should accurately move to collect ice cream, and get the highest high score!', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1984cf24c5994b96b03dc9c174aa4233-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1984cf24c5994b96b03dc9c174aa4233-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1984cf24c5994b96b03dc9c174aa4233/', '457', '953', 'cat,halloween,music,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'duet-cats-halloween-cat-music', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1984cf24c5994b96b03dc9c174aa4233-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1984cf24c5994b96b03dc9c174aa4233-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(991, '2025-04-19', 'Little Lily Halloween Prep', 'Welcome to Little Lily Halloween Prep. Its time to celebrate Halloween with Little Lily! Enjoy a memorable Halloween night with Lily and play fun-packed Halloween games and activities. Help the lily to complete her makeover, then help her with Halloween face painting. Browse her wardrobe and pick cute outfits and costumes. Finally, help her with cake decoration. A lot more to enjoy and explore this Halloween season with Little Lily. Happy Halloween!!', 'Left Mouse Button Click or Tap to play', 'Casual,Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8850675c26c64fd088e2be0daa618820-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8850675c26c64fd088e2be0daa618820-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8850675c26c64fd088e2be0daa618820/', '560', '854', 'halloween,cutedressup,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'little-lily-halloween-prep', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8850675c26c64fd088e2be0daa618820-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8850675c26c64fd088e2be0daa618820-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(992, '2025-04-19', 'Candy Cascade', 'Click on groups of two or more candies to destroy them. You need to collect certain amount of different sweets on every level.  Wooden blocks, honey and jam should be cleared from the game field. If there is a key on the game field it should be dropped down. The moves are limited for each level. If you have hard time with a task you can use bonuses that can be received when you collect jam.', 'Destroy tiles by tapping on a group of them.', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9dc0bfa97de94a879aab0c38b6b6c387-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9dc0bfa97de94a879aab0c38b6b6c387-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9dc0bfa97de94a879aab0c38b6b6c387/', '1280', '720', 'candies,candy,collect,matching,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'candy-cascade', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9dc0bfa97de94a879aab0c38b6b6c387-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9dc0bfa97de94a879aab0c38b6b6c387-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(993, '2025-04-19', 'Word Rivers', 'Play Word Rivers - an exciting word game where you can enjoy a sea of words and fantastic crosswords. Find words from letters and discover the wonders of the world and words right now!', 'Playing and guessing words from the world of letters is very simple. Look at the crossword and try to find words by forming them from the letters at the bottom of the screen. Combine the letters in the circle at the bottom by swiping your finger on mobile devices. On a computer, click the first letter in the circle at the bottom, and without releasing the mouse button, move the mouse toward the following letter of the new word.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fec982ec0f784e52801ff2ec4da56b6c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fec982ec0f784e52801ff2ec4da56b6c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/fec982ec0f784e52801ff2ec4da56b6c/', '800', '600', '1player,wordsearch,crossword,alphabet,wordscapes,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'word-rivers', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fec982ec0f784e52801ff2ec4da56b6c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fec982ec0f784e52801ff2ec4da56b6c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(994, '2025-04-19', 'Solve the Cube Wooden Blocks 2D!', ' This is a game in which you have to connect wooden blocks! In the game you have a playing area where you must connect blocks to fill the line! Once the line is full, the blocks will disappear, giving you the most\npoints! Compete with friends or colleagues on the leaderboard! Enjoy your game!', '1. At first it will be easy to connect the blocks, but over time there will be more and more of them.\nConnect wisely so you have room!\n2. Press and hold your finger or mouse to control the block. Release your finger or\nclick the mouse to make the block fall onto the field\n3. Enjoy the game!', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ef031eed4aad43bca10c88d95349fffb-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ef031eed4aad43bca10c88d95349fffb-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ef031eed4aad43bca10c88d95349fffb/', '800', '600', '1player,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'solve-the-cube-wooden-blocks-2d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ef031eed4aad43bca10c88d95349fffb-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ef031eed4aad43bca10c88d95349fffb-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(995, '2025-04-19', 'Wild Hunting Clash', 'Challenge yourself and hunt beautiful animals in stunningly luscious woods. The calming sounds of the forest and lovely graphics will capture your heart. Feel like a true hunter in the unconquered wilderness!\n', 'Shoot the animals and collect their trophies in all the different levels to progress to the next region. Unlock and upgrade your hunting gear using the gold you get as a reward.\n', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0143ede05b904e3db4add3645b0ef415-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0143ede05b904e3db4add3645b0ef415-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0143ede05b904e3db4add3645b0ef415/', '800', '600', 'hunt,hunting,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'wild-hunting-clash', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0143ede05b904e3db4add3645b0ef415-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0143ede05b904e3db4add3645b0ef415-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(996, '2025-04-19', 'Obby Halloween Danger Skate', 'Obby is skateboarding on the rooftops and performing dangerous tricks. He wants to skateboard on the rooftops during Halloween. Help Obby reach the finish line safely. You must be very careful! Since it\'s Halloween, the city is flooded with toxic water, and if you fall from the building, you will die. Jump from barrels to containers and climb to the top of the building. Collect all the pumpkins along the way to earn money. Gather all the pumpkins and reach the finish line!', '*Use the \'WASD\' keys to move.\n*15 different levels with unique challenges.\n*Collect all the pumpkins.\n*You can buy 4 different costumes from the shop.', 'Casual,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e7a5d8f1c4f2488685f7ca892201c672-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e7a5d8f1c4f2488685f7ca892201c672-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e7a5d8f1c4f2488685f7ca892201c672/', '800', '600', '1player,pixel,platformer,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'obby-halloween-danger-skate', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e7a5d8f1c4f2488685f7ca892201c672-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e7a5d8f1c4f2488685f7ca892201c672-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
