(1165, '2025-04-19', 'Zen Tile', 'Are you a master player of matching games? Do you enjoy matching puzzle games? Come to challenge this addictive puzzle game: Zen Tile - Relaxing Match!', '- Tap 3 same tiles to eliminate them.\n- Match tiles from the screen.\n- Pay attention to the collecting bar; if fill it up, you\'ll fail.\n- Use boosters to help you solve tricky levels.', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a0ffeddb8add4bdc9af1d9bdbf8c7f58-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a0ffeddb8add4bdc9af1d9bdbf8c7f58-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a0ffeddb8add4bdc9af1d9bdbf8c7f58/', '506', '900', '2d,magic,relaxing,tiles,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'zen-tile', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a0ffeddb8add4bdc9af1d9bdbf8c7f58-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a0ffeddb8add4bdc9af1d9bdbf8c7f58-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1166, '2025-04-19', 'Magic and Wizards Match', 'Magic and Wizards is an enchanting Match 3 game where you and your friend Aurora embark on a mystical journey through a magical realm. With over 4000+ levels, match gems representing magical elements to overcome obstacles, using powerful boosters to progress. Complete Daily Missions, tackle tricky blockers, and uncover hidden treasures. With stunning graphics and immersive gameplay, Magic &amp; Wizards delivers a captivating experience filled with mystery. Ready for your magical adventure?', 'Combine more magical gems of the same kind to unlock powerful spells! Embark on an adventure through a mystical world with 4000+ levels. Join Aurora as you remove obstacles and cast spells to uncover hidden treasures. Watch out for magical creatures trying to hinder your progress! Enjoy daily missions, challenges, and discover enchanted rewards along the way. Experience endless fun and mystery in this captivating Match 3 game, Magic and Wizards!', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e003f23e182a4c2984407681402d4e77-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e003f23e182a4c2984407681402d4e77-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e003f23e182a4c2984407681402d4e77/', '800', '600', '1player,halloween,matching,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'magic-and-wizards-match', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e003f23e182a4c2984407681402d4e77-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e003f23e182a4c2984407681402d4e77-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1167, '2025-04-19', 'Merge Town!', 'Ever wanted to be Mayor? Ever wanted to run a town, develop the land, and see a metropolis grow? Well, look no further than Merge Town!, the newest title from Gram Games. The concept of the game is simple - you have a plot of land, and its your job to turn it into a town. Every so often, youll be gifted with a house. Each house can be merged with other houses of the same variety to form a bigger home.', 'Tap to play, click to merge', 'Strategy,Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1c726ea44ef646cdac297eb74563ad8e-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1c726ea44ef646cdac297eb74563ad8e-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1c726ea44ef646cdac297eb74563ad8e/', '750', '1334', 'logic,matching,timekiller,clicker,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood,No Cruelty', 0, 0, 0, 'merge-town', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1c726ea44ef646cdac297eb74563ad8e-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1c726ea44ef646cdac297eb74563ad8e-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1168, '2025-04-19', 'Vega Mix: Sea Adventures', 'Vega Mix: Sea Adventures is an exciting three-in-a-row game with vivid effects and unique mechanics. Embark on an unforgettable adventure with brave heroes who find themselves on the seabed and explore a sunken ship and an ancient city. But their story does not end there  after that they will have to restore the ancient lighthouse on the island. Enjoy colorful levels, various bonuses and puzzles that will help you uncover the secrets of the depths of the sea and restore the lighthouse.', 'How to play match-3 puzzle:\n\n Match 3 or more pieces in a line to explode them.\n Match 4 pieces to create the Rocket. The Rocket blows up the whole line!\n Match 4 pieces to form a square to create the Spinner. The Spinner destroys one of the targets!\n Make a T-shaped match of 5 pieces to create the Bomb. The Bomb makes a massive explosion on the board!\n Match 5 pieces in a line to create the Rainbow Flower. The Rainbow Flower explodes pieces of the same color!', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/903f32fa04e542d8903791f27f313d3a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/903f32fa04e542d8903791f27f313d3a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/903f32fa04e542d8903791f27f313d3a/', '1200', '650', 'No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'vega-mix-sea-adventures', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/903f32fa04e542d8903791f27f313d3a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/903f32fa04e542d8903791f27f313d3a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1169, '2025-04-19', 'Animal Transform Race', 'Animal Transform Race is a fun game based on reaction where different types of animals compete. Each animal is fast in some areas and very slow in some tracks according to their abilities. Try to lead the race by making the right choices. The faster you make animal choices, the more advantages you gain. You can unlock new animals from the market section with the coins you earn from the races.\n', 'You can use \"MOUSE\" or touch controls to change animals.\nFor 2 player mode, you can use \"A,S,D\" and \"J,K,L\" keys for shortcuts to change animals.', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/34572875eb1347629a2553de28c5f6aa-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/34572875eb1347629a2553de28c5f6aa-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/34572875eb1347629a2553de28c5f6aa/', '800', '600', '1player,animal,transformation,2players,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'animal-transform-race', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/34572875eb1347629a2553de28c5f6aa-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/34572875eb1347629a2553de28c5f6aa-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1170, '2025-04-19', 'Math Quest', '\"Math Quest\" - an exciting game for the whole family that develops mathematical skills, logic, and reaction speed. Overcome challenges, calculate correct answers, and reach new levels!', 'Solve all the math problems and answer the questions in the given time. ', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0e8e1bea7eb643448947d921e9ad43b9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0e8e1bea7eb643448947d921e9ad43b9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0e8e1bea7eb643448947d921e9ad43b9/', '800', '600', 'math,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'math-quest', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0e8e1bea7eb643448947d921e9ad43b9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0e8e1bea7eb643448947d921e9ad43b9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1171, '2025-04-19', 'Block Stacking', 'Block Stacking is a very fun, leisure, and pressure-relieving game. The game is very delicate and fresh. In the game, you will play by combining many different fruits. As long as you can complete the target tasks, you will have a chance to get rewards! By eliminating the fruits on the screen, you can successfully pass the level. It\'s extremely easy to operate, which makes you feel very addicted. Come and try the game!', 'Mouse or tap to play.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/261e725a841f473b8deb1d64a929794f-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/261e725a841f473b8deb1d64a929794f-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/261e725a841f473b8deb1d64a929794f/', '720', '1280', 'block,relaxing,3d,boys', 0, 0, 0, 'block-stacking', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/261e725a841f473b8deb1d64a929794f-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/261e725a841f473b8deb1d64a929794f-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1172, '2025-04-19', 'Dynamons 9', 'Embark on a brand new Dynamons adventure in Dynamons 9! This online monster collecting game includes two fresh areas to explore; Halloween world and the bonus cave.\n\nEncounter Tholanyx, Scarykin, Anubolt, Sauryx in frankenstein skin, Zonysus in Dracula skin and many more special Dynamons. Recruit them for your team and beat others in thrilling 1v1 battles with special attacks and power-ups.\n', 'Play the game using touchscreen controls or your mouse.\n\nThe game consists of spellbinding turn-based battles. You can use the action cards to attack, and catch the opposing creature when its weakened. The backpack is filled with items you can collect and use during your journeys. By selecting it during battle, you can access these special items. Use shards to level up your Dynamons, and to gain new action cards. Challenge other trainers and become the strongest Dynamon Captain!', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/200443b8a09a402ea935508e948f04fb-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/200443b8a09a402ea935508e948f04fb-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/200443b8a09a402ea935508e948f04fb/', '800', '600', '1player,collect,halloween,monster,rpg,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'dynamons-9', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/200443b8a09a402ea935508e948f04fb-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/200443b8a09a402ea935508e948f04fb-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1173, '2025-04-19', 'Galactic Golf Solitaire', 'Enjoy a relaxing round of Golf Solitaire, a fun and easy-to-play card game. The goal is to clear the board by matching cards that are one rank higher or lower than the one on the discard pile. Dont worry about suitsjust focus on the numbers! If youre stuck, you can draw from the deck to keep the game going. Play at your own pace and see how many rounds you can win.\n\nPerfect for a quick break or to unwind at the end of the day!', 'Objective: Clear the board by moving all cards to the waste pile.\nSetup: 7 columns of 5 face-up cards; the remaining cards form the draw pile.\nGameplay: Click the card from the board to move it to the waste pile if its one rank higher or lower than the top card of the waste pile. Suits don\'t matter. Aces can be placed on Kings or Twos. If no moves are possible, draw a card from the draw pile.\nWin: Clear all cards from the board.\nLoss: No moves left, and the draw pile is empty.', 'Cards', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bdd8d57467fa48ffa2f319d8149a8228-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bdd8d57467fa48ffa2f319d8149a8228-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bdd8d57467fa48ffa2f319d8149a8228/', '1280', '720', 'board,solitaire,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'galactic-golf-solitaire', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bdd8d57467fa48ffa2f319d8149a8228-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bdd8d57467fa48ffa2f319d8149a8228-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1174, '2025-04-19', 'Hoop World 3D', 'Hoop World 3D is a flip-and-dunk game that brings basketball to a whole new dimension! Get your timing right or you\'ll fall short of the net and fall flat on your face.', 'Hoop World 3D is fairly easy to maneuver and easy to learn. Use your mouse or keypad to control movement with just one finger.\n', 'Basketball', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/27f311ee037a4df5a300b486cdbf9c63-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/27f311ee037a4df5a300b486cdbf9c63-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/27f311ee037a4df5a300b486cdbf9c63/', '800', '1200', 'ball,basket,flip,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood,jumping', 0, 0, 0, 'hoop-world-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/27f311ee037a4df5a300b486cdbf9c63-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/27f311ee037a4df5a300b486cdbf9c63-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1175, '2025-04-19', 'Antistress Relaxation Box', 'Antistress - Relaxation Box is a fun casual game. Have you long been upset with some people in your life? He may be your date or a relative, and this game will vent your dissatisfaction! Choose a character and a tool for hitting, and your task is to beat the blood bar to 0 in a limited time. Easy to pick up, but informative and will give you hours of entertainment. Relax yourself and have fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/eca3fbb72e564d7d8eb85fa430fe6401-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/eca3fbb72e564d7d8eb85fa430fe6401-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/eca3fbb72e564d7d8eb85fa430fe6401/', '720', '1280', '2d,attack,relax,relaxing,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'antistress-relaxation-box', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/eca3fbb72e564d7d8eb85fa430fe6401-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/eca3fbb72e564d7d8eb85fa430fe6401-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1176, '2025-04-19', 'Rooftop Challenge', 'Rooftop Challenge is an exhilarating parkour adventure where players must leap, climb, and strategize their way through a sprawling urban landscape. Starting from ground level, the goal is to find the elusive \"house\" that serves as the gateway to even greater heights. Once found, the journey continues as players ascend rooftop after rooftop, navigating complex jumps, narrow ledges, and towering structures. ', '- Arrow to Move\n- Space to Jump ', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2f3c2c902efb4082903c82976881704b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2f3c2c902efb4082903c82976881704b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2f3c2c902efb4082903c82976881704b/', '960', '640', 'parkour,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'rooftop-challenge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2f3c2c902efb4082903c82976881704b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2f3c2c902efb4082903c82976881704b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1177, '2025-04-19', 'Obby Climb Racing', 'In the adventure game Obby Climb Racing, players may spend a lot of time racing on insane roads, acquiring interesting skins, improving Obby\'s bike, and completing difficult parkour courses. For fans of fast-paced, skill-based games, this is a must-play because of the thrilling combination of racing, platforming, and character advancement. In this adrenaline-pumping game, you\'ll have to crank your engines, level up your character, and complete parkour tasks.', 'Instructions:\nDrive your bike around the circuit accelerating and braking to reach the track of each level. Collect as many coins as you can to be able to buy a new skin.\n\nControls \nW = Accelerate \nS = Break \nArrows = Rotate \nSpacebar Jump', 'Adventure,Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8a7c5aeb2a074b2cb5d26de57cbd85a9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8a7c5aeb2a074b2cb5d26de57cbd85a9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8a7c5aeb2a074b2cb5d26de57cbd85a9/', '900', '600', 'car,roblox,climb,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'obby-climb-racing', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8a7c5aeb2a074b2cb5d26de57cbd85a9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8a7c5aeb2a074b2cb5d26de57cbd85a9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1178, '2025-04-19', 'Limousine Car Game Simulator', 'Limousine car game free driving\nWelcome to the world of car game of Limousine 3d &amp; car simulator 3d game of limousine. Enjoy the Limousine game of car driving in the city of cars game.limo car driving 2024 simulator mobile game taxi driving 2024 needs perfect driver to show skills. Collect maximum coins in the police jeep president limousine simulator to unlock luxury limo car game ? 3d 2024. ', 'USE W,A,S,D for Player Movement.', '.IO,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/519c5c3adae848899a3f3693b93611f1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/519c5c3adae848899a3f3693b93611f1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/519c5c3adae848899a3f3693b93611f1/', '960', '600', 'army,car,drift,parking,highway', 0, 0, 0, 'limousine-car-game-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/519c5c3adae848899a3f3693b93611f1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/519c5c3adae848899a3f3693b93611f1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1179, '2025-04-19', 'Cat Challenge', 'Meet the game Cat Challenge, where at each level the cat will patiently wait until you drop him a round colored candy disc. To do this, you need to cut the rope on which the candy dangles. But first, think about which side to do this and take into account the items that are on the playing field, they must be used to achieve the goal. The candy is not always directly above the cat, so it needs to be moved somehow.', 'Use the mouse or tap on the screen to play the game.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/95171c72f15a4690b282f12faf4171f2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/95171c72f15a4690b282f12faf4171f2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/95171c72f15a4690b282f12faf4171f2/', '1080', '1920', 'animal,cat,skill,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cat-challenge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/95171c72f15a4690b282f12faf4171f2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/95171c72f15a4690b282f12faf4171f2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1180, '2025-04-19', 'Cat Cut', 'A fun game about a hungry cat, get him a fish, cut the rope so that it falls directly to the cat. All objects move according to physics, do not miss the fish, do not upset the cat!', 'To complete the level, determine the route of movement of the fish, cut the rope or, conversely, rock or push and so on, depending on the level, so that the fish gets into the cat. Each object works in its own way, something flies, something falls, something cuts. Solve the riddle and feed the cat.\n\nTo get points, collect coins with a fish, for which you can unlock new characters!', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/df15bf88e85a4917bc16e6c55710fe43-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/df15bf88e85a4917bc16e6c55710fe43-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/df15bf88e85a4917bc16e6c55710fe43/', '800', '600', 'cat,cute,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cat-cut', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/df15bf88e85a4917bc16e6c55710fe43-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/df15bf88e85a4917bc16e6c55710fe43-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1181, '2025-04-19', 'COINs', 'A line of 10 coins with the same number changes to a coin with one higher number. Coins can be moved anywhere, even to empty lines or on coins with different numbers. You can add coins at any time. The game is cleared if you make a coin with the number 10! The faster the clear time, the higher the score.', 'Tap to hold the coin and tap to place it.', 'Puzzle,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7ea5afdd37a64eac95cb0d7600d46065-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7ea5afdd37a64eac95cb0d7600d46065-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/7ea5afdd37a64eac95cb0d7600d46065/', '378', '672', 'evolution,number,sorting,speedrun,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'coins', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7ea5afdd37a64eac95cb0d7600d46065-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7ea5afdd37a64eac95cb0d7600d46065-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1182, '2025-04-19', 'Brick Game Classic', 'Brick Game Classic is a classic Tetris online game. If you are a fan of classic games, then this game that has been popular for many years is just right for you. When any row or column is filled, it is eliminated. You can change the shape of the cubes before they fall to eliminate them quickly. You can also make them fall faster if you are satisfied with their shape.  Now join the world of fun games.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/50060980890049a689afa0e9ac1bcdfb-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/50060980890049a689afa0e9ac1bcdfb-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/50060980890049a689afa0e9ac1bcdfb/', '750', '1334', 'tetris,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'brick-game-classic', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/50060980890049a689afa0e9ac1bcdfb-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/50060980890049a689afa0e9ac1bcdfb-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1183, '2025-04-19', 'Brain puzzles-Quests', 'This is the puzzle game filled with challenging, interesting tasks that will help you relax and have fun. There are games for training thinking, mental tasks, and IQ tests suitable for those who like to think. Develop logic, pump your brains!', 'Carefully read the task on the screen. It will let you know what needs to be done.\nUse your logic and ingenuity to solve problems. This may include dragging objects, clicking on various items on the screen, or performing other actions.\nIf you find it difficult to solve a puzzle, think outside the box or try different approaches.\nIf you get stuck, you can use hints. Usually, to get hints, you need to watch commercials or spend in-game currency.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b031b8f60a614bfba9246610fcbccb8a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b031b8f60a614bfba9246610fcbccb8a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b031b8f60a614bfba9246610fcbccb8a/', '600', '800', 'logical,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'brain-puzzles-quests', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b031b8f60a614bfba9246610fcbccb8a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b031b8f60a614bfba9246610fcbccb8a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1184, '2025-04-19', 'Transformers Battle For The City', 'In this game you will find an open world where you will defend the city from the invasion of robots. If you are a fan of transformers, then you will definitely like this game. \nIn the game you will find 7 full-fledged story tasks, the complexity of which will gradually increase. After receiving the task, you will go to the place of military operations, where you can use various super-techniques to destroy powerful robot villains.', 'Control in the game.\n\nThe car:\n\nWASD-Movement.\nSpace bar - Brake.\nLeft mouse button - shooting with machine guns.\nT - Transformation into a robot.\nEsc - Pause.\n\nRobot:\nWASD-Movement.\nLeft Shift - Running.\nLeft mouse button - Easy attack.\nRight mouse button - Medium attack.\nMiddle mouse button - Heavy attack.\nT - Transformation to a car.\nEsc - Pause.', 'Adventure,Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/284f0df3cc504fd3a36b5093698c8e41-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/284f0df3cc504fd3a36b5093698c8e41-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/284f0df3cc504fd3a36b5093698c8e41/', '800', '600', 'attack,car,robot,transformation,3d', 0, 0, 0, 'transformers-battle-for-the-city', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/284f0df3cc504fd3a36b5093698c8e41-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/284f0df3cc504fd3a36b5093698c8e41-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1185, '2025-04-19', 'Spin Shot Siege', 'In \"Spin Shot Siege,\" take control of a gunner on a rotating tower. Enemy tanks orbit around you in the opposite direction. Each level has tanks following paths like diamonds, circles, rectangles, or triangles. Aim carefully and destroy all tanks before running out of ammo. Can you master the spin and win the siege?', 'Tap the screen to fire when a tank is in front of your gun. The tower rotates automatically, so aim and shoot at the perfect moment.', 'Shooter,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3b98f63e687e4f70a3386d811c5878e6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3b98f63e687e4f70a3386d811c5878e6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3b98f63e687e4f70a3386d811c5878e6/', '960', '1280', 'guns,shoot-em-up,tank,bullet,target,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'spin-shot-siege', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3b98f63e687e4f70a3386d811c5878e6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3b98f63e687e4f70a3386d811c5878e6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1186, '2025-04-19', 'Landmine Cube', 'In Landmine Cube you will you will take the role of a rolling cube that has to collect all the jewels in each level, without step on the landmines scattered around the floor. Every time you step on one of them, you will lose a life. If you lose all the lives, you will have to restart the level from the ground up. Do not worry, the Cube knows when a landmine is near, and it will start to glow boldly. Try your best and complete all the 21 levels of this engaging puzzle game!     ', 'use WASD / Arrow Keys / Touch the on-screen arrows to move the cube ', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fbe2045a5fab4fc0beb7331920a07641-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fbe2045a5fab4fc0beb7331920a07641-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/fbe2045a5fab4fc0beb7331920a07641/', '720', '1280', 'classic,collect,memory,thinking,mining,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'landmine-cube', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fbe2045a5fab4fc0beb7331920a07641-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fbe2045a5fab4fc0beb7331920a07641-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1187, '2025-04-19', 'Nesting Dolls', 'Embark on an exciting adventure with an addictive puzzle game that will challenge your mind and soothe your soul. Immerse yourself in a world of bright colours and intricate Russian matryoshka dolls as you complete tasks to clear the field and become a true matryoshka doll master.', 'The aim of the game is to clear the whole field. You have to drag the nesting dolls to the bottom tier. Three nesting dolls of the same colour disappear and make room. Be careful, if the bottom tier fills up, you lose.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b6bb84607ef44a3da7b25d929605ab29-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b6bb84607ef44a3da7b25d929605ab29-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b6bb84607ef44a3da7b25d929605ab29/', '800', '600', 'doll,logic,logical', 0, 0, 0, 'nesting-dolls', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b6bb84607ef44a3da7b25d929605ab29-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b6bb84607ef44a3da7b25d929605ab29-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1188, '2025-04-19', 'Bouncy Blob Race: Obstacle Course', 'Bouncy Blob Race: Obstacle Course is an exciting physics-based racing game. Guide a bouncy blob through challenging obstacles with just one click. The blob will move in the opposite direction of the thrust. Maneuver through the course and beat your opponent to the finish line. Grab power-ups for an extra boost and secure victory in this thrilling race!', 'Tap/click to Thrust To Blob and the blob will move in the opposite direction of the thrust.', '.IO', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6cec11b225764338a9d67a11f68bdc69-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6cec11b225764338a9d67a11f68bdc69-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6cec11b225764338a9d67a11f68bdc69/', '900', '600', 'ball,bounce,physics,2players,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bouncy-blob-race-obstacle-course', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6cec11b225764338a9d67a11f68bdc69-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6cec11b225764338a9d67a11f68bdc69-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1189, '2025-04-19', 'Idle Drive: Merge, Upgrade, Drive', 'Welcome to Idle Drive: Merge Upgrade &amp; Drive! Unleash your creativity, craft a unique vehicle for travels. Start with a basic car, enhance it using in-game currency earned by tapping. Accumulate funds for components like engines and tires. Merge parts for higher levels, boosting speed and power. Visit the garage to customize your car. Idle DriftDrive offers exhilarating fun and satisfaction of creating your own ride. Perfect for car enthusiasts and racing fans. Exciting moments await you!', 'Simply tap on the screen and earn money! Use it to buy new parts, and then upgrade them by merging two parts of the same level. ', 'Casual,Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/83f80b1451554638b7a480535ab42a31-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/83f80b1451554638b7a480535ab42a31-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/83f80b1451554638b7a480535ab42a31/', '900', '600', 'car,challenge,idle,upgrade,clicker,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'idle-drive-merge-upgrade-drive', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/83f80b1451554638b7a480535ab42a31-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/83f80b1451554638b7a480535ab42a31-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1190, '2025-04-19', 'Super Bitcoin Boy', 'Super Bitcoin Boy is a Mario Bros style platform game, themed around the Bitcoin cryptocurrency, eliminate enemies, overcome obstacles, collect all the bitcoins to get the highest score possible. Enjoy the Halving year, have fun playing and complete all levels.', 'On the computer, use the \"AWSD\" arrow keys to move.\n\nOn mobile, use the arrow keys on the screen to move.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cf86048ca4ac4c8e823e295ba7cfe65b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cf86048ca4ac4c8e823e295ba7cfe65b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cf86048ca4ac4c8e823e295ba7cfe65b/', '1280', '720', '1player,platformer,bitcoin,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'super-bitcoin-boy', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cf86048ca4ac4c8e823e295ba7cfe65b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cf86048ca4ac4c8e823e295ba7cfe65b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1191, '2025-04-19', 'Pull The Thread - Puzzle', 'Unwind your mind with Pull The Thread - Puzzle, a captivating HTML5 game that challenges your logic and creativity! In this fun puzzle game, your task is to stretch a thread between all the screws on the screen, creating intricate patterns while solving each level. As the puzzles grow more complex, your problem-solving skills will be put to the test. With simple controls, engaging gameplay, and a satisfying sense of accomplishment.', 'Use the mouse or touchscreen to pull the end of the thread.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/40b6cfabcb1c464a8465dfa756fb69ed-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/40b6cfabcb1c464a8465dfa756fb69ed-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/40b6cfabcb1c464a8465dfa756fb69ed/', '640', '1024', '1player,dots,family,connection,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'pull-the-thread-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/40b6cfabcb1c464a8465dfa756fb69ed-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/40b6cfabcb1c464a8465dfa756fb69ed-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1192, '2025-04-19', 'Timberland Arrange Puzzle Game', 'Arrange the animals and color them!  refreshing reinterpretation of classic Tag and Sudoku. Assemble a logical puzzle by finding intersections between different types of hints. Enjoy colorful hand-drawn graphics, fascinating sounds of nature and cheerful cries of animals!\n\nIt may seem that the game is quite simple. However, level by level you will dive deeper into the rabbit hole, discover new mechanics, and the number of combinations will increase reaching hundred thousand!', 'The goal is to find a suitable place for each animal on the field and paint them in 3 colors, finding intersections between different types of hints.\n\nUse the buttons to select the beast, then click on the desired cell on the field and the beast will be carved in stone. Then choose a color, click on the beast again, one stroke of the brush, and it will come to life! Each of the 9 pets has its own character.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/89b674adbc344c52b3e92fa0e435aacc-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/89b674adbc344c52b3e92fa0e435aacc-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/89b674adbc344c52b3e92fa0e435aacc/', '1920', '1080', '1player,animal,logic,relax,colormatch,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'timberland-arrange-puzzle-game', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/89b674adbc344c52b3e92fa0e435aacc-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/89b674adbc344c52b3e92fa0e435aacc-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1193, '2025-04-19', 'Trial Xtreme', 'Trial Xtreme is an exciting game in which you have to get a new experience from driving a motorcycle. Experience a sea of adrenaline while riding a motorcycle and passing 30 levels with dizzying and spectacular obstacles.', 'The player needs to go through the entire track from beginning to end, there will be many obstacles on the way, various jumps, obstacles, pipes, stones and everything in that spirit are painted in such a way that the user cannot pass the track without falls and difficulties. During the race, you need to collect as many stars as possible, depending on the collected stars, the next track will open for you.', 'Racing & Driving,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/04425491014a4c64a7578f725ba51415-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/04425491014a4c64a7578f725ba51415-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/04425491014a4c64a7578f725ba51415/', '800', '600', '1player,bicycle,bike,motorbike,motorcycle,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'trial-xtreme', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/04425491014a4c64a7578f725ba51415-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/04425491014a4c64a7578f725ba51415-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1194, '2025-04-19', 'Fill Glass', 'Fill Glass is a simple yet addictive game. Fill the glass to the perfect level without letting it overflow or fall short of the target. Precision is key as you pour, aiming for the highest highscore!\nAs you progress, upgrade your pouring machine to enhance your accuracy!', 'Mobile: tap to where you want the liquid to pour to move the dispenser\nPC: Move the dispenser with mouse and click to pour the liquid', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6bfc0c6ffa5b42958fd5cff50654b96c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6bfc0c6ffa5b42958fd5cff50654b96c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6bfc0c6ffa5b42958fd5cff50654b96c/', '720', '1280', '2d,endless,drink,singleplayer,Kids Friendly,No Blood,No Cruelty', 0, 0, 0, 'fill-glass', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6bfc0c6ffa5b42958fd5cff50654b96c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6bfc0c6ffa5b42958fd5cff50654b96c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1195, '2025-04-19', 'Party Games Mini Shooter Battle', 'Party Games: Mini Shooter Battle is a battle-royale shoot-em-up game with 2D cartoon models. In 4 modes, you can shoot other players to earn scores for coins and gems. Then you can buy more roles and guns in the Shop. Your character can aim at the closest target automatically so that you only need to fire and dodge bullets from enemies. More kills and less death will make you claim more coin and gem rewards. Good luck!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/96ff43f7b5594faa9de94b25abab24b7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/96ff43f7b5594faa9de94b25abab24b7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/96ff43f7b5594faa9de94b25abab24b7/', '1280', '720', 'shoot-em-up,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'party-games-mini-shooter-battle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/96ff43f7b5594faa9de94b25abab24b7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/96ff43f7b5594faa9de94b25abab24b7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1196, '2025-04-19', 'Paint Master', 'Paint Master is a fun casual puzzle game. The homeowner has arranged a strict painting plan for you, you need to arrange the painters to paint in a certain order. Match your paint color with the owner\'s arrangement and you will be the winner. If there is a difference, the owner will return you to work.', 'How to play:\n1. Observe the schematic diagram given at the top;\n2. Determine the order of painting based on the available patterns;\n3. Click on the painter to work;', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/47e30ffac22a4599b2c7529d923a94a0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/47e30ffac22a4599b2c7529d923a94a0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/47e30ffac22a4599b2c7529d923a94a0/', '720', '1280', 'decoration,logic,painting,relaxing,2048,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'paint-master', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/47e30ffac22a4599b2c7529d923a94a0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/47e30ffac22a4599b2c7529d923a94a0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1197, '2025-04-19', 'Draw To Home 3D', 'Draw to home is a game to draw lines home. Everyone needs to return home according to their respective homes. This type of puzzle game is full of adventure with avoiding traps and obstacles on the way to finding a house.\n\nPlay a game of drawing a line to get home. It is very fun for children or teenagers to fill their days with this fun game.', '- Touch people and draw a line to the house\n- Draw a line towards the house according to the color of the person', 'Adventure,Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4ffc67d23949459ab936de05eebd1da6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4ffc67d23949459ab936de05eebd1da6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4ffc67d23949459ab936de05eebd1da6/', '1920', '1080', '1player,drawing,find,activity,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'draw-to-home-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4ffc67d23949459ab936de05eebd1da6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4ffc67d23949459ab936de05eebd1da6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1198, '2025-04-19', 'Hex Planet Idle', 'Hex Planet Idle is both an RPG adventure game and a survival idle game with 3D models. You can control a stickman warrior to discover the whole universe by collecting resources and unlocking new areas. When you step on the white lighting areas, you will know the resource request of the next area. Get close to any items to collect them automatically. If I were you, I would unlock all areas because of the plentiful resources.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f797a7d83750414fae3c86418fbaf56c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f797a7d83750414fae3c86418fbaf56c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f797a7d83750414fae3c86418fbaf56c/', '720', '1280', '1player,rpg,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'hex-planet-idle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f797a7d83750414fae3c86418fbaf56c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f797a7d83750414fae3c86418fbaf56c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1199, '2025-04-19', 'Candy Color Sort Puzzle', 'Welcome to our addictive and fun ball sort color puzzle game! If you\'re looking for a game that challenges your brain and keeps you entertained for hours, you\'ve come to the right place. You\'ll never get bored. Our game is perfect for those who enjoy brain teasers, puzzles, and games that challenge their cognitive skills. \n', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0d1caa7e39dd47acb82ce4bb37a4e301-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0d1caa7e39dd47acb82ce4bb37a4e301-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0d1caa7e39dd47acb82ce4bb37a4e301/', '800', '600', '1player', 0, 0, 0, 'candy-color-sort-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0d1caa7e39dd47acb82ce4bb37a4e301-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0d1caa7e39dd47acb82ce4bb37a4e301-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1200, '2025-04-19', 'Blockapolypse Zombie Shooter', 'Blockapolypse: Zombie Shooter is a defense shooting simulation game with 3D pixel undead creatures. To defend this position, you need to use weapons to defend incoming zombies from 3 directions. After you kill all zombies, you still need to defeat a giant undead creature. As long as you lose all of your HP, you will lose the game. When you earn enough gold coins, you can buy better weapons in the gun shop. Good luck and survive!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Shooter,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/827331e3831541baa8ee51d63d6ceec2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/827331e3831541baa8ee51d63d6ceec2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/827331e3831541baa8ee51d63d6ceec2/', '1280', '720', 'shoot-em-up,zombie', 0, 0, 0, 'blockapolypse-zombie-shooter', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/827331e3831541baa8ee51d63d6ceec2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/827331e3831541baa8ee51d63d6ceec2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1201, '2025-04-19', 'Moto Road Rash 3D 2', 'Rev up your engines and feel the thrill of the open road in Moto Road rash 3D 2! This high-octane motorcycle game immerses you in a heart-pounding racing experience where agility and precision are your best allies. Zoom through a dynamic, ever-changing cityscape, weaving between lanes, dodging traffic, and mastering daring stunts.', 'WASD/Arrow keys - Race/Steer/Brake', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0d6c422de82f4f6b832697ed1da3c0b7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0d6c422de82f4f6b832697ed1da3c0b7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0d6c422de82f4f6b832697ed1da3c0b7/', '960', '600', 'bike,car,rider,traffic,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'moto-road-rash-3d-2', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0d6c422de82f4f6b832697ed1da3c0b7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0d6c422de82f4f6b832697ed1da3c0b7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1202, '2025-04-19', 'Block Dropping Merge', 'Block Dropping Merge is a special but classic number merge puzzle. It\'s easy to play but hard to master.\nShow us how good you are among other puzzlers!\n\n1024 2048 4096 8192 16384... Drop them numbers and merge to get bigger numbers and show how smart you are!\n\nPlay and share your best score now!', '- You will be given numbers to play and count\n- Drop the number block at bottom or beside to merge\n- Keep merging to avoid losing the game!\n- If it is too tricky, check your next number block and plan your next move!', 'Casual,Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e13c14074f36411886a70ef94f2d0a92-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e13c14074f36411886a70ef94f2d0a92-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e13c14074f36411886a70ef94f2d0a92/', '1920', '1080', 'block,logic,matching,tetris,2048,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'block-dropping-merge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e13c14074f36411886a70ef94f2d0a92-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e13c14074f36411886a70ef94f2d0a92-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1203, '2025-04-19', 'Zombie Highway Rampage', 'Drive your Rhino truck through hordes of zombies in this zombie apocalypse game.\n\nAvoid incoming obstacles such as land mines, bounders, cars and other hazard materials.\n\nShoot and destroy obstacles with bullets.', 'Run over zombies for coins in this intense driving and shooting game!', 'Racing & Driving,Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/755f4af98e77469aa7733336ea8acea1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/755f4af98e77469aa7733336ea8acea1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/755f4af98e77469aa7733336ea8acea1/', '1280', '720', '1player,car,endless,zombie', 0, 0, 0, 'zombie-highway-rampage', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/755f4af98e77469aa7733336ea8acea1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/755f4af98e77469aa7733336ea8acea1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1204, '2025-04-19', 'Vex X3M', 'VEX X3M, a new extreme hill racing game with bike stunts and obstacles, is here! \nEnjoy the classic Vex elements, but this time you will be racing your way to the finish line! \n\nPerform crazy bike stunts in 30 unique levels filled with danger - from spikes and shooting knives to rockets and lasers. Reach the finish safely and obtain stars to unlock new unique bike skins.\n\nComplete all levels in easy and hard mode to crown yourself a master VEX X3M Rider.\n\nStart your engines and enjoy VEX X3M! ', 'Press up (or W) to accelerate, use left (or A) and right (or D) to tilt your bike and press backwards (or S) to brake. Look at your surroundings and pay attention to all the traffic signs! Good luck!', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0a3c55fe33ba415f9b761b5831e75b27-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0a3c55fe33ba415f9b761b5831e75b27-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0a3c55fe33ba415f9b761b5831e75b27/', '800', '600', '1player,bike,biker,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'vex-x3m', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0a3c55fe33ba415f9b761b5831e75b27-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0a3c55fe33ba415f9b761b5831e75b27-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1205, '2025-04-19', 'Tile Farm Story - Matching Game', 'Are you tired of your dull daily routine? Discover the magical world of the remote corners of the Earth where life is in harmony with nature. Help the heroines in the game build parks and nature reserves in the most exotic countries and populate them with the greatest variety of animals. But first, they will have to solve the mystery of the inheritance that the Stone sisters were left by their mysterious Grandpa.   ', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c07885e726eb4d87af0b120b4e8c8638-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c07885e726eb4d87af0b120b4e8c8638-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c07885e726eb4d87af0b120b4e8c8638/', '800', '600', '1player,2d,animal,build,building,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'tile-farm-story-matching-game', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c07885e726eb4d87af0b120b4e8c8638-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c07885e726eb4d87af0b120b4e8c8638-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
