(1206, '2025-04-19', 'Ball Tower of Hell', 'Ball in hell rolling his way to the top of the tower. There are many difficulties on the way, but the brave ball not scared ', 'wasd + mouse', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7a02dc15cbe34498b82dd0281a359829-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7a02dc15cbe34498b82dd0281a359829-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/7a02dc15cbe34498b82dd0281a359829/', '800', '600', 'arcade', 0, 0, 0, 'ball-tower-of-hell', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7a02dc15cbe34498b82dd0281a359829-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7a02dc15cbe34498b82dd0281a359829-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1207, '2025-04-19', 'Wooden bolts and nuts', 'As you play, you\'ll find tangled screws, nuts, bolts, plates, rings, ropes, and more. Find out how to solve the riddle. It\'s not just a game, it\'s a journey through the many fun nuts and bolts of the game.', 'The goal of the game is to unscrew bolts and transfer them to empty cells! Unscrew all the bolts from the planks so that they fall down. Then you will pass the level.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7af952d994104a128cd4bb51c8c207c7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7af952d994104a128cd4bb51c8c207c7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/7af952d994104a128cd4bb51c8c207c7/', '1920', '1080', 'construction,logic,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'wooden-bolts-and-nuts', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7af952d994104a128cd4bb51c8c207c7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7af952d994104a128cd4bb51c8c207c7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1208, '2025-04-19', 'BitGoblins RPG Simulator', 'Become the protector of the kingdom from goblin robbers!\n\nGet stronger by fighting goblin armies! Upgrade your hero with every battle, earn gold and get new items\n\nDefeat the leaders of the goblins - the ogres! Gain strength after fighting goblin armies and test your skills\n\nExplore the possibilities of this game! Start as a young wizard and upgrade your abilities, get new equipment and become the menace of goblins.', 'Increase your hero\'s level by pressing the upgrade buttons.\nYour hero is a superhero. He never dies.\nDefeat bosses and special bosses.\nWin in different game modes to earn more gold and crystals.', 'Adventure,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e2757a6abddd43ce9ce4a671ad3dfc75-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e2757a6abddd43ce9ce4a671ad3dfc75-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e2757a6abddd43ce9ce4a671ad3dfc75/', '1920', '1080', 'fantasy,magic,rpg,sword,battlefield,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bitgoblins-rpg-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e2757a6abddd43ce9ce4a671ad3dfc75-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e2757a6abddd43ce9ce4a671ad3dfc75-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1209, '2025-04-19', 'Simon Super Rabbit', 'Simon and his friends have turned into superheroes and now they must look for the evil Professor Wolf and get their marbles back.\nGrrr That boastful and braggart Professor Wolf and his minions dont want to give the marbles back to Simon and they have challenged him to a super mega competition which he must win to get them back. If you beat him, he will be giving the marbles back to you. Surely you can win and get them all back. Go for it!', 'Help Simon, Gaspard, Lou and Ferdinand beat Professor Wolf in 3 amazing events which only a superhero can win but be careful with the cheater Professor Wolf!\n', 'Adventure,Educational', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2a58aca09449458393812b26e76573af-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2a58aca09449458393812b26e76573af-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2a58aca09449458393812b26e76573af/', '800', '600', 'animal,kidgames,arcade,Kids Friendly', 0, 0, 0, 'simon-super-rabbit', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2a58aca09449458393812b26e76573af-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2a58aca09449458393812b26e76573af-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1210, '2025-04-19', 'Beauty puzzle', 'A puzzle game in which you need to connect the pieces in a line. To successfully complete the game, it is important to use its mechanics to your advantage', '1. Connecting the lines will be easy at first, but as time goes by, the speed will increase.  Once you connect a line, it will disappear and earn you points!  If the playing field overflows and a piece is on a line and stays on it for a long time, you will lose and start the game over!\n2. Press and hold your finger or mouse to control the game. Tap the screen to make the figure scroll or swipe down to make the figure fall. \n3. enjoy the game, become the leader and top the list!', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/71238afd932b41fb940cfc337d9d6187-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/71238afd932b41fb940cfc337d9d6187-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/71238afd932b41fb940cfc337d9d6187/', '800', '600', '1player,2d,tetris', 0, 0, 0, 'beauty-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/71238afd932b41fb940cfc337d9d6187-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/71238afd932b41fb940cfc337d9d6187-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1211, '2025-04-19', 'My Farm Empire', 'My Farm Empire is a fun and relaxing game that lets you create your own farm paradise on a beautiful island. You will become a farmer and grow various crops, from fruits and vegetables to flowers and herbs. You will also enjoy the stunning graphics, the smooth gameplay, and the rewarding progression system that will make you feel like a real farmer. My Farm Empire is more than just a game, its a lifestyle. Join the My Farm Empire today and start your farming adventure.', 'Drag and swipe = move\n', 'Casual,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3dc7fa33ba0b4ab78fd9370bebe05a25-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3dc7fa33ba0b4ab78fd9370bebe05a25-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3dc7fa33ba0b4ab78fd9370bebe05a25/', '1334', '750', 'collect,farm,stickman,Kids Friendly,No Blood,No Cruelty', 0, 0, 0, 'my-farm-empire', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3dc7fa33ba0b4ab78fd9370bebe05a25-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3dc7fa33ba0b4ab78fd9370bebe05a25-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1212, '2025-04-19', '100 Rooms Escape', 'This is a brain-burning and challenging escape room online game. Interesting gameplay so you won\'t get bored. You need to open 100 doors to escape the room. Interact with objects and solve puzzles to complete the tasks in the escape game. Solve the puzzles, and take inventory of the hidden items. You may use them to open the room, move on to the next level, use your skills, and do whatever it takes to escape.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dbba47ed5b3548fc9356c4c5ce289956-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dbba47ed5b3548fc9356c4c5ce289956-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/dbba47ed5b3548fc9356c4c5ce289956/', '1280', '720', 'roomescape,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, '100-rooms-escape', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dbba47ed5b3548fc9356c4c5ce289956-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dbba47ed5b3548fc9356c4c5ce289956-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1213, '2025-04-19', 'Northern Lights - the secret of the forest', 'A new hit for fans of the Match 3 game genre!\n\nThe Scientist Cat is already hiding items throughout the mysterious forest so you can enjoy finding things and earn as many emeralds as possible. The cat is happy to have new guests!', '- Combine identical objects and get new achievements\n- Open up territories\n- Meet your favorite childhood characters in person\n- New adventures open every day', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cd722a3ebb8549c7b9929ac5c7240328-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cd722a3ebb8549c7b9929ac5c7240328-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cd722a3ebb8549c7b9929ac5c7240328/', '800', '600', '2d,cat,cute,farm,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'northern-lights-the-secret-of-the-forest', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cd722a3ebb8549c7b9929ac5c7240328-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cd722a3ebb8549c7b9929ac5c7240328-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1214, '2025-04-19', 'Spot&Differs', 'A new exciting game \"Spot&amp;Differs\" for children and adults! Find differences between two pictures and train your brain and mindfulness. If you like to play logic games, join us!', 'Open the game and start passing levels - find the differences between the pictures.\nIn each level, you need to find 5 or more differences within the time limit.\n\nComfortable game control: find the differences with touches (tap) on the phone or tablet screen, use the mouse on the computer.\n\nIf you can\'t advance or find differences, use hints!', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a4e1d77b8c1b4ab3b1c1d3d0faa1f12a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a4e1d77b8c1b4ab3b1c1d3d0faa1f12a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a4e1d77b8c1b4ab3b1c1d3d0faa1f12a/', '1920', '1080', 'colorful,find,hidden,logic,differences,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'spot-differs', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a4e1d77b8c1b4ab3b1c1d3d0faa1f12a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a4e1d77b8c1b4ab3b1c1d3d0faa1f12a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1215, '2025-04-19', 'Thor Merge', 'Dive into Norse mythology in Thors Merge! \nMerge planets representing the Nine Realms to create even bigger worlds. \nPlay solo to reach the highest score or battle others in PvP mode to climb the leaderboard and achieve ultimate glory in Asgard!', 'Computer:\n-Mouse: Drag the planet left or right and click to drop.\n-Keyboard: Use the left and right arrow keys to move the planet and the space bar to drop it.\n\nMobile: Drag the planet left or right with your finger and release to drop it.', 'Casual,Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5a12e99c2997451f98813349fa7e8d46-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5a12e99c2997451f98813349fa7e8d46-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5a12e99c2997451f98813349fa7e8d46/', '1080', '1920', '2players,arcade', 0, 0, 0, 'thor-merge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5a12e99c2997451f98813349fa7e8d46-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5a12e99c2997451f98813349fa7e8d46-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1216, '2025-04-19', 'Devs Simulator', 'Welcome to the world of high technology and business! In this exciting strategy game you will become the director of a thriving IT company. Your task is to find the best programmers, assemble a dream team and lead it to success!', 'The goal of the game is to develop and expand your IT company by managing its resources, hiring qualified employees, improving equipment and software, as well as attracting customers and earning profit. The player must strive for the growth and success of his company, achieving high results and becoming a leader in the technology industry.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1a26f58eb0ef4eb391958b750bec3d44-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1a26f58eb0ef4eb391958b750bec3d44-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1a26f58eb0ef4eb391958b750bec3d44/', '800', '600', 'idle,upgrade,computer,clicker,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'devs-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1a26f58eb0ef4eb391958b750bec3d44-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1a26f58eb0ef4eb391958b750bec3d44-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1217, '2025-04-19', 'Poppy Player Puzzle', 'Solve the riddle of this fun game. In each of the many stages of Poopy Player Puzzle, the small player must use his or her wits to direct the doll to the right keys that will release it from captivity.The goal of the game is to rescue the small doll from Poppy\'s clutches to progress through the levels, you\'ll need to keep an eye on the things in the labyrinth; pressing certain buttons may speed up the game or remove hazards.', 'Play by dragging the player\'s hand to the key, then hit the corresponding button to unleash the level\'s traps. Navigate the labyrinth in the right way.\nControls\nUse the mouse to play or touch the screen on touch devices.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b92b5c18ad964762a544734172c80b70-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/b92b5c18ad964762a544734172c80b70-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/b92b5c18ad964762a544734172c80b70/', '900', '600', 'drawing,levels,clicker', 0, 0, 0, 'poppy-player-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b92b5c18ad964762a544734172c80b70-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/b92b5c18ad964762a544734172c80b70-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1218, '2025-04-19', 'Fashionista Avatar Studio Dress Up', 'It is a fun, creative dress-up and hairstyling game for all ages. Players mix and match outfits, hairstyles, and accessories to create stylish looks. The game features cute characters, diverse clothing options, and a salon scene for designing unique hairstyles, colors, and headpieces. Enjoy endless fashion fun and creativity in a joyful, relaxed atmosphere.', 'Tap to choose and dress up.', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8b9f8b20d5114013b7be3e95ccb101f8-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8b9f8b20d5114013b7be3e95ccb101f8-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8b9f8b20d5114013b7be3e95ccb101f8/', '1334', '750', '2d,fashionista,hair,girlsdressup,girls', 0, 0, 0, 'fashionista-avatar-studio-dress-up', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8b9f8b20d5114013b7be3e95ccb101f8-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8b9f8b20d5114013b7be3e95ccb101f8-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1219, '2025-04-19', 'Guess Word', 'Guess Word is a free online puzzle and word game for boys played on PuzzleGame. It\'s easy to play. You have six chances to guess words. The letter you guessed will change color to give you a hint. This tests your vocabulary. The game is simple and very suitable for players of all ages. Mobile, Tablet, and Desktop are playable! We have three modes for you. Challenge yourself!', 'Mouse or tap to play', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fdf1b9b4c4cf49048c02314500360a9d-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fdf1b9b4c4cf49048c02314500360a9d-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/fdf1b9b4c4cf49048c02314500360a9d/', '750', '1334', 'guessing,boys', 0, 0, 0, 'guess-word', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fdf1b9b4c4cf49048c02314500360a9d-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fdf1b9b4c4cf49048c02314500360a9d-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
