(1375, '2025-04-19', 'Block Eating Simulator', 'The battle of the blocks begins in the block\'s arena with this great eating simulator game. Eat blocks around and grow your cube. Become the biggest block of the arena. Find various cube skins. Play single or 2 player! Cube players are all around the arena and they are eating blocks, cubes, and lower-scored players. Each block you eat will give you some points. Try to eat as many blocks as possible and try to eat low-scored players. Try to get to the top of the leaderboard. ', 'The game is both played single and two player.\n\nPlayer 1: W,A,S,D\nPlayer 2: ARROW KEYS\n\nOn single player mode:\nControl the camera by LEFT-CLICK and MOUSE\nControl the camera zoom with: MOUSE SCROLL\n\nUse Joystick controls on mobile devices/tablets.', '.IO', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5fc3261d72e6452f91c9fbd224991222-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5fc3261d72e6452f91c9fbd224991222-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5fc3261d72e6452f91c9fbd224991222/', '800', '600', 'block,cube,arena,2players,eat', 0, 0, 0, 'block-eating-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5fc3261d72e6452f91c9fbd224991222-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5fc3261d72e6452f91c9fbd224991222-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1376, '2025-04-19', 'Toy Cars: 3D Racing', 'Jump into the car and participate in this racing experience. Compete with other racers, participate in various challenges and time-limited events. Prepare your car and drift. Upgrade your carriage. The engine, tires and chassis improve the overall performance of your car.', 'The goal of the game is to get to all races first.\nPC control: WASD - control of a toy car\nControl on a mobile device: touch/swipe', 'Racing & Driving,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/43faeb3504ea49bdbee8221caf3ef80f-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/43faeb3504ea49bdbee8221caf3ef80f-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/43faeb3504ea49bdbee8221caf3ef80f/', '800', '600', 'car,crash,parking,timekiller,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'toy-cars-3d-racing', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/43faeb3504ea49bdbee8221caf3ef80f-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/43faeb3504ea49bdbee8221caf3ef80f-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1377, '2025-04-19', 'Politon', 'Politon is a turn-based strategy game with easy-to-understand mechanics and satisfying visuals. If you want to test your strategical logic against enemies of different numbers and difficulty levels, Politon offers a variety of hex-based maps with various terrains. You\'ll need to manage your economy while expanding your territories and defend your region against rival invasions.\n', 'Point and click on tiles to select the region you want to manage. Then click on building cards to select which units you want to recruit. Expand your regions by moving units around and defeat your enemies.', 'Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f0de10012d244cc586ae05cf4c6bb408-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f0de10012d244cc586ae05cf4c6bb408-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f0de10012d244cc586ae05cf4c6bb408/', '1920', '1080', '1player,2d,real-time-strategy,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'politon', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f0de10012d244cc586ae05cf4c6bb408-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f0de10012d244cc586ae05cf4c6bb408-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1378, '2025-04-19', 'Puzzle lub', 'In this puzzle game you need to connect the pieces in a line. To successfully complete the game, use its mechanics to your advantage.', '1. Connecting the lines will be easy at first, but the speed will increase with time. As soon as you connect a line, it will disappear and you will get points! If the playing field fills up and the piece remains on the line, you will lose and you will have to start the game again!\n\n2. Press and hold your finger or mouse button to control the game. Tap the screen to make the piece scroll, or swipe down to make it fall.\n\n3. Enjoy the puzzle, become the best and top the leaderboard!', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fa9200967482491f8bd3cd7b3fae524c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fa9200967482491f8bd3cd7b3fae524c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/fa9200967482491f8bd3cd7b3fae524c/', '800', '600', '1player,2d,tetris,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'puzzle-lub', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fa9200967482491f8bd3cd7b3fae524c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fa9200967482491f8bd3cd7b3fae524c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1379, '2025-04-19', 'Caillou Chef', 'In \"Caillou Chef,\" Caillou puts on his apron and takes on the role of a chef in a fun and challenging caf. The goal of the game is to help Caillou prepare delicious coffees and pancakes for his customers, effectively managing time to keep everyone happy with the service.\n', 'Pancake Preparation: Place batter on the stove, watch the time to avoid burning, and add requested toppings (jam, cream, chocolate).\nCoffee Service: Serve coffee according to customer orders.\nTime Management: Manage multiple stoves and coffee makers as difficulty increases. Ensure quick service to keep customer satisfaction high.\n', 'Cooking,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d119302cb9f84bae926d787b8e08d3f6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d119302cb9f84bae926d787b8e08d3f6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d119302cb9f84bae926d787b8e08d3f6/', '800', '600', 'cook,kidgames', 0, 0, 0, 'caillou-chef', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d119302cb9f84bae926d787b8e08d3f6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d119302cb9f84bae926d787b8e08d3f6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1380, '2025-04-19', 'Unblock It 3D', 'Power up your logic and spatial reasoning skills with Unblock It 3D! Rotate the cluster of bricks to find unblocked tiles you can slide away without hitting any obstructions. \n\nPlay Classic Mode and enjoy hundreds of intricate puzzles with unlimited moves, new cube designs and backgrounds to unlock.\n\nOr, journey through time in Adventure Mode. Try your hand at 25 additional levels of increasing complexity and size. Explore Ancient Egypt, Medieval Europe, the Aztec Empire, feudal Japan, and more.', 'Clear the entire cluster of blocks by sliding them in an open direction. Each cube has an arrow on it. If its not blocked by other bricks, you can swipe it away. \n\nTap and drag to spin the camera around the big cube. Search all sides and discover your next move. Watch out - the blocks come in different sizes!\n\nIn adventure mode, you also have to keep an eye on the limited move count. Think strategically to avoid wasting moves on blocked tiles.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bb321f67a2fc481ba31308582f3df0d5-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bb321f67a2fc481ba31308582f3df0d5-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bb321f67a2fc481ba31308582f3df0d5/', '800', '600', 'block,journey,logic,3d,singleplayer,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'unblock-it-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bb321f67a2fc481ba31308582f3df0d5-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bb321f67a2fc481ba31308582f3df0d5-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1381, '2025-04-19', 'Emerland Solitaire', '     Welcome to the wonderful country of Emerland! \n     Dive deep into the world of magical tale where great mages battle for the Source of the ancient magic of the Cards! Explore mysterious lands accompanied by heroes that include a noble Knight, an Elven Archeress and a mystical Sorceress to defeat the malevolent Dark Master! \n     Solve puzzles and collect combinations to complete difficult and varied levels! Get rewards and find new assistants! ', 'Use the left mouse button to interact with in-game UI.', 'Cards', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a8d2dd3ae70d464d9e36029a038ffb09-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a8d2dd3ae70d464d9e36029a038ffb09-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a8d2dd3ae70d464d9e36029a038ffb09/', '800', '600', '1player,magic,relaxing', 0, 0, 0, 'emerland-solitaire', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a8d2dd3ae70d464d9e36029a038ffb09-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a8d2dd3ae70d464d9e36029a038ffb09-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1382, '2025-04-19', 'Join Clash Color Button', 'Are you ready for a game of choices and surprises? Color Button is the game for you! You need to pick the right door and make it to the end safely. But be careful, each door can lead to a different challenge or enemy. You have to use your skills and strategies to avoid traps and obstacles. Teamwork is the key to success in this game. Color Button is an exciting game that tests your judgment and decision-making skills. Do you have what it takes to beat the enemies and reach the end? ', 'Tap to play', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d10b01d306fb4e09afdb1c5c9208d761-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d10b01d306fb4e09afdb1c5c9208d761-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d10b01d306fb4e09afdb1c5c9208d761/', '750', '1334', 'avoid,collect,arcade', 0, 0, 0, 'join-clash-color-button', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d10b01d306fb4e09afdb1c5c9208d761-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d10b01d306fb4e09afdb1c5c9208d761-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1383, '2025-04-19', 'Magic Finger Puzzle 3d', 'Magic Finger Puzzle 3D is an interesting casual puzzle online game. You have an amazing pair of  hands that can fire the laser. It can help you smash the cages that are holding you. It can also\n  launch boxes onto barricades so that you can escape from the cage without stepping on spikes and dying. But don\'t worry, you need to use your ingenuity to make good use of those amazing hands. All difficulties will be solved. Join the game if you want to try a journey full of adventure.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9ba79172eea743d78c002c1c4091b422-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9ba79172eea743d78c002c1c4091b422-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9ba79172eea743d78c002c1c4091b422/', '750', '1334', '3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'magic-finger-puzzle-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9ba79172eea743d78c002c1c4091b422-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9ba79172eea743d78c002c1c4091b422-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1384, '2025-04-19', 'Shape Transform Race', 'Shape Transform Race is a fun racing game that can be played in reaction-based 1 and 2 player game modes. You can play the game against bots or against your friend. Always be the fastest by choosing the right vehicle for the terrain! You can unlock new vehicles and characters with the coins you earn from the races.\n\n', 'You can use \"MOUSE\" or touch controls to change vehicles.\nFor 2 player mode, you can use \"A,S,D\" and \"J,K,L\" keys for shortcuts to change vehicles.', 'Racing & Driving,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4983f8202e43488894571f56bab784e2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4983f8202e43488894571f56bab784e2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4983f8202e43488894571f56bab784e2/', '1920', '1080', '1player,running,vehicle,2players,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'shape-transform-race', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4983f8202e43488894571f56bab784e2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4983f8202e43488894571f56bab784e2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1385, '2025-04-19', 'Hungry Snake Io', 'Hungry Snake.io is a classic game. Here you can try three game modes, Endless mode, Toilet Man, and Monster Brawl. Please note that there can be no collision between worms! In addition, our team takes user experience very seriously, we are always happy to improve the game so that every player can have a better gaming experience, if you encounter any difficulties during the game, please feel free to leave us a message!', 'Mouse click or tap to play\n', '.IO', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a6195768e1d945678a79772c2e5dfc1f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a6195768e1d945678a79772c2e5dfc1f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a6195768e1d945678a79772c2e5dfc1f/', '1560', '720', 'classic,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'hungry-snake-io', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a6195768e1d945678a79772c2e5dfc1f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a6195768e1d945678a79772c2e5dfc1f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1386, '2025-04-19', 'Zombie Arena 2 Fury Road', 'The player assumes the role of a driver in Zombie Arena 2 Fury Road, whose objective is to navigate a confined arena populated by zombies while using their vehicle as a weapon to overcome waves of the undead and unlock new levels.\n\nAlso, there are modes where you have to beat the clock or fend off waves of zombies, respectively, and games where you have to live as long as possible.', 'In the main campaign, you\'ll have to complete a number of objectives where you have to do things like wipe out zombies from the battlefield and demolish regions that are filled with zombies.', 'Racing & Driving,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6bdeacb49a324925829f9bed83cd6d96-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6bdeacb49a324925829f9bed83cd6d96-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6bdeacb49a324925829f9bed83cd6d96/', '800', '600', 'car,survival,zombie', 0, 0, 0, 'zombie-arena-2-fury-road', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6bdeacb49a324925829f9bed83cd6d96-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6bdeacb49a324925829f9bed83cd6d96-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1387, '2025-04-19', 'Fennec The Fox Click Adventure', 'Embark on a cosmic adventure with Fennec the Fox! Tap your way across the desert, unlocking upgrades that transform Fennec into a powerful cosmic traveler.  Explore new worlds, face thrilling challenges, and evolve Fennec to reach the stars. Can you guide Fennec to the farthest reaches of the universe? Start clicking and discover the wonders that await!', 'Click on Fennec: Start by tapping on Fennec the Fox to earn points and progress through the game.\n\nUpgrade Fennec: Use your points to purchase upgrades that boost Fennec\'s abilities and speed up your progress.\n\nEvolve and Advance: As you level up, Fennec will evolve, unlocking new powers and moving from the desert to increasingly advanced environments.\n\nReach the Universe: Your ultimate goal is to guide Fennec from the desert sands to the farthest reaches of space.', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c8489d47ad3649c7a21ae421803c72c0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c8489d47ad3649c7a21ae421803c72c0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c8489d47ad3649c7a21ae421803c72c0/', '800', '600', 'arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'fennec-the-fox-click-adventure', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c8489d47ad3649c7a21ae421803c72c0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c8489d47ad3649c7a21ae421803c72c0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1388, '2025-04-19', 'Hexa Tile Master', 'Welcome to Hexa Tile Master! Drag stacks of hex tiles from the bottom of your screen to empty spots on the board. Watch as similar tiles merge into bigger stacks, and collect stacks of 10 or more matching tiles to clear them. Your goal is to clear all the hex tiles before time runs out. Each level gets more challenging, but don\'t worryfun animations and exciting rewards will keep you engaged. Enjoy the strategic fun and see how far you can go!', 'You can move stacks using touch or mouse.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/54059d2d0e4d4599a2e4644fe0474218-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/54059d2d0e4d4599a2e4644fe0474218-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/54059d2d0e4d4599a2e4644fe0474218/', '960', '1280', 'hexagon,stack,colormatch,sorting,real-time-strategy', 0, 0, 0, 'hexa-tile-master', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/54059d2d0e4d4599a2e4644fe0474218-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/54059d2d0e4d4599a2e4644fe0474218-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1389, '2025-04-19', 'Block Puzzle Cats', 'Train your brain and solve puzzles with cute cats! Drag and drop the cats onto the puzzle board and try to put them all together! Unique puzzle shapes and ever-changing challenges will train your brain to think in a whole new way. Can you fit all the cats in? Collect cute new cats as you beat each puzzle challenge.Now come and join the fun and challenging game world.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c43e8d972eb9459f8f0ee9a09a3fa8a7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c43e8d972eb9459f8f0ee9a09a3fa8a7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c43e8d972eb9459f8f0ee9a09a3fa8a7/', '1080', '1920', 'cat,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'block-puzzle-cats', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c43e8d972eb9459f8f0ee9a09a3fa8a7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c43e8d972eb9459f8f0ee9a09a3fa8a7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1390, '2025-04-19', 'Skyscraper to the Sky', 'Challenge your skills as an engineer and architect in this  puzzle game. Build the tallest, most stable skyscraper across 30 levels, from small houses to huge buildings.', 'In Skyscraper to the Sky, players build tall skyscrapers by connecting building floors. A single mistake can cause a collapse, adding excitement. The intuitive interface allows easy placement of floors and monitoring of stability. The goal is to build the tallest, most stable skyscraper across 30 levels, from small houses to huge buildings.', 'Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/14ea4bedde164885aa01278fdbd65352-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/14ea4bedde164885aa01278fdbd65352-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/14ea4bedde164885aa01278fdbd65352/', '800', '600', '1player,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'skyscraper-to-the-sky', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/14ea4bedde164885aa01278fdbd65352-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/14ea4bedde164885aa01278fdbd65352-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1391, '2025-04-19', 'Unpuzzle Master', 'Unpuzzle master plan and execute your moves strategically to become the master, navigating through bottlenecks and utilizing exit strategies effectively.\n\nTouch the tile to move it in the direction of the tile. Complete each level that really challenges your brain to think sharper.\n\nChoose from a variety of themes and skins to customize your block-puzzle adventure. Each skin not only changes the visual aesthetic but also improves the way you interact with the puzzles, making every move count.', 'PC : Use the left mouse button to move block.\n\nMobile : Touch a tile to move the block.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e53138467dc14ecfbd6c3c666583d4af-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e53138467dc14ecfbd6c3c666583d4af-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e53138467dc14ecfbd6c3c666583d4af/', '720', '1280', '1player,block,2048,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'unpuzzle-master', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e53138467dc14ecfbd6c3c666583d4af-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e53138467dc14ecfbd6c3c666583d4af-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1392, '2025-04-19', 'Indygirl and the Golden Skull', 'The girl \nwho loves to uncover hidden treasures and adventures. She now found the \nGolden Skull and now ready come and needs your help dig into the cave! Your \ntask is help Indygirl in her journey to collect all the jewels and golds that are \nhidden in the cave. Focus on getting gold! Run as fast as \nyou can before that gigantic rock will run over you!', 'Save yourself from the Skull.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0447b6e77a524f1fb079b6f996aa56db-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/0447b6e77a524f1fb079b6f996aa56db-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/0447b6e77a524f1fb079b6f996aa56db/', '800', '600', '1player,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'indygirl-and-the-golden-skull', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0447b6e77a524f1fb079b6f996aa56db-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/0447b6e77a524f1fb079b6f996aa56db-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1393, '2025-04-19', 'Practice On Me', 'Get ready for a glamorous summer adventure with Practice On Me, the ultimate makeup game! Transform into a festival goddess, beach babe, or blooming flower child in three exciting themed units. Grab your brushes, swipe on lipstick, and let your inner artist shine. Dance at festivals, relax by the beach or embrace nature\'s beauty. With Practice On Me, the possibilities are endless. Make waves, channel your inner mermaid, and bloom like a flower. Experience a summer adventure like no other!', 'Use your mouse to play this game on desktops, or tap to play on mobile devices.', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/af88d35ad8ef4ca29640dadba1c8dc85-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/af88d35ad8ef4ca29640dadba1c8dc85-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/af88d35ad8ef4ca29640dadba1c8dc85/', '1024', '768', 'beauty,makeup,manicure,summer,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'practice-on-me', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/af88d35ad8ef4ca29640dadba1c8dc85-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/af88d35ad8ef4ca29640dadba1c8dc85-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1394, '2025-04-19', 'Basketball.io Dunk Sport', 'Sports Basketball is a thrilling 3D basketball game that will keep you entertained for hours. Whether you\'re a basketball fan or just love fast-paced Sports games Fun', 'Basketball IO is a thrilling 3D basketball game that will keep you entertained for hours. Whether you\'re a basketball fan or just love fast-paced games, Basketball IO is perfect for you. With easy gameplay using either the keyboard\'s arrow keys or WASD or mouse click and drag, you can dribble, dodge, and score against opposing teams in offline games.', 'Basketball', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/591a5f6390cd4a2a95782ef203bc7438-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/591a5f6390cd4a2a95782ef203bc7438-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/591a5f6390cd4a2a95782ef203bc7438/', '1080', '1920', 'ball,basket,sport,champion,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'basketball-io-dunk-sport', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/591a5f6390cd4a2a95782ef203bc7438-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/591a5f6390cd4a2a95782ef203bc7438-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1395, '2025-04-19', 'Cleaning Simulator', 'Cleaning Simulator is a very fun simulation game. Although this game is 2D, it restores the shape of objects in real life very well. This game has a total of 12 parts, covering sports cars, technological products, daily necessities, and other elements, which will definitely meet all your\nexpectations for cleaning games. Want to know more about this game? Come and try it!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2c0a09f82dc04768ab98e946b9f42812-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2c0a09f82dc04768ab98e946b9f42812-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2c0a09f82dc04768ab98e946b9f42812/', '720', '1280', 'cleaning,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cleaning-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2c0a09f82dc04768ab98e946b9f42812-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2c0a09f82dc04768ab98e946b9f42812-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1396, '2025-04-19', 'Bike Stunt Racing Legend', 'Bike Stunt Racing Legend is not merely a motorcycle racing but also a balanced stunt simulation game. Under a 3D game engine, you are required to ride the motorbike to the finish line in the first place. As long as you can keep high speed, the AI opponent will make mistakes and lose you. Don\'t be afraid of rolling ramps, pass the green arrows to speed up more easily. Keep calm and step on the gas!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cc3eba0c3a1844ad9e7fe64812ffb8ed-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cc3eba0c3a1844ad9e7fe64812ffb8ed-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cc3eba0c3a1844ad9e7fe64812ffb8ed/', '1630', '750', 'motorbike,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bike-stunt-racing-legend', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cc3eba0c3a1844ad9e7fe64812ffb8ed-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cc3eba0c3a1844ad9e7fe64812ffb8ed-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1397, '2025-04-19', 'Turbo Car Track', 'Get ready for an exhilarating ride with Turbo Car Track! Navigate through winding tracks that get progressively more challenging as your speed increases. Collect gold coins to unlock new, more powerful vehicles and boost your progress. Can you handle the speed and conquer the track? Find out in this thrilling, high-speed adventure!', 'Movement: \"ARROW KEYS\" to Drive', 'Racing & Driving,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a198643d3153409b9c51fc908f170eea-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a198643d3153409b9c51fc908f170eea-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a198643d3153409b9c51fc908f170eea/', '934', '1040', 'car,crash,rider,speed,stunts,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'turbo-car-track', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a198643d3153409b9c51fc908f170eea-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a198643d3153409b9c51fc908f170eea-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1398, '2025-04-19', 'Hair Stack 3D', 'Hair Stack 3D is a hair running game. Go through the numbered doors and collect more hair. Dodge the obstacles that make you less in number. Your ultimate goal is to make more hair so that the bald head at the end can have beautiful hair! Are you ready to help him? Let him applaud you!', 'Slide to move', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6b27629fca9e4913b28c64846a6bdd16-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6b27629fca9e4913b28c64846a6bdd16-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6b27629fca9e4913b28c64846a6bdd16/', '720', '1280', 'relax,running,number', 0, 0, 0, 'hair-stack-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6b27629fca9e4913b28c64846a6bdd16-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6b27629fca9e4913b28c64846a6bdd16-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1399, '2025-04-19', 'CityMix Solitaire', 'Play card games, relax and train your memory and brain with CityMix Solitaire. Solitaire CityMix is more than just another game!\nWhich would you prefer: decorating and restoring a quiet town, or solving puzzles and seeking adventure on a lost island? With CityMix Solitaire you can decorate, solve puzzles and mysteries, follow adventures and help brave heroes. Vicky and her pet Raccoon will help in this challenging quest. ', 'Collect cards in the correct order. Complete game tasks. Help the residents of this cozy town and find out their history!', 'Cards', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/78f1fc2086bf4a3d93de850174ff5a28-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/78f1fc2086bf4a3d93de850174ff5a28-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/78f1fc2086bf4a3d93de850174ff5a28/', '1200', '650', 'city,decoration,relax,solitaire,story,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'citymix-solitaire', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/78f1fc2086bf4a3d93de850174ff5a28-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/78f1fc2086bf4a3d93de850174ff5a28-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1400, '2025-04-19', 'Stickman Leave Prison', 'You take control of two characters in Stickman Leave jail, a new entry in the stickman jail series. Your goal is to guide them to the level\'s finish as they search for the corresponding colored keys to unlock the door. The objective is to evade capture by the guards. Collect money spread over the level to unlock new, more skilled skins. As you go around the game, leap and avoid harmful things to arrive safely.', 'Find the key to change characters so you can move and get to the exits on time; the goal is to get all the stick figures to the door.\n\nEvery single stickman jail game is available right now on Kiz10 for free online play.\n\nA walkthrough:\nTo move and leap, use WASD.\nClick and hold on the screen to navigate and leap.', 'Adventure,Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5c1d43932d9a4c38bd730149b35cf5c5-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5c1d43932d9a4c38bd730149b35cf5c5-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5c1d43932d9a4c38bd730149b35cf5c5/', '900', '600', 'escape,prison,stickman', 0, 0, 0, 'stickman-leave-prison', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5c1d43932d9a4c38bd730149b35cf5c5-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5c1d43932d9a4c38bd730149b35cf5c5-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1401, '2025-04-19', 'Blastify II', 'Blastify II is a new addictive  tap-to-blast puzzle game. Easy to pick up and play, this game offers a delightful experience for all ages. With endless entertainment and a steady stream of new puzzles, you can enjoy playing for hours on end.', 'In this puzzle game, you should destroy the group of the same colored blocks in the puzzle board by tapping on them. You should collect the remaining blocks until you hit the target. Utilize four unique boosters to blast through obstacles and reach new heights.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/eda3319ebe62475ebe09bd81da2dc005-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/eda3319ebe62475ebe09bd81da2dc005-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/eda3319ebe62475ebe09bd81da2dc005/', '800', '600', 'colorful,matching,relax,tiles,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'blastify-ii', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/eda3319ebe62475ebe09bd81da2dc005-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/eda3319ebe62475ebe09bd81da2dc005-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1402, '2025-04-19', 'Just Dice - Random Tower Defence', '? Welcome to \"Just Dice: Random Tower Defense\"! Get ready to roll the dice and defend your territory against hordes of relentless monsters in this exciting tower defense game. With a unique merging mechanic and vibrant visuals, you\'ll be hooked from the very first roll!', '? In \"Just Dice: Random Tower Defense,\" you\'ll strategically place dice-shaped towers on the map to fend off waves of monsters. Each tower resembles a dice, with different numbers of dots indicating its power level.\n? To strengthen your defenses, merge two dice towers of identical dot counts to create a higher-level tower with increased firepower. Choose your merges wisely to build the most powerful defense against the relentless monster onslaught.', 'Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2e60df1aede34f8889fd208898cb3f8a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2e60df1aede34f8889fd208898cb3f8a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2e60df1aede34f8889fd208898cb3f8a/', '800', '600', '1player,board', 0, 0, 0, 'just-dice-random-tower-defence', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2e60df1aede34f8889fd208898cb3f8a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2e60df1aede34f8889fd208898cb3f8a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1403, '2025-04-19', 'Nugget Man Survival Puzzle', 'Are you ready for adventure with the Nugget man character? To save the Nugget Man character who is stranded in the desert, you must fly into the sky without bursting the balloons. You must be careful to take the character to the finish by solving the puzzles before time runs out, accompanied by Gedagedago music. Rescue Nugget Man through desert bandits, cacti and many other challenging obstacles! Enjoy.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/17a33f4057c54631ab56386df4449c13-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/17a33f4057c54631ab56386df4449c13-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/17a33f4057c54631ab56386df4449c13/', '1920', '1080', 'cartoon,sliding-puzzle,balance,kidgames,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'nugget-man-survival-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/17a33f4057c54631ab56386df4449c13-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/17a33f4057c54631ab56386df4449c13-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1404, '2025-04-19', 'Falling Man', 'Fall for fun in this addictive hypercasual game!\nReady for a wild ride? Join the thief as he falls from dizzying heights, dodging obstacles and collecting coins in this addictive hypercasual game. With two distinct locations to explore and endless possibilities for high scores, the fun never ends in this exciting game.', 'With simple one-tap controls and fast-paced gameplay, you\'ll be hooked from the start. Keep an eye out for power-ups like gravity boosts and magnets, and unlock new skins with the coins you collect.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e75e40efce7f4a00b4f72c045af90c07-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e75e40efce7f4a00b4f72c045af90c07-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e75e40efce7f4a00b4f72c045af90c07/', '800', '600', 'No Blood,No Cruelty', 0, 0, 0, 'falling-man', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e75e40efce7f4a00b4f72c045af90c07-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e75e40efce7f4a00b4f72c045af90c07-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1405, '2025-04-19', 'Pet Fall', 'You can move animals from side to side. You have to collect full horizontal lines to make them disappear. Some animals are frozen and must be released twice, some are locked in cages and cannot be moved. Use bonuses when necessary', 'Slide Pet blocks and create full lines. Move Pet blocks to empty positions and create full lines to remove lines.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/63189411738d462b8264943ab23f7de9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/63189411738d462b8264943ab23f7de9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/63189411738d462b8264943ab23f7de9/', '1280', '720', 'animal,fall,matching,pet,tetris', 0, 0, 0, 'pet-fall', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/63189411738d462b8264943ab23f7de9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/63189411738d462b8264943ab23f7de9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1406, '2025-04-19', 'Finger Heart Monster Refill', 'Do you love Finger Heart posing? Do you want to make Finger Heart with a cute character? Let\'s Play This Game. In Finger Heart: Monster Refill, you must choose how to fit your finger with other\nadorable monsters to form a perfect heart. To fill a perfect heart, you dont need any special skills, just use your imagination and creativity.  They can change its shape in many ways. You\'ll need to think carefully about which form fits the shape of your fingers. Come make hearts with cute monsters!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/49e5198f436d4ca19320000476913eb4-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/49e5198f436d4ca19320000476913eb4-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/49e5198f436d4ca19320000476913eb4/', '720', '1280', 'girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'finger-heart-monster-refill', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/49e5198f436d4ca19320000476913eb4-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/49e5198f436d4ca19320000476913eb4-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1407, '2025-04-19', 'Bus Collect', 'The aim of the Bus Collect game is to collect the passengers waiting on the road by making the right directions and deliver them to the finish point. To do this, direct the roads the vehicle will follow with arrow signs. Try to reach high scores by carrying as many passengers as possible to the finish point.', 'Use MOUSE to turn arrow signs and steer the car.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/99f5b2c35eec4f67ab74980ef9e4de8c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/99f5b2c35eec4f67ab74980ef9e4de8c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/99f5b2c35eec4f67ab74980ef9e4de8c/', '1920', '1080', '1player,bus,stick,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bus-collect', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/99f5b2c35eec4f67ab74980ef9e4de8c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/99f5b2c35eec4f67ab74980ef9e4de8c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1408, '2025-04-19', 'Sky Block Bounce', 'Welcome to Sky Block Bounce, the ultimate test of agility and strategy in a sky-high adventure! Your mission is simple yet exhilarating: jump on the blocks and navigate your way to the teleporter. But beware, each block behaves differentlysome will vanish after just one jump, while others can withstand two or more. ', 'Use Arrow keys or WASD to move.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dd5962af58ad4303af5701e75f84126c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/dd5962af58ad4303af5701e75f84126c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/dd5962af58ad4303af5701e75f84126c/', '854', '480', 'ball,bounce,collect,skill,Kids Friendly,No Blood,jumping', 0, 0, 0, 'sky-block-bounce', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dd5962af58ad4303af5701e75f84126c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/dd5962af58ad4303af5701e75f84126c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1409, '2025-04-19', 'Bubble Blitz Galaxy', 'Welcome to Bubble Blitz Galaxy! Aim and shoot bubbles towards similar ones to collect them while ensuring they stay away from the borderline. Experience two exciting modes: In Arcade Mode, strive to survive as long as possible and score as much as you can. In Challenge Mode, survive and achieve target scores, facing new challenges one after another. Get ready for an exhilarating bubble-blasting adventure!', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to aim and shoot bubbles towards similiar ones to collect them while ensuring they stay away from the borderline.', 'Bubble Shooter,Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e95f253e12154468bfe7a0f3cfe21f3a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e95f253e12154468bfe7a0f3cfe21f3a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e95f253e12154468bfe7a0f3cfe21f3a/', '1280', '720', 'bubble,matching,skill,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bubble-blitz-galaxy', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e95f253e12154468bfe7a0f3cfe21f3a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e95f253e12154468bfe7a0f3cfe21f3a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1410, '2025-04-19', 'Bridge Fight!', 'Stack Strategic bridges for your monster army to cross and defeat the monster enemies. Construct bridges wide enough to guide your army of monster characters to cross safely and face off against formidable foes. \nWith simple yet addictive gameplay, immerse yourself in a world of tactical challenges where every move counts. \nCan you lead your army to victory and claim dominance over your enemies? \n\nPlay Bridge Fight! now and let the fun begin!', 'Tap to stack the bricks and build the bridge. Drag around to move and avoid the Boss enemy', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1c67d3c872c84c75b57161228c7889d7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1c67d3c872c84c75b57161228c7889d7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1c67d3c872c84c75b57161228c7889d7/', '800', '600', 'building,color,stack,battlefield', 0, 0, 0, 'bridge-fight', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1c67d3c872c84c75b57161228c7889d7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1c67d3c872c84c75b57161228c7889d7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1411, '2025-04-19', 'Biking Extreme 3D', 'Do you like riding a mountain bike? Biking Extreme 3D offers you a chance to ride a mountain bike and challenge multiplayer mountain racing tracks. It doesn\'t matter when you crash any other riders on the track, they will be crashed into the sky. But please always keep a safe distance between your vehicle and obstacles like trees and rocks. Or else, you will lose the game directly. The coins you won are used to upgrade your bike. Don\'t forget to try another 5 characters!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a7f62a8b1b744a48bbc4bc8af4d33391-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a7f62a8b1b744a48bbc4bc8af4d33391-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a7f62a8b1b744a48bbc4bc8af4d33391/', '720', '1280', '1player,bike,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'biking-extreme-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a7f62a8b1b744a48bbc4bc8af4d33391-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a7f62a8b1b744a48bbc4bc8af4d33391-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1412, '2025-04-19', 'Slidee', 'In this sliding-puzzle game you will have to make your way by painting the walls. Along the way you\'ll encounter spikes, portals, and collapsing walls.', 'Use WASD or Arrow Keys to move / Touch-screen buttons\nR - Restart\nEsc - Menu', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fc9cebd79a564ab1bcd211387fb600b1-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fc9cebd79a564ab1bcd211387fb600b1-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/fc9cebd79a564ab1bcd211387fb600b1/', '1280', '720', 'arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'slidee', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fc9cebd79a564ab1bcd211387fb600b1-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fc9cebd79a564ab1bcd211387fb600b1-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1413, '2025-04-19', 'Stickman Ragdoll Playground', 'Build-A-Flop: The Sickman Playground is not just a gameit\'s a people\'s playground of laughter and creativity! With its whimsical world and endless opportunities for hilarity, it\'s sure to become a favorite among players of all ages.', 'mouse , arrow key ', 'Adventure,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cf1a420ece8c407aa9d62f5b710016dc-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cf1a420ece8c407aa9d62f5b710016dc-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cf1a420ece8c407aa9d62f5b710016dc/', '900', '600', 'boss,balance,3d', 0, 0, 0, 'stickman-ragdoll-playground', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cf1a420ece8c407aa9d62f5b710016dc-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cf1a420ece8c407aa9d62f5b710016dc-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1414, '2025-04-19', 'Duck Hunting Open Season', 'Are you ready to go on an exciting adventure in the heart of nature with Duck Hunting: Open Season? In this addictive matching game, your goal is to pass challenging levels by collecting bullets and shooting ducks.Make items of the same type explode by combining them in groups of three or more. Your goal is to collect bullets and hunt ducks. Also use various power-ups such as Explosives, rockets and special hammers to create bigger explosions and go faster. Have Fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/aaa57f7e703140b3935bc90eeead2bca-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/aaa57f7e703140b3935bc90eeead2bca-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/aaa57f7e703140b3935bc90eeead2bca/', '1920', '1080', 'cartoon,cute,kidgames,arcade,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'duck-hunting-open-season', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/aaa57f7e703140b3935bc90eeead2bca-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/aaa57f7e703140b3935bc90eeead2bca-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1415, '2025-04-19', 'Idle Inventor', 'Grow your industrial powerhouse: become a heavy machine titan of industry!\n\nManufacture cars, trucks, planes, military vehicles, and high-tech instruments for space exploration!\n\nWatch your factory grow from a single production line to a world-famous industrial powerhouse. And because youre automating, your factory keeps working while youre away - check in the morning,  its amazing to see how much money you made while sleeping\n\nTry it now, and see how the idle tycoon life suits you!', 'Use the mouse to manage your manufacturing empire.', 'Simulation,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4db06aa6190446ac9972b9014d3a0749-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4db06aa6190446ac9972b9014d3a0749-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4db06aa6190446ac9972b9014d3a0749/', '1920', '1080', 'car,creative,tycoon,clicker', 0, 0, 0, 'idle-inventor', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4db06aa6190446ac9972b9014d3a0749-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4db06aa6190446ac9972b9014d3a0749-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
