(1416, '2025-04-19', 'Candy Match 4', 'The long-awaited sequel to our popular Match 3 game! Candy Match 4 takes you on a delightful journey through the world of delicious candies. With incredible 4000+ levels you will enjoy endless fun combining candies, completing Daily Missions and Challenges, and discovering gifts along the way. Meet your friend Luffy the cat, who helps you navigate through tricky blockers and master the game. Experience one of the best Match 3 games ever!', 'Combine more candies of the same kind to get stronger power-ups! Go on an adventure through the beautiful world of candies with 4,120 levels. Help Luffy the cat remove stones and obstacles to collect candies or go treasure hunting. Beware of villains trying to stop you! Enjoy daily missions, challenges, and discover gifts along the way. Experience endless fun in this beautiful Match 3 game!', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/78d72ca2c6ca4eb788813ca8c49b57ea-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/78d72ca2c6ca4eb788813ca8c49b57ea-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/78d72ca2c6ca4eb788813ca8c49b57ea/', '800', '600', 'candy,matching,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'candy-match-4', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/78d72ca2c6ca4eb788813ca8c49b57ea-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/78d72ca2c6ca4eb788813ca8c49b57ea-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1417, '2025-04-19', 'TicToc Urban Outfits', 'Your favorite influencers are back, and this time, they are getting ready to have fun and dress up in urban fashion!  We\'ve gathered four of our most fashionable BFFs to show you all their hottest looks, so join us in getting started with the TicToc Urban Fashion dress up game for girls, and have a blast choosing their outfit of the day. Experiment with different styles, play with colors and don\'t forget to use cool accessories for stunning urban looks. ', 'Use your mouse to play this game.', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ada5c17a852d4aa28592238460bb9290-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ada5c17a852d4aa28592238460bb9290-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ada5c17a852d4aa28592238460bb9290/', '1024', '768', 'princess,dressing,fashion,outfit,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'tictoc-urban-outfits', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ada5c17a852d4aa28592238460bb9290-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ada5c17a852d4aa28592238460bb9290-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1418, '2025-04-19', 'Classic Labyrinth 3d Maze', 'Classic Labyrinth 3d - The wooden maze funny game with the steel ball everyone knows comes to your browser! Enjoy this classic marble maze labyrinth.  \n     \nFeatures:\n- Accurate ball physic simulation\n- Joystick Controler\n- Smooth ball movement\n- Personal highscores\n- 3 Star rating system\n- One coin per 3 Star finished level\n- Realistic sounds\n- Coins to continue, if you fail during the level.', 'Use mouse or arrow / wasd keys to move the steelball to the target. Avoid the holes and obstacles.\nCollect coins by finishing the level as fast as possible.\nUse the coins to continue after you fell into a hole.', 'Boardgames', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8a48992496624ba9a7541fc7682c8107-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8a48992496624ba9a7541fc7682c8107-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8a48992496624ba9a7541fc7682c8107/', '800', '600', '1player,maze,3d', 0, 0, 0, 'classic-labyrinth-3d-maze', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8a48992496624ba9a7541fc7682c8107-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8a48992496624ba9a7541fc7682c8107-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1419, '2025-04-19', 'Incredible Princesses and Villains Puzzle', 'A puzzle game for girls where the player has to collect puzzles with images of princesses and villains. The game features 50 tasks, the difficulty of which is gradually increasing. Each puzzle is unique, which contributes to the development of logical thinking, imagination and fine motor skills of the players. Let\'s start collecting puzzles and immerse ourselves in a world of magic and adventure with beautiful princesses and dangerous villains!', 'The game consists of 50 levels, the difficulty of which is gradually increasing. At each level, you need to assemble a puzzle with some fabulous female character. There is no time limit on the level, but at each level there is a timer. At the end of the game, you can find out the total time spent on completing the game and save this result to share with your friends. Depending on the gaming device, a computer mouse click or a simple touch of the touch screens is used to control.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8bccd73267d74f0c9a61a66ec32ec5ec-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8bccd73267d74f0c9a61a66ec32ec5ec-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8bccd73267d74f0c9a61a66ec32ec5ec/', '800', '600', 'princess,cute,historical,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'incredible-princesses-and-villains-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8bccd73267d74f0c9a61a66ec32ec5ec-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8bccd73267d74f0c9a61a66ec32ec5ec-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1420, '2025-04-19', 'Neon Rider', 'Ride, rotate, and rule the neon world in Neon Rider - the ultimate 2D motorbike game!\nNeon Rider is an electrifying 2D game where you control a motorbike on a neon obstacle course. Perform tricks mid-air to rack up points, with perfect landings earning you even more. Dodge obstacles, collect batteries for a fire mode, and fly through the stage for maximum points. Your goal? To go as far as possible in this neon-lit adventure! So start riding the Neon Ride of your life in Neon Rider!', 'Touch or click the screen to accelerate your neon bike. Avoid flipping the bike in the air by carefully controlling its speed. Ensure smooth landings to avoid game over. Navigate through obstacles and reach the goal to complete each level. Practice makes perfect  keep playing to master the neon tracks!', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3c48eb1a56064a83b3c2ca0acbe01bb2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3c48eb1a56064a83b3c2ca0acbe01bb2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3c48eb1a56064a83b3c2ca0acbe01bb2/', '800', '600', '1player,motorcycle,skill,speed,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'neon-rider', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3c48eb1a56064a83b3c2ca0acbe01bb2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3c48eb1a56064a83b3c2ca0acbe01bb2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1421, '2025-04-19', 'L.O.L. Surprise Game Zone', 'Hi, B.B.s, welcome to the big city of L.O.L. Surprise! where you will visit the coolest shops, full of games and surprises. \n', 'PLAY FUN MINIGAMES\nExplore the shops and buildings in the big city and have fun discovering funny minigames: solve puzzles, shop for you and other B.B.s, decorate the disco, learn other languages, make music, and lots more!\n\nCOMPETE WITH B.B.s\nFind the hidden words, test your knowledge about the L.O.L. connecting each BB with her LIL and her pet, win a game at checkers and tic-tac-toe, and try to win at other fun games.\n', 'Boardgames,Educational', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c0188a8d609a4a399e49cbd5ec7a689f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c0188a8d609a4a399e49cbd5ec7a689f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c0188a8d609a4a399e49cbd5ec7a689f/', '800', '600', 'kidgames,Kids Friendly', 0, 0, 0, 'l-o-l-surprise-game-zone', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c0188a8d609a4a399e49cbd5ec7a689f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c0188a8d609a4a399e49cbd5ec7a689f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1422, '2025-04-19', 'Cargo Skates', 'No obstacles, no matter how high, can stop me from collecting more goods.\nPass the obstacles and finally collect enough goods.\nNow, your supermarket can open', 'Swipe the screen to control character movement', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/425d512c97d84b4292aea4ffe826e570-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/425d512c97d84b4292aea4ffe826e570-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/425d512c97d84b4292aea4ffe826e570/', '600', '800', 'supermarket,boss,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cargo-skates', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/425d512c97d84b4292aea4ffe826e570-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/425d512c97d84b4292aea4ffe826e570-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1423, '2025-04-19', 'Jewel Legend Quest', 'The most legendary quest of your life begins! Miners from all around the world have come to get their hands on these precious gems. Join them in the effort and engage in various challenges while trying to dig out as many diamonds as possible.\n', 'Move and match identical diamonds into chains of 3 or more. You will be rewarded with explosive power-ups if you match 4 or more.\n', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bf8673b9e69f44e2b89dd950a41080fa-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bf8673b9e69f44e2b89dd950a41080fa-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bf8673b9e69f44e2b89dd950a41080fa/', '800', '600', 'jewels,logic,logical,Kids Friendly,No Blood,match3', 0, 0, 0, 'jewel-legend-quest', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bf8673b9e69f44e2b89dd950a41080fa-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bf8673b9e69f44e2b89dd950a41080fa-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1424, '2025-04-19', 'My Dreamy Flora Fashion Look', 'Welcome to My Dreamy Flora Fashion Look. Girls! You know that spring is on its way when you see the trees starting to bud and bloom, and the bulbs you planted last fall start to sprout out of the ground. Join with Ellie and their friends to celebrate the most beautiful and colorful season. ', 'Left Mouse Button click or Tap to Play', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/55a43f24d5d04c11a8414716d9e78bcc-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/55a43f24d5d04c11a8414716d9e78bcc-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/55a43f24d5d04c11a8414716d9e78bcc/', '800', '600', 'fashion,spring,girlsdressup,cutedressup,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'my-dreamy-flora-fashion-look', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/55a43f24d5d04c11a8414716d9e78bcc-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/55a43f24d5d04c11a8414716d9e78bcc-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1425, '2025-04-19', 'Mahjong Magic Islands', 'The wonderful world of the Magic Islands is in desparate need of magic to help restore the waning natural beauty of their ancient cities with a new wild energy. Tons of mythical creatures await your help throughout these scattered island. You are their only hope to be saved, fix these wonderful magic lands back to their former beauty!\n\nMahjong: Tile Match features classic mahjong solitaire in a uniquely original visual format.', 'Use the left mouse button to interact with in-game UI.', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3ae65937ea3e4cb29483d4e928024580-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3ae65937ea3e4cb29483d4e928024580-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3ae65937ea3e4cb29483d4e928024580/', '800', '600', '1player,relax,relaxing,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mahjong-magic-islands', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3ae65937ea3e4cb29483d4e928024580-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3ae65937ea3e4cb29483d4e928024580-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1426, '2025-04-19', 'Bubble Race Party', 'Cute characters race on the platform to collect water drops and fill the pools. To use the aquapark slides you need to fill the mini pools. Collect water drops and try to knock down the opponents. To get better, you can use bombs, booster boxes and doors that give positive bonuses. Try to finish first in this fun race!\n\nGame Features:\n- Colorful and fun map designs\n- 1 and 2 Player game modes\n- Different hats available for characters\n- Surprise bonuses and game mechanics', 'If playing single:\n\nMove: \"W,A,S,D\" or \"ARROW KEYS\" or \"MOUSE\"\n\nIf playing two player:\n\nPlayer 1:\nMove: \"W,A,S,D\"\n\nPlayer 2:\nMove: \"ARROW KEYS\"', '.IO,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cee74a8cc9e948eda08ecbddf2ec6e02-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cee74a8cc9e948eda08ecbddf2ec6e02-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cee74a8cc9e948eda08ecbddf2ec6e02/', '1920', '1080', '1player,arena,2players,aquapark,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bubble-race-party', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cee74a8cc9e948eda08ecbddf2ec6e02-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cee74a8cc9e948eda08ecbddf2ec6e02-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1427, '2025-04-19', 'Toy Assembly 3D', 'Assemble a wide variety of brick buildings and scenes in this classic constructor game. Start as a baby builder and level your way up to increasingly complex construction sets. This relaxing and\nsatisfying game is sure to bring you back to the imagination and fun of your childhood!  Find the right piece and simply tap to add it to your build.  Get hands-on fun without the clutter or accidentally stepping on toys.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d794f26575d7485a815b1677545bba11-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d794f26575d7485a815b1677545bba11-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d794f26575d7485a815b1677545bba11/', '720', '1280', '1player,build,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'toy-assembly-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d794f26575d7485a815b1677545bba11-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d794f26575d7485a815b1677545bba11-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1428, '2025-04-19', 'Jump Ball Classic', 'Jump Ball Classic is the best game to test your reflexes. Move your ball left and right to avoid obstacles and enjoy the thrilling moment! Once it hits, it will fail immediately. Concentrate and challenge for success!', 'Tap to jump', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a42d91608d7d44b9bb3722ea9ca55a5a-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a42d91608d7d44b9bb3722ea9ca55a5a-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a42d91608d7d44b9bb3722ea9ca55a5a/', '750', '1334', 'avoid,ball,classic,,jumping', 0, 0, 0, 'jump-ball-classic', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a42d91608d7d44b9bb3722ea9ca55a5a-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a42d91608d7d44b9bb3722ea9ca55a5a-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1429, '2025-04-19', 'Chrome Cars Garage', 'Dive into the world of car mechanics in this engaging hidden object game. After inheriting your grandpa\'s global network of garages, you take on the role of the new owner, with your Uncle Joe guiding you through the intricacies of the trade. Explore various locations, uncover hidden car parts, and learn the art of automotive repair. ', 'Explore and uncover hidden car parts in this captivating car mechanic hidden object game.', 'Adventure,Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/83225c0c2adc4f3a8241092ea85dec8d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/83225c0c2adc4f3a8241092ea85dec8d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/83225c0c2adc4f3a8241092ea85dec8d/', '1280', '720', '1player,car,hidden,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'chrome-cars-garage', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/83225c0c2adc4f3a8241092ea85dec8d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/83225c0c2adc4f3a8241092ea85dec8d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1430, '2025-04-19', 'Colored Bricks', 'Colored Bricks is a fun and simple endless game. There are colorful bricks and one on the top. You should move that one to the right or left. When it hits the same color brick, it will destroy all bricks of the row. The challenge is to improve your high score in the limited time that you have! Some bricks have extra time if you destroy them.', 'In the Colored Bricks game you may  swipe left or right to position the top brick.\nMatch Colors: Align it with a brick of the same color.\nEarn Extra Time: Destroy special bricks to gain extra time.\nAim for the highest score within the limited time!', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e4740d5887674a4baaaed656623290d2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e4740d5887674a4baaaed656623290d2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e4740d5887674a4baaaed656623290d2/', '800', '600', 'colorful,matching,colormatch,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'colored-bricks', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e4740d5887674a4baaaed656623290d2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e4740d5887674a4baaaed656623290d2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1431, '2025-04-19', 'Mental Hospital Escape', 'Mental Hospital Escape is an exciting hide-and-seek game. In total, it contains two modes, doctor and patient. If you choose a doctor, you need to capture all the patients within the time limit. If you are patient, you need to run as hard as you can in the time limit, climb rocks, dodge chases, and survive!', 'Mouse click and drag to move', 'Battle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4b8288b531524537947ee106a12baee8-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4b8288b531524537947ee106a12baee8-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4b8288b531524537947ee106a12baee8/', '720', '1280', 'doctor,escape,hospital,catch,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mental-hospital-escape', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4b8288b531524537947ee106a12baee8-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4b8288b531524537947ee106a12baee8-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1432, '2025-04-19', 'Robots Gone Wild', 'Robots Gone Wild is a thrilling survival game in a sci-fi world with captivating visuals and intense shooting mechanics. Your goal is to escape from rogue robots and destroy them while navigating through hazardous environments.\n\nTo survive, keep upgrading your character and weapons.\nImprove your armor, and unlock powerful guns to fend off waves of increasingly powerful robots. \n\nEngage in exciting battles, and explore beautiful environments that immerse you in the chaos of a world gone wild.', 'One finger control to navigate around attacking robots.\nShooting aims automatically at the closest enemy. \nKeep collecting blue dots and coins to upgrade your character', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/aad5f39332994669aa2e77bbae075ddf-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/aad5f39332994669aa2e77bbae075ddf-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/aad5f39332994669aa2e77bbae075ddf/', '720', '1280', 'survival', 0, 0, 0, 'robots-gone-wild', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/aad5f39332994669aa2e77bbae075ddf-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/aad5f39332994669aa2e77bbae075ddf-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1433, '2025-04-19', 'Organizer master', 'An engaging 3D puzzle with numerous levels. Find pairs and arrange objects so that everything fits. Develop spatial thinking and solve challenges. Enjoy high-quality 3D graphics in this captivating browser puzzle game.', 'The game is controlled using the mouse or your finger (if playing on a mobile device). Press the right mouse button or use your finger to drag and drop items to their desired locations.\n\nThe game offers various locations and levels, each of which may present different challenges. You\'ll need to sort items of the same type, find matching items, and try to fit the required quantity into a box.\n\nHints will accompany you throughout the game to ensure you don\'t get stuck and always know what to do!', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/88adc972f6bc4956be084fe44998a531-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/88adc972f6bc4956be084fe44998a531-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/88adc972f6bc4956be084fe44998a531/', '800', '600', 'cute,find,kidgames,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood,No Cruelty', 0, 0, 0, 'organizer-master', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/88adc972f6bc4956be084fe44998a531-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/88adc972f6bc4956be084fe44998a531-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1434, '2025-04-19', 'Idle Restaurant Tycoon', 'Do you want to be a unique restaurant manager? You can learn how to be a manager with the Idle Restaurant game. You may need some experts for cooking and serving. Hire a master chef, develop your staff, manage your finances and become the perfect boss. Also, dont forget to check your market for surprise gifts. You can play Idle Restaurant Tycoon in a simple way without the need to constantly click.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Cooking,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ef5a10fb8f474e4591c7bdbea67c232f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/ef5a10fb8f474e4591c7bdbea67c232f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/ef5a10fb8f474e4591c7bdbea67c232f/', '1920', '1080', 'cook,food,idle,tycoon,kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'idle-restaurant-tycoon', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ef5a10fb8f474e4591c7bdbea67c232f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/ef5a10fb8f474e4591c7bdbea67c232f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1435, '2025-04-19', 'Boss Market', 'You are the owner of your market. Customers are coming to buy various products. Collect these products and place them into correct stands so that customers can buy them. Collect money from customers and open new markets and become a market boss!', 'Collect products and sell them to customers and drum up your business!', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f14923827f2247a18f67481cfd520a3c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f14923827f2247a18f67481cfd520a3c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f14923827f2247a18f67481cfd520a3c/', '1920', '1080', '1player,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'boss-market', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f14923827f2247a18f67481cfd520a3c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f14923827f2247a18f67481cfd520a3c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1436, '2025-04-19', 'Horror Escape Granny Room', 'In case you are ready for a creepy adventure full of horror and exploration, then choose Horror Escape: Granny Room without hesitation! In our game, you are going to go on a dangerous journey.\nCollect clues and keys while trying to escape the clutches of horrible granny. Your path is full of dangers. You must dodge the monsters lurking in the dark corners.  To unlock these areas, you must collect keys and reveal secrets. What awaits you? Only time will tell.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/22b6b7c811d648489947c30ee7213b44-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/22b6b7c811d648489947c30ee7213b44-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/22b6b7c811d648489947c30ee7213b44/', '1560', '720', '1player,horror,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'horror-escape-granny-room', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/22b6b7c811d648489947c30ee7213b44-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/22b6b7c811d648489947c30ee7213b44-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1437, '2025-04-19', 'Headleg Dash Parkour', 'Touch controls have never been easier and more accurate! Run, jump, and climb walls just by tapping anywhere on. Pass the obstacles and raise the flag to complete the level. Difficult levels will make you addicted and feel challenged. complete all levels and try to unlock cute and cool skins', 'tap anywhere to jump and raise the flag to complete the level', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6403330940374ab8b521b2052e817039-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6403330940374ab8b521b2052e817039-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6403330940374ab8b521b2052e817039/', '1280', '720', 'avoid,platformer,run,arcade,speedrun,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'headleg-dash-parkour', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6403330940374ab8b521b2052e817039-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6403330940374ab8b521b2052e817039-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1438, '2025-04-19', 'Tiny Fighter - Unstoppable Run', '10 Levels of an exciting and action-packed game that brings player to a mysterious woods and castles. The game begins with a dramatic scenario in which a vampire has stolen the princess and the brave Tiny Knight is the only one who can save her.\n\nAs the princess is abducted, the Tiny Knight embarks on a quest to retrieve her by through dangerous woodlands and battle his way through the castle\'s maze. Along the journey, the knight must fight Orcs, Skeletons and win Dracula to save the princess!', 'Click to jump, double click to double jump', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6b69e13ddf994e2cbaee4afd2f214ddd-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6b69e13ddf994e2cbaee4afd2f214ddd-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6b69e13ddf994e2cbaee4afd2f214ddd/', '780', '360', '1player,fighting,knight,runner,No Blood,jumping', 0, 0, 0, 'tiny-fighter-unstoppable-run', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6b69e13ddf994e2cbaee4afd2f214ddd-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6b69e13ddf994e2cbaee4afd2f214ddd-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1439, '2025-04-19', 'Stickman Warrior Way', 'Epic battles, complex labyrinths with multiple paths and treacherous enemies await you in the game!\n\nYou will have to pass difficult tests in the fight against an ancient evil that wants to destroy all existing worlds.\n Only you can prevent the destruction of the universe and save other worlds from destruction.\n\n18 challenging levels and mazes are waiting for you.\n2 or more ways to pass the level\nSave this world to give the rest of the universe a chance!\n', 'Your goal is to collect the right amount of energy to open the portal and move to the next level.\n\nControls for PC:\nA - move left\nD - move right\nW  jump\nW+W - double jump\nSpacebar - punch\n\n Controls for mobile/tablet:\nVirtual left arrow - move left\nVirtual right arrow - move right\nVirtual jump button  jump\nVirtual attack button  punch\n', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3309b5f6170945ec908c10a884c18d28-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3309b5f6170945ec908c10a884c18d28-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3309b5f6170945ec908c10a884c18d28/', '1280', '720', '1player,platformer', 0, 0, 0, 'stickman-warrior-way', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3309b5f6170945ec908c10a884c18d28-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3309b5f6170945ec908c10a884c18d28-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1440, '2025-04-19', 'Mega Ramp Car Stunts', 'Mega Ramp Car Stunts plays like a hard-core stunt car-driving simulation game. With 3D obstacles on the track, you have a chance to challenge 10 levels in the Stunt Mode and 16 levels in the Giant Ramp mode. Whether you meet checkpoints or not, you need to drive the car to the finish line safely. Don\'t forget to buy better vehicles in the garage when you have enough green diamonds.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6e5613afd2dd4497bdd8eb73151de402-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/6e5613afd2dd4497bdd8eb73151de402-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/6e5613afd2dd4497bdd8eb73151de402/', '1334', '750', '1player,car,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mega-ramp-car-stunts', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6e5613afd2dd4497bdd8eb73151de402-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/6e5613afd2dd4497bdd8eb73151de402-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1441, '2025-04-19', 'Cube Connect', 'Move the blocks and guide the ball to the goal. After a period of time, the ball starts to move. Connect the paths quickly so that the ball doesn\'t fall. Some blocks can jump and some can warp.', 'Drag to move blocks.', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8ce04aa2cd7d4e8cb9a098e1e5d290b7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8ce04aa2cd7d4e8cb9a098e1e5d290b7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8ce04aa2cd7d4e8cb9a098e1e5d290b7/', '378', '672', 'ball,road,slide,sliding,sliding-puzzle,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cube-connect', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8ce04aa2cd7d4e8cb9a098e1e5d290b7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8ce04aa2cd7d4e8cb9a098e1e5d290b7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1442, '2025-04-19', 'Panda Adventure', 'A small panda has to go through many challenges to reach his home safely form school. there will be many challenges on the way', 'PC Keybord Run - arrow key right - left /  jump - arrow up key\nMobile - Touch Button', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f18a68b9ae1f42098e727af16753907a-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f18a68b9ae1f42098e727af16753907a-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f18a68b9ae1f42098e727af16753907a/', '800', '600', 'arcade,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'panda-adventure', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f18a68b9ae1f42098e727af16753907a-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f18a68b9ae1f42098e727af16753907a-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1443, '2025-04-19', 'Tank Battle.io', 'Players can control the tank to perform various exciting missions and defeat the enemy. Players will have to synthesize a variety of weapons for tanks.\nThere are many tanks in the game that you can choose according to your preference. While completing the task, you must avoid obstacles at any time, and also constantly resist fire from enemy tanks\nEach level mode has a different difficulty that you can choose from.\n\nThe higher the level, the higher the stable income received.', 'Activate your tank and shoot at the enemy\'s concentration area, destroying the enemy\'s armor.\nTake part in many new real-time challenge modes.\nComplete tasks of the assigned level and unlock new tanks.\nAs you continue to control the tank, it is necessary to use various gaming skills correctly.\n\nMobile:\nControl your tank to navigate the map using a virtual joystick\nPC:\nUse WSAD to move and click the red icon to shoot', '.IO,Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/02143684ea9943a691c58002542929fb-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/02143684ea9943a691c58002542929fb-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/02143684ea9943a691c58002542929fb/', '1280', '720', '1player,battlefield,3d', 0, 0, 0, 'tank-battle-io', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/02143684ea9943a691c58002542929fb-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/02143684ea9943a691c58002542929fb-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1444, '2025-04-19', 'Dice Merge', 'Dive into Dice Merge Challenges, a game that blends strategic merging with thrilling destruction!\nDice Merge Challenges offers intuitive gameplay that\'s easy to pick up.\nBut as you progress, the challenges become more mind-bending!\nCombine dice with identical numbers to trigger an explosion creating a new dice with a higher value.\nStrategically merge your dice to overpower obstacles and shatter every box! Are you ready to become the ultimate Dice Merge Champion? \n', 'Press Space, or Click on the drop button to drop a Dice.', 'Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7201965a39e8408fbbbb268f14557582-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7201965a39e8408fbbbb268f14557582-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/7201965a39e8408fbbbb268f14557582/', '800', '600', '1player,2d,dice,sliding-puzzle,2048,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'dice-merge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7201965a39e8408fbbbb268f14557582-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7201965a39e8408fbbbb268f14557582-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1445, '2025-04-19', 'Om Nom Bubbles', 'Get ready for Om Nom\'s challenging new adventure Om nom bubbles and help him shoot all those yummy candies! Shoot as many candies as possible and act fast because time is ticking!\nHelp Om Nom with his aiming laser and shoot as many candies as possible, because you have a timer! And don\'t worry, when you hit the wall, the candy bounces off of it to all the other candies, making the more risky and crazy moves even more viable! Try to collect as many candies of your color as possible. ', 'Shoot as many candies as possible, because you have a timer! And don\'t worry, when you hit the wall, the candy bounces off of it to all the other candies, making the more risky and crazy moves even more viable! Try to collect as many candies of your color as possible. A 10-hit chain will open the Fireball, a powerful ball that cuts bubbles as if it were nothing! Om Nom rewards you with powerful buffs like a giant bomb, more time, or even a bubble color change.', 'Agility', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/95474768c77547ccbb065f122ddcbae8-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/95474768c77547ccbb065f122ddcbae8-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/95474768c77547ccbb065f122ddcbae8/', '684', '1024', '1player,2d,bubble', 0, 0, 0, 'om-nom-bubbles', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/95474768c77547ccbb065f122ddcbae8-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/95474768c77547ccbb065f122ddcbae8-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1446, '2025-04-19', 'Insta Trends Galaxy Fashion', 'Embark on a fashionable trip to the center of the Universe with your favorite princesses while playing the Insta Trends: Galaxy Fashion dress-up game for girls. Elsa, Anna, Moana, Ariel, and Rapunzel recently found Planet Her, and they are super excited to share their new home with you. Fashion on this amazing planet is galaxy colored and centered around fashionable suits and out-of-this-world accessories. Discover them all while helping the girls choose their outfits for the day! Have fun!', 'Use your mouse to play this game.', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c6a974a21a894b0b8795f3a0bcef3fca-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c6a974a21a894b0b8795f3a0bcef3fca-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c6a974a21a894b0b8795f3a0bcef3fca/', '1024', '768', 'princess,bffs,dressing,fashion,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'insta-trends-galaxy-fashion', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c6a974a21a894b0b8795f3a0bcef3fca-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c6a974a21a894b0b8795f3a0bcef3fca-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1447, '2025-04-19', 'Two Dots Remastered', 'Welcome to Two Dots Remastered, a fun and popular HTML5 connecting game enjoyed by gamers of all ages! Two Dot Remastereds gameplay is straightforward: Match two or more dots in the same color (not diagonal ones) and then blast them! Enjoy playing Two Dots Remastered, the ultimate connecting game for gamers of all ages, and become a master at connecting dots!', 'Find two or more dots of the same color that are adjacent (horizontally or vertically). Draw a line connecting the dots to blast them and score points. Plan your moves to create longer chains for higher scores. Two Dots puzzle also has 4 in-game boosters along with in-game items like Anchor, Box, etc. Use boosters strategically to clear challenging levels. ', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d5264541f9104717b0a34ff9072b008c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d5264541f9104717b0a34ff9072b008c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d5264541f9104717b0a34ff9072b008c/', '800', '600', 'dots,dotconnect,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'two-dots-remastered', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d5264541f9104717b0a34ff9072b008c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d5264541f9104717b0a34ff9072b008c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1448, '2025-04-19', 'Idle Town Billionaire', 'Dive into the world of entrepreneurship by purchasing lots in the town and building a variety of businesses. This idle game allows your businesses to automatically generate profit, even while you\'re away. Hire managers to boost your earnings and optimize your operations. Expand your business empire by strategically investing in new properties and upgrades. ', 'Build and manage businesses in an idle game where profits grow automatically, even when you\'re away.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f0c4490e0dce48b08c119294c1338483-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f0c4490e0dce48b08c119294c1338483-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f0c4490e0dce48b08c119294c1338483/', '1280', '720', '1player,2d,business,idle', 0, 0, 0, 'idle-town-billionaire', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f0c4490e0dce48b08c119294c1338483-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f0c4490e0dce48b08c119294c1338483-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1449, '2025-04-19', 'GunFu Stickman 2', 'Armed with a pistol in each hand, take control of the famous Stickman from the \"Gun Fu\" series and blast through hordes of enemies!\n\nReflexes and reaction times will be challenged and put to the test as the never-ending onslaught gets faster and faster!\n\nUnlock more deadly guns and outfits, and customize your Stickman to suit your style!\n', ' Test your reflexes and fire guns in the coolest Stickmen shooting game ever!', 'Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/54051bd5a055495da4170bcabc1f5e56-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/54051bd5a055495da4170bcabc1f5e56-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/54051bd5a055495da4170bcabc1f5e56/', '800', '600', 'guns,stickman', 0, 0, 0, 'gunfu-stickman-2', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/54051bd5a055495da4170bcabc1f5e56-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/54051bd5a055495da4170bcabc1f5e56-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1450, '2025-04-19', 'Hole Battle.io', 'The battle between the holes is beginning in the arena! Pick your hole and join this battle! Eat fruits, planes, cars, and many things that come to mind, and grow as much as you can! Your goal is to eat things that are smaller than you and make your hole bigger than the enemy\'s. Avoid bigger holes and try to collect power-ups besides eatable items.\nFour different great maps are waiting for you:\n- 2048 Map\n- World Map\n- Stationary Map\n- Kitchen Map', 'On PC:\nMove: MOUSE\nBoost: LEFT-CLICK\n\nOn Mobile Devices/Tablets:\nUse Joystick and Boost buttons.\n\nEat smaller items, destroy smaller opponents, and avoid bigger enemies.', '.IO,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/872540e7a0214fb4bf3cb08034c37100-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/872540e7a0214fb4bf3cb08034c37100-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/872540e7a0214fb4bf3cb08034c37100/', '960', '600', 'animal,monster,hole,arena,eat,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'hole-battle-io', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/872540e7a0214fb4bf3cb08034c37100-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/872540e7a0214fb4bf3cb08034c37100-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1451, '2025-04-19', 'Ninja Time', 'Immerse yourself in the world of samurai and ninjas in Ninja Time. Stretch your bamboo stick to navigate increasingly complex levels, collecting coins for new ninja skins. Experience Japan\'s martial arts era and become the ultimate ninja legend!', 'Grow your stick to reach the next platform. ', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9fc57b5143884ff8832d0a3ff479475f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9fc57b5143884ff8832d0a3ff479475f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9fc57b5143884ff8832d0a3ff479475f/', '800', '600', 'highscore,skill,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'ninja-time', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9fc57b5143884ff8832d0a3ff479475f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9fc57b5143884ff8832d0a3ff479475f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1452, '2025-04-19', 'Bubiloons', 'Funny, witty, bubbling and very magical these are the Bubiloons, some cute unicorn animals full of surprises that you will discover in this App.', 'Navigate through the app by swiping (touchscreen devices) or clicking (mouse devices) on the screen elements as directed.', 'Care,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8fce672918da40ff92bdb1d57ddd97b4-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/8fce672918da40ff92bdb1d57ddd97b4-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/8fce672918da40ff92bdb1d57ddd97b4/', '800', '600', 'bath,kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bubiloons', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8fce672918da40ff92bdb1d57ddd97b4-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/8fce672918da40ff92bdb1d57ddd97b4-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1453, '2025-04-19', 'GT Cars Mega Ramps', 'Exotic cars, mega ramps, colorful giant bosses and face to face races all come together in this game. GT Cars Mega Ramps invites you to a fantastic driving experience with its completely unique game-play. Fly over mega ramps with your customized exotic car, destroy giant bosses or try to finish the stages first in face to face races!', 'If playing single:\n\nMove: \"W,A,S,D\" or \"ARROW KEYS\"\nNOS: \"L-SHIFT\"\nRestart car position: \"R\"\nChange camera view: \"C\"\n\nIf playing two player:\n\nPlayer 1:\nMove: \"W,A,S,D\"\nNOS: \"L-SHIFT\"\nRestart car position: \"R\"\nChange camera view: \"C\"\n\nPlayer 2:\nMove: \"ARROW KEYS\"\nNOS: \"N\"\nRestart car position: \"L\"\nChange camera view: \"U\"', 'Racing & Driving,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/24113c58bbd347569687d35efc5ef900-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/24113c58bbd347569687d35efc5ef900-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/24113c58bbd347569687d35efc5ef900/', '1920', '1080', '1player,crash,boss,2players,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'gt-cars-mega-ramps', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/24113c58bbd347569687d35efc5ef900-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/24113c58bbd347569687d35efc5ef900-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1454, '2025-04-19', 'Human Evolution Run', 'Start with a skeleton, choose your evolution route.', 'Swipe the screen to control character movement', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2a950e44abd1427aa75da753601d516d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/2a950e44abd1427aa75da753601d516d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/2a950e44abd1427aa75da753601d516d/', '600', '800', '1player,alchemy,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'human-evolution-run', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2a950e44abd1427aa75da753601d516d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/2a950e44abd1427aa75da753601d516d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1455, '2025-04-19', 'Chain Cube 2048 3D Merge Game', 'Ready to challenge yourself? Chain Cubes 2048 is an addictive merging puzzle online game for those who like challenging brain teasers and logic puzzle merging games. Believe it or not, it\'s much\nharder to put together 2048 cubes than it is to throw away the numbers. If you fail to merge the cube number blocks, they will bounce off each other!  Keep playing and eventually complete 2248 number puzzles!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/45c9c545b6014eb1a6d8b8cb206fd1a0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/45c9c545b6014eb1a6d8b8cb206fd1a0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/45c9c545b6014eb1a6d8b8cb206fd1a0/', '720', '1280', '1player,2048,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'chain-cube-2048-3d-merge-game', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/45c9c545b6014eb1a6d8b8cb206fd1a0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/45c9c545b6014eb1a6d8b8cb206fd1a0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1456, '2025-04-19', 'Idle Firefighter 3D', 'Idle Firefighter 3D is a single player firefighter simulator game. You will play the role of a firefighter and it is your duty to save the survivors from the fire. Here, new emergencies are constantly occurring and you need to be on standby and must put out the fires as soon as possible! The fire extinguisher is your friend, if the props run out, you will not be able to put out the fire.', 'Slide to move', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a2e511cd27e74371b61d3cfbca6f3f33-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a2e511cd27e74371b61d3cfbca6f3f33-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a2e511cd27e74371b61d3cfbca6f3f33/', '750', '1334', 'fire,idle,relax', 0, 0, 0, 'idle-firefighter-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a2e511cd27e74371b61d3cfbca6f3f33-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a2e511cd27e74371b61d3cfbca6f3f33-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
