(1457, '2025-04-19', 'Tiny Cars', 'Tiny Cars is a colorful arcade traffic management game where players must avoid collisions. With a top-down view and engaging gameplay, this game features 50 base stages set in various locations like crossroads, squares, and highways. After completing the initial 50 levels, players will encounter the same environments with increased difficulty, offering a challenging and addictive experience for traffic control enthusiasts. Enjoy managing the traffic and becoming a master of Tiny Cars, the ultimate arcade traffic management game!', 'Click on the cars to manage their movement. Keep an eye on all the cars to anticipate potential collisions. Some levels require precise timing and patience to complete successfully.\nEnjoy managing the traffic and becoming a master of Tiny Cars, the ultimate arcade traffic management game!', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5d513da2cf424e5e907b734848a3ec5d-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5d513da2cf424e5e907b734848a3ec5d-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5d513da2cf424e5e907b734848a3ec5d/', '800', '600', '1player,car,Kids Friendly,No Blood,point-and-click', 0, 0, 0, 'tiny-cars', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5d513da2cf424e5e907b734848a3ec5d-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5d513da2cf424e5e907b734848a3ec5d-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1458, '2025-04-19', 'Eat Blobs Simulator', 'The battle of the blobs and slimes is beginning in this great eating simulator. Pick your slime character and start competing against others. Eat smaller blobs and slimes, and make yours bigger than the others. Become the king of the blob arena! Buy various blob skins during the game. On each game, receive various rewards with the blob sizes and coins. Chase smaller blobs and eat them. Collect blobs around and increase your score.', 'The game is playable in 1 or 2 players at time.\nPlayer 1: W,A,S,D\nPlayer 2: ARROW KEYS\n\nCommon controls:\nControl the camera by holding RIGHT-CLICK on the MOUSE\nControl the camera zoom with MOUSE SCROLL\n\nUse Joystick controls on mobile devices/tablets.', '.IO,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1f699e7fa7724cceb25dbd57c87edf14-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1f699e7fa7724cceb25dbd57c87edf14-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1f699e7fa7724cceb25dbd57c87edf14/', '800', '600', 'arena,2players,battlefield,eat,jelly', 0, 0, 0, 'eat-blobs-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1f699e7fa7724cceb25dbd57c87edf14-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1f699e7fa7724cceb25dbd57c87edf14-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1459, '2025-04-19', 'Boom Stick Bazooka', 'In Boom Stick Bazooka, an explosive online game where you may customize your bazooka and smash platforms and opposing stickmen, you\'re in for a wild ride. The black stickmen are stationed in towers, and if you pause for even a second, they\'ll open fire, attempting to wipe off your three lives.\n\nIn each level, you\'ll have three chances to aim and fire; you may always try again or purchase more ammo. If you want to kill foes quickly, blow up the barrels so they explode and knock down the towers.', 'Using just three bazooka rounds, you must destroy all adversaries in the game. You may use heavy items or adjacent barrel explosions to attack the stickmen and demolish the towers.\n\nControls:\nUse the mouse to aim and shoot\nTap on the screen and drag to shoot.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/88cbf39c387f4472bc16ea59b0da3636-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/88cbf39c387f4472bc16ea59b0da3636-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/88cbf39c387f4472bc16ea59b0da3636/', '900', '600', 'aim,bomb,shoot-em-up', 0, 0, 0, 'boom-stick-bazooka', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/88cbf39c387f4472bc16ea59b0da3636-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/88cbf39c387f4472bc16ea59b0da3636-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1460, '2025-04-19', 'Stunt Rider', 'In this exciting game, you will take on the role of an experienced stuntman, performing daring stunts on your motorcycle at different levels. Unlock new levels and buy cool motorcycles in the Stunt Rider game.', 'Control the motorcycle, avoiding overturning, and get to the finish line.\n\nManagement:\nComputer: Arrow keys or W, A, S, D to control the motorcycle. Additionally, Left Shift and Right Shift can be used for the gas pedal, and the Space bar can be used for the brake\nMobile phone: Use the pedal buttons on the screen to control the motorcycle.', 'Racing & Driving,Sports', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/98ddff27fcb349bea90758188b384e31-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/98ddff27fcb349bea90758188b384e31-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/98ddff27fcb349bea90758188b384e31/', '800', '600', 'car,rider,sport,biker', 0, 0, 0, 'stunt-rider', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/98ddff27fcb349bea90758188b384e31-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/98ddff27fcb349bea90758188b384e31-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1461, '2025-04-19', 'Wood Nuts Master: Screw Puzzle', 'In this physics-based innovative puzzle game, your objective is to strategically place screws and nuts to fall all the wooden blocks.\nUnleash your cognitive ability as you tackle each brain-teasing level, each one designed to test your problem-solving skills. From simple puzzles to complex constructions, this 2D puzzle game offers an array of challenges suitable for puzzle enthusiasts of all ages.', 'Use the left mouse button or tap on the screw, then tap to the empty holes to place the screw.\nThink well and find best spots of empty holes to place the screws. Be careful when placing screws as you have limited empty holes and some of which may become covered by the wood blocks you released.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/45027b37d96b46baad6752efd5c9430f-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/45027b37d96b46baad6752efd5c9430f-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/45027b37d96b46baad6752efd5c9430f/', '720', '1280', '1player,2d,logic,physics,relax,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'wood-nuts-master-screw-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/45027b37d96b46baad6752efd5c9430f-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/45027b37d96b46baad6752efd5c9430f-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1462, '2025-04-19', 'Grand Clash Arena', 'Grand Clash Arena is a unique war game that offers an action-packed experience.\n\nKey Features of the Game:\n\n-Epic Combat Experience: Showcase your mastery against opponents by using every object at your disposal.\n\n-Drop Weapons and Surprises: Alter the flow of the game with surprise drops from the sky. Surprise your opponents with powerful weapons that suddenly appear and gain an advantage.\n\nGrand Clash Arena offers a unique gaming experience that combines the art of war and strategy.', 'Join now, prove yourself in battles! Use WASD keys to move around the arena, spacebar to jump and right mouse button to hit.', 'Battle,Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5b1cb82de3324264912fe78c015fafa0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5b1cb82de3324264912fe78c015fafa0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5b1cb82de3324264912fe78c015fafa0/', '1920', '1080', 'fighting,weapons,arena,battlefield,3d,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'grand-clash-arena', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5b1cb82de3324264912fe78c015fafa0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5b1cb82de3324264912fe78c015fafa0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1463, '2025-04-19', 'Magnetic Merge - Number Master', 'Merge numbers by adding tiles with the same number to the field next to already placed tiles (vertically or horizontally).\nEach merge will create a new tile with a number one higher.\n\nBoosters:\n- Remove any tile from the field;\n- Remove all tiles with the selected number;\n- Refresh: allows to change tile form the \"NEXT\" up to 5 times.\n\nEach booster is available only once in a single game.\n\nChallenge yourself in this number master merge puzzle. Try to get the higher tile and beet your best score.', 'Left mouse click to interact', 'Casual,Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c757314032b34684b0d197b1e7812473-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c757314032b34684b0d197b1e7812473-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c757314032b34684b0d197b1e7812473/', '720', '1280', '1player,color,relax,2048,timekiller,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'magnetic-merge-number-master', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c757314032b34684b0d197b1e7812473-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c757314032b34684b0d197b1e7812473-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1464, '2025-04-19', 'Slope Emoji 2', 'Slope Emoji is a fantastic endless ball rolling game with many emoji balls. Guide a colorful cast of emoji characters down challenging slopes. Test your reflexes with endless series of obstacles, unexpected twists, and surprises. Collect Likes button for more new emoji characters with unique faces! Get ready for the ride of your life and master the art of ball rolling!', 'Steer the ball with A/D or Left/Right arrow keys. Get as far as you can and climb up the leaderboard. Avoid all obstacles, bombs, and try to stay on the platform. Falling off the platform or hitting any obstacle and the game is over.', 'Agility,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/566a3a6a293f464299216a53166aa2d7-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/566a3a6a293f464299216a53166aa2d7-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/566a3a6a293f464299216a53166aa2d7/', '800', '600', '1player,run,rolling,3d,speedrun,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'slope-emoji-2', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/566a3a6a293f464299216a53166aa2d7-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/566a3a6a293f464299216a53166aa2d7-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1465, '2025-04-19', 'Solitaire Tail', 'Raise your dragons at Solitaire! Clear the game by moving all cards to the foundation! Move cards from the tableau or stockpile in ascending order of the same suit. In the tableau, you can stack cards in descending order with alternating colors! You can place a King card in an empty column! When there are no available moves, you can draw cards from the stockpile to the foundation or tableau!', 'Tap or drag to move cards.', 'Cards', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/29380fce64cc4337b8f4d01158a691c9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/29380fce64cc4337b8f4d01158a691c9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/29380fce64cc4337b8f4d01158a691c9/', '378', '672', 'animal,dragon,fantasy,solitaire,klondike,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'solitaire-tail', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/29380fce64cc4337b8f4d01158a691c9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/29380fce64cc4337b8f4d01158a691c9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1466, '2025-04-19', 'Gelatino', 'Gelatino needs your help! He needs to collect as much ice as he can! \nThe hot summer sun will melt him if he doesn\'t pay attention!\nBut the road isn\'t safe: it is full of evil hot suns that will melt Gelatino in no time!\nDestroy them will make you earn more points, but the price to pay to make a highscore could be to high...', 'Touch the screen to move the player left and right', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/316e4e331e8c4d498017175ad003d602-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/316e4e331e8c4d498017175ad003d602-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/316e4e331e8c4d498017175ad003d602/', '480', '854', 'avoid,collect,colorful,fly,flying,icecream,blast,timekiller,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'gelatino', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/316e4e331e8c4d498017175ad003d602-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/316e4e331e8c4d498017175ad003d602-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1467, '2025-04-19', 'Nuts And Bolts Screw Puzzle', 'Nuts And Bolts Screw Puzzle is a puzzle game to remove bolts from the board, by moving the bolts to other bolt holes. The game will be finished when all the boards are gone\nThis challenging and addictive Wooden Nuts &amp; Bolts puzzle game will test your problem solving skills as you twist, turn and strategize your way through a maze of tricky Wooden tools. With each level, the puzzles become more complicated and complex.', 'Touch the bolt you selected, then move it to the available bolt hole, removing all boards from the game screen. When the board is stuck, it is your job to drop the board so that the game is finished.', 'Puzzle,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5116a63fee654a77b8aa0d4769439a2c-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5116a63fee654a77b8aa0d4769439a2c-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5116a63fee654a77b8aa0d4769439a2c/', '720', '1280', '1player,block,board,2048,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'nuts-and-bolts-screw-puzzle', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5116a63fee654a77b8aa0d4769439a2c-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5116a63fee654a77b8aa0d4769439a2c-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1468, '2025-04-19', 'Bitball', 'A unique tile ball puzzle game from coin base bitcoin games loved by millions of players around the world. \nMake a lot of coins and become a rich. ?\n - Start with 10 and start making millions. ?\n - Coun you rech the topmillioners.\n - Play with friend together.?\n - Guess the ball where it will go.?', 'It is that simple as going to school (lol).\n\n - On the right sight you will see a lot of buttons. ?\n - Just click on any one. ?', '.IO,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/11041bb37a5543dbb677da564cafe192-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/11041bb37a5543dbb677da564cafe192-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/11041bb37a5543dbb677da564cafe192/', '960', '600', 'ball,2players,drop,arcade,clicker', 0, 0, 0, 'bitball', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/11041bb37a5543dbb677da564cafe192-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/11041bb37a5543dbb677da564cafe192-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1469, '2025-04-19', 'Cards 2048', 'Are you looking for a fresh twist on a familiar game? Cards 2048 is the perfect blend of classic solitaire and the popular 2048 puzzle game! This unique combination creates an engaging brain teaser that\'s highly addictive. As you merge cards with matching numbers, the challenge intensifies, offering a true test of your skill and strategy. Sharpen your logic and enjoy hours of fun with Cards 2048, the ultimate card merging game for puzzle enthusiasts!', 'In this puzzle game, you should drag the cards to an open slot on the board. When you put two same number cards in a column together, they will be merged. You should challenge yourself and reach 2048! If you cant merge the numbers and you have no space left to drag the new cards, the game will be over.', 'Cards', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5370293cd9434e4abe9084397f091ed6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5370293cd9434e4abe9084397f091ed6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5370293cd9434e4abe9084397f091ed6/', '800', '600', 'solitaire,stack,2048,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cards-2048', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5370293cd9434e4abe9084397f091ed6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5370293cd9434e4abe9084397f091ed6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1470, '2025-04-19', 'Beach Soccer', 'Immerse yourself in a fun-filled beach adventure where your goal is to aim and shoot the ball into the goal while collecting starfish for maximum points. With over 20 challenging levels, you\'ll need to think strategically to navigate obstacles like crabs and sandcastles. Enjoy a vibrant beach setting complete with golden sand, coconut trees, and a soothing soundtrack. ', 'Aim, shoot, and collect starfish in a beach-themed puzzle adventure with over 20 challenging levels.', 'Sports,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/857b1422e8654a389c0d70d18910fed0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/857b1422e8654a389c0d70d18910fed0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/857b1422e8654a389c0d70d18910fed0/', '1280', '720', '1player,2d,ball,beach,skill,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'beach-soccer', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/857b1422e8654a389c0d70d18910fed0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/857b1422e8654a389c0d70d18910fed0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1471, '2025-04-19', 'BFF Lovely Kawaii Outfits', 'Welcome to BFF Lovely Kawaii Outfits game. Princesses Elsa, Anna, Moana, and Jasmine are more fascinated about Kawaii Outfits. They are very eager to browse the new collection of Kawaii outfits. Start helping with each princess for their outfits and matching costumes by browsing their wardrobe. Play these cute girl games and have fun!', 'Left mouse button click', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f24f601406f848aa9d2d7acfcc4db511-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f24f601406f848aa9d2d7acfcc4db511-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f24f601406f848aa9d2d7acfcc4db511/', '800', '600', 'fashion,cutedressup,girls,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'bff-lovely-kawaii-outfits', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f24f601406f848aa9d2d7acfcc4db511-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f24f601406f848aa9d2d7acfcc4db511-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1472, '2025-04-19', 'Dynamons 8', 'Embark on a brand new Dynamons adventure in Dynamons 8! This online monster collecting game includes two fresh areas to explore; Chinese Festival world and the bonus cave.\n\nSeasoned Dynamons connoisseur Jovani will tell you everything you need to know to become a true Dynamon Captain. Encounter Robocanyx, Jaxaguar, Sauryx, Dagaryx and Tydonyx and many more special Dynamons. Recruit them for your team and beat others in thrilling 1v1 battles with special attacks and power-ups.', 'Play the game using touchscreen controls or your mouse.\n\nThe game consists of spellbinding turn-based battles. You can use the action cards to attack, and catch the opposing creature when its weakened. The backpack is filled with items you can collect and use during your journeys. By selecting it during battle, you can access these special items. Use shards to level up your Dynamons, and to gain new action cards. Challenge other trainers and become the strongest Dynamon Captain!\n', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5fd7ae34b61c42649aecb9a0ea44e572-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5fd7ae34b61c42649aecb9a0ea44e572-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5fd7ae34b61c42649aecb9a0ea44e572/', '800', '600', 'collect,rpg,story,singleplayer,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'dynamons-8', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5fd7ae34b61c42649aecb9a0ea44e572-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5fd7ae34b61c42649aecb9a0ea44e572-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1473, '2025-04-19', 'Mermaidcore Makeup', 'In Mermaidcore Makeup, you ladies can step into the shoes of a talented makeup artist and work your magic on three stunning ladies. Journey into the realm of fantasy as you help these beauties achieve their perfect, enchanting looks. Prepare for a sensational trip filled with endless options as you explore an extensive selection of hairstyles, eyeshadows, mascara, lipsticks, face patterns, and intricate shoulder and neck patterns that perfectly match each girl\'s unique style and personality. ', 'Use your mouse to play this game', 'Dress-up', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7d3336e382c443d5a27edcfd6f12ef28-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/7d3336e382c443d5a27edcfd6f12ef28-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/7d3336e382c443d5a27edcfd6f12ef28/', '1024', '768', 'fantasy,makeover,makeup,mermaid,summer,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'mermaidcore-makeup', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7d3336e382c443d5a27edcfd6f12ef28-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/7d3336e382c443d5a27edcfd6f12ef28-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1474, '2025-04-19', 'Stunt Fury', 'Stunt Fury takes adrenaline-fueled stunts to new heights in this action-packed gaming experience. Strap in and prepare to defy gravity as you showcase your skills on a variety of daring platforms. With heart-pounding excitement around every corner, this game challenges players to push the limits of physics and creativity.', '- Use arrow keys and WASD to Drive\n- Space to Hand Brake', 'Racing & Driving', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/46dc46bb1d6341bda2b509e69a094ac4-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/46dc46bb1d6341bda2b509e69a094ac4-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/46dc46bb1d6341bda2b509e69a094ac4/', '960', '640', 'car,stunts,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'stunt-fury', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/46dc46bb1d6341bda2b509e69a094ac4-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/46dc46bb1d6341bda2b509e69a094ac4-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1475, '2025-04-19', 'Merge cubes 2048 3D', 'A completely new approach to the classic game 2048?! Now in 3D and with dynamic physics?! Number cubes don\'t just merge - they bounce and collide?, adding an element of surprise to every game! Compete with friends or colleagues?!\n', '1. At first it will be easy to connect the cubes, but over time there will be more and more of them. Once you connect the biggest cube in this game, it will disappear. If one of the cubes touches the line, you lose and the game starts again.\n2. Press and hold your finger or mouse to control the cube. Release your finger or mouse button to let the cube fall onto the field!', 'Casual,Merge', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a675bc1d6ae54479b5d21383ec7da937-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/a675bc1d6ae54479b5d21383ec7da937-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/a675bc1d6ae54479b5d21383ec7da937/', '800', '600', '1player,3d,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'merge-cubes-2048-3d', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a675bc1d6ae54479b5d21383ec7da937-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/a675bc1d6ae54479b5d21383ec7da937-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1476, '2025-04-19', 'Cat Football', 'Enter the adorable world of Cat Football, where cute felines don caps and engage in soccer madness! Score goals using a ball of blue thread against cardboard box goals. Compete with friends or challenge a skilled computer opponent in time-limited matches filled with frantic fun!', 'Control cute cats in caps, score goals with a ball of blue thread.', 'Sports', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/acec6a75c18049a8aa17547de8087ac3-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/acec6a75c18049a8aa17547de8087ac3-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/acec6a75c18049a8aa17547de8087ac3/', '800', '600', 'headsoccer,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'cat-football', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/acec6a75c18049a8aa17547de8087ac3-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/acec6a75c18049a8aa17547de8087ac3-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1477, '2025-04-19', 'Dino Ranch', 'JON &amp; BLITZ - ITS VELOCI-TIME!\n Throwing the lasso to the escaped compies\n Dodging herds of ankylosaurus.\n Finding the naughty compies.\n Feeding Angus.\n Flying and dodging objects with Pteddy\n Moving the dinosaurs to the stable.\n Challenging the Trihorn Raptor to a race.\n Helping the compies to jump across the river.', 'Navigate through the app by swiping (touchscreen devices) or clicking (mouse devices) on the screen elements as directed.', 'Casual,Educational', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/22f6423e414044c49deb493baae4fb63-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/22f6423e414044c49deb493baae4fb63-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/22f6423e414044c49deb493baae4fb63/', '800', '600', 'dinosaurs,kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'dino-ranch', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/22f6423e414044c49deb493baae4fb63-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/22f6423e414044c49deb493baae4fb63-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1478, '2025-04-19', 'Popping Pets', 'In Popping Pets, stack and match adorable pets to score points! Connect three or more adjacent pets to clear them before time runs out. Look out for bombs for big clears and big points. Can you reach the highest score in one minute?', 'Click pets that are connected with three or more of the same pets to pop them! Find as many matches as fast as possible to score big points! Unlock pet abilities with your earnings to change your strategy and possibly increase your high score!', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9fbeef1c6f5d435ca633deefcd0e2a49-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/9fbeef1c6f5d435ca633deefcd0e2a49-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/9fbeef1c6f5d435ca633deefcd0e2a49/', '800', '600', 'animal,pet,arcade', 0, 0, 0, 'popping-pets', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9fbeef1c6f5d435ca633deefcd0e2a49-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/9fbeef1c6f5d435ca633deefcd0e2a49-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1479, '2025-04-19', 'Muscle Up Master', 'The aim of this game that will help you become a muscle master, a boxer or an MMA fighter is to reach the best level! In this adventure where you start with a weak body, start exercising and reach a more muscular body by merging with the characters. As you progress, participate in fighting tournaments and grow faster with the rewards you earn!\n', '- Select characters and combine them with others.\n- Level up as you score and join fights when the tournament is ready.\n- During fights, try to defeat the opponent by clicking on the screen quickly or using the spacebar on the computer.', 'Agility,Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c7aa364f5ca243dd84729b3f1cb337b0-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/c7aa364f5ca243dd84729b3f1cb337b0-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/c7aa364f5ca243dd84729b3f1cb337b0/', '1920', '1080', '1player,fighting,idle,boxing,clicker,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'muscle-up-master', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c7aa364f5ca243dd84729b3f1cb337b0-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/c7aa364f5ca243dd84729b3f1cb337b0-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1480, '2025-04-19', 'Supermarket Manager Simulator', 'Supermarket Manager Simulator is a business game. Have you ever fantasized about running your supermarket in your childhood?  Play as the store manager in this game and stock up on a variety of goods, from chips and fries to meats, burgers, vegetables, and fruits. From stocking, and shelving to selling, you will be the one to take care of it!  Don\'t hesitate to start your entrepreneurial journey now and become a great store tycoon!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5dff4319bd2845c781cd3378d86735ed-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/5dff4319bd2845c781cd3378d86735ed-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/5dff4319bd2845c781cd3378d86735ed/', '1280', '720', 'business,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'supermarket-manager-simulator', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5dff4319bd2845c781cd3378d86735ed-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/5dff4319bd2845c781cd3378d86735ed-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1481, '2025-04-19', 'Stickman vs Zombies WorldCraft', 'Stickman vs Zombies WorldCraft is an action and adventure platform game in which you can play as a brave stick ninja. As your stickman hero, your mission is to wipe all the craft zombies. Along the way, you\'ll find money that you may use to unlock cool new skins.\n\nNavigate the map in search of zombies before they track you down and rush you or open fire on you. Keep going, for the zombie craft will attempt to catch you if you leave even one alive.\n', 'Instructions:\n\nSearch and eliminate all the craft zombies in each level to emerge alive and move on to another level.\n\nWASD to move and jump\nSpacebar and Click mouse to attack\nE Shield\nUse the game buttons for touch devices.', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4bc40841bbaf49248168112266c2f7bf-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4bc40841bbaf49248168112266c2f7bf-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4bc40841bbaf49248168112266c2f7bf/', '800', '600', 'fighting,minecraft,zombie', 0, 0, 0, 'stickman-vs-zombies-worldcraft', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4bc40841bbaf49248168112266c2f7bf-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4bc40841bbaf49248168112266c2f7bf-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1482, '2025-04-19', 'Color Strings', 'Looking for a simple way to exercise your brain every day? Try Color Strings! This game features straightforward rules and fun, challenging gameplay. In this puzzle game, you need to rearrange the strings on the dots to match the given pattern. With various puzzle levels, you\'ll keep your brain sharp in just a few minutes each day.', 'In this puzzle game, you should reshape the strings on the dots to match the pattern shape.\nEach string on the puzzle board has a color, and you should use the same-colored string as the pattern. With each level progressing, the shape gets more complicated and challenging for your players.\n', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1888ad26ba80461eac41ea35db484092-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/1888ad26ba80461eac41ea35db484092-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/1888ad26ba80461eac41ea35db484092/', '800', '600', 'colorful,logic,connection,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'color-strings', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1888ad26ba80461eac41ea35db484092-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/1888ad26ba80461eac41ea35db484092-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1483, '2025-04-19', 'Riot Village', 'Step into Riot Village, a thrilling browser-based adventure where your shooting skills and strategy are tested. Navigate 10 intense levels with AI enemies. Visit the market to choose from 6 unique weapons and equip up to 4 in your inventory. Switch weapons during gameplay to overcome challenges. The game features automatic character movement, letting you focus on aiming and shooting. Adapt your strategy as each enemy wields different weapons. Are you ready for the challenge?', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Shooter,Battle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/251f712ac4a945dd876eb5c120e7e7d6-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/251f712ac4a945dd876eb5c120e7e7d6-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/251f712ac4a945dd876eb5c120e7e7d6/', '1920', '1080', 'guns,war,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood,point-and-click', 0, 0, 0, 'riot-village', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/251f712ac4a945dd876eb5c120e7e7d6-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/251f712ac4a945dd876eb5c120e7e7d6-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1484, '2025-04-19', 'Untwist Road', 'Collect cylinders, roll out the road and overcome obstacles in this unique game. It is suitable for all fans of arcade games who like to test their skills and reactions. Try all the features of the game, unlock new levels and beat your records! You only need a few minutes to fully immerse yourself in this exciting game. Try it yourself!', '1. Hold down the mouse button or finger on the screen and move left/right to control the stickman.\n2. Collect as many cylinders as possible to make your way, avoid obstacles.\n3. Get rewards and improve the characteristics of the stickman to play better.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/583140e5a9ca4046bb56c64e62204983-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/583140e5a9ca4046bb56c64e62204983-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/583140e5a9ca4046bb56c64e62204983/', '800', '600', 'arcade,3d,Kids Friendly', 0, 0, 0, 'untwist-road', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/583140e5a9ca4046bb56c64e62204983-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/583140e5a9ca4046bb56c64e62204983-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1485, '2025-04-19', 'Summer Connect', 'You can test your pattern detection skills in this relaxed mahjong &amp; connect puzzle game with summer theme. You can eliminate pair of same tiles. The line connecting the two clicked tiles can\'t have more than 2 corners. Some levels the tiles can auto slide( to left, to right, to up, to bottom). Can you clear the board before time runs out? Enjoying matching summer tiles with 30 puzzle stages in this game.', 'Use mouse to play this mahjong connect games with the summer theme.', 'Mahjong & Connect', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f168da43c30446bdbbc2c803fcaa69a4-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/f168da43c30446bdbbc2c803fcaa69a4-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/f168da43c30446bdbbc2c803fcaa69a4/', '1280', '768', 'summer,tiles,connection,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'summer-connect', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f168da43c30446bdbbc2c803fcaa69a4-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/f168da43c30446bdbbc2c803fcaa69a4-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1486, '2025-04-19', 'Banana Bounce!', 'Banana Bounce! ? is a side-scrolling game where you lead your banana to as far as you can.\nDiscover many cool ? and amazing ? powerups to boost ? your progress!\nDiscover unique ? characters and earn coins ? while you run!\nDon\'t forget to upgrade  your powerups to make them even stronger ? and better!\n\nMade with  by Realinspirer', 'Use click/tap and drag to control the character.\nUse tap/click to control the UI.', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fb1df24707dd4e8aba2fa7056ec48862-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/fb1df24707dd4e8aba2fa7056ec48862-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/fb1df24707dd4e8aba2fa7056ec48862/', '1080', '1920', '1player,2d,arcade', 0, 0, 0, 'banana-bounce', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fb1df24707dd4e8aba2fa7056ec48862-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/fb1df24707dd4e8aba2fa7056ec48862-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1487, '2025-04-19', 'Live or Die', 'Welcome to the Live or Die pixel puzzle. The goal of the game is to escape the room. To do this, you need to get a key to open the door.\nWhen your player is alive he can move right, left, jump, take the keys and escape the room. If the player takes any damage, they turn into a ghostly form and can fly and pass through obstacles. However the ghost can\'t take keys or escape.\nTo return to human form, the ghost must fly to the gravestone.\nRemember that you have only 3 lives. Can you escape the room?', 'Arrows to move, mouse/touch to interact with interface', 'Adventure', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cd28d31092624f05b9bd3f8175d8a2ae-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/cd28d31092624f05b9bd3f8175d8a2ae-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/cd28d31092624f05b9bd3f8175d8a2ae/', '1024', '576', '1player,escape,platformer,roomescape,transformation,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'live-or-die', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cd28d31092624f05b9bd3f8175d8a2ae-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/cd28d31092624f05b9bd3f8175d8a2ae-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1488, '2025-04-19', 'Drawer Sort', 'Do you like a cluttered space exactly where everything has its place? It is time to organize your life and become a tidying hero, conquering chaos one drawer at a time.  Be sure to plan ahead for this epic puzzle or you may find yourself with a messier hand than when you started! Each brain training task will challenge you to place various items in the right places. You\'ll have to aim for perfect precision if you want to make sure the objects fit snugly and achieve the ultimate tidy victory. ', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Strategy', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d924a9f2a4b94fae8966d3131b7e02c8-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/d924a9f2a4b94fae8966d3131b7e02c8-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/d924a9f2a4b94fae8966d3131b7e02c8/', '720', '1280', 'drawing,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'drawer-sort', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d924a9f2a4b94fae8966d3131b7e02c8-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/d924a9f2a4b94fae8966d3131b7e02c8-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1489, '2025-04-19', 'Brain Find Can You Find It', 'Brain Find brings new brain puzzles! Combine brain power and discovery for a brain challenge like no other! You can use your brain and reverse thinking to get the final target item. The unexpected way of passing levels can bring you endless laughs.  The game tests your logical thinking skills, reflexes as well as memory and creativity. Come and experience it and prove that you are the smartest!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bd985417916041369433883efc7b0ac4-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/bd985417916041369433883efc7b0ac4-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/bd985417916041369433883efc7b0ac4/', '720', '1280', '1player,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'brain-find-can-you-find-it', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bd985417916041369433883efc7b0ac4-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/bd985417916041369433883efc7b0ac4-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1490, '2025-04-19', 'Fruit Balls: Juicy Fusion', 'Discover the exciting world of juicy fruits! The task is simple: connect identical fruits to create ever larger and tastier associations, heading towards the treasured watermelon.\n\n- Click on the field\n- Connect identical fruits\n- Create combinations to get bigger fruits.\n- Reach the last level\n- Don\'t let the container overfill\n- Earn money for new skins and try to pass with them ???', 'CLICK or TAP on your screen to throw an object', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e33c800f99c741d09fb19c97f6fbfbe9-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/e33c800f99c741d09fb19c97f6fbfbe9-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/e33c800f99c741d09fb19c97f6fbfbe9/', '1080', '1920', '2d,fruits,matching,relaxing,2048,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'fruit-balls-juicy-fusion', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e33c800f99c741d09fb19c97f6fbfbe9-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/e33c800f99c741d09fb19c97f6fbfbe9-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1491, '2025-04-19', 'Microplastics Feeding', 'Microplastics Feeding is a game about a hungry fish who is looking for its favorite food: plastic! Help the fish to eat all the plastic things in the ocean!', 'Game controls: \nTouch click or press psacebar to change direction', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3519812027764a309a7ffad739caa0cf-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3519812027764a309a7ffad739caa0cf-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3519812027764a309a7ffad739caa0cf/', '800', '450', 'avoid,collect,feed,fish,sea,swimming,pixelart,fishing,ocean,creature', 0, 0, 0, 'microplastics-feeding', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3519812027764a309a7ffad739caa0cf-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3519812027764a309a7ffad739caa0cf-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1492, '2025-04-19', 'Chaos Road Combat Car Racing', 'Chaos Road: Combat Car Racing plays like a shoot-em-up car shooting arcade game. With 3D vehicles on the ground, your mission is to defeat the final boss by collecting upgrade items and shooting down vehicles on the ground. Your vehicle will keep shooting automatically. Don\'t forget to collect the magnet to collect all kinds of items easily. To defeat the final boss, you need to avoid its bullets and keep shooting. Have fun!', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Adventure,Shooter', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3b4e41e448514cbaa872fa6384ebbbd2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/3b4e41e448514cbaa872fa6384ebbbd2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/3b4e41e448514cbaa872fa6384ebbbd2/', '720', '1280', '1player,car,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'chaos-road-combat-car-racing', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3b4e41e448514cbaa872fa6384ebbbd2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/3b4e41e448514cbaa872fa6384ebbbd2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1493, '2025-04-19', 'Sigil Seeker', 'Welcome to Sigil Seeker!\\nEmbark on a quest to collect mystical sigils by tapping tiles on the screen. Add tiles to your row, aiming to gather three identical sigils to collect them. Your goal is to gather all the sigils before time runs out. But beware, if your row overflows or the clock reaches zero, the game is over.\\nAre you ready to become the ultimate Sigil Seeker? Dive in and start your adventure now!', 'Use a mouse or touchpad to play this game.', 'Match-3', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/380bd283750f4f14879cbc414d984eb3-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/380bd283750f4f14879cbc414d984eb3-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/380bd283750f4f14879cbc414d984eb3/', '600', '800', 'fantasy,matching,tiles,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'sigil-seeker', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/380bd283750f4f14879cbc414d984eb3-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/380bd283750f4f14879cbc414d984eb3-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1494, '2025-04-19', 'Summer Spotlight Differences', 'Dive into the sunny and captivating world of Summer Spotlight Differences, a delightful spot-the-difference game that\'s perfect for all ages. This engaging game challenges you to find all 5 differences in each level to advance to the next, offering endless fun and a great way to sharpen your observational skills. Enjoy the challenge and have a blast with this fantastic spot-the-difference game!', 'Use mouse to play.', 'Puzzle,Educational', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/77acc3ee9dbc4458973045f0eba6a7f2-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/77acc3ee9dbc4458973045f0eba6a7f2-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/77acc3ee9dbc4458973045f0eba6a7f2/', '1280', '720', 'school,summer,differences,kidgames,arcade,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'summer-spotlight-differences', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/77acc3ee9dbc4458973045f0eba6a7f2-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/77acc3ee9dbc4458973045f0eba6a7f2-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1495, '2025-04-19', 'Bomb Evolution', 'Bomb Evolution is a cannon-shooting arcade game. On the mysterious and mist-shrouded island, you have the opportunity to strategically establish not one, but three main bases, bolstered by an additional rocket. Engage in an enthralling battle against a formidable opponent, both of you operating under identical circumstances. Your ultimate objective: obliterating all the enemy\'s main bases positioned on the neighboring fog-laden island. May victory in this war be your prized accomplishment!', 'Swipe to shoot, Release to launch bombs', 'Casual', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4a55248d23744a1391e748e5c89437b1-512x384.jpeg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/4a55248d23744a1391e748e5c89437b1-512x512.jpeg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/4a55248d23744a1391e748e5c89437b1/', '750', '1334', '2d,avoid,arcade,boys', 0, 0, 0, 'bomb-evolution', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4a55248d23744a1391e748e5c89437b1-512x384.jpeg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/4a55248d23744a1391e748e5c89437b1-512x512.jpeg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1496, '2025-04-19', 'Hex Triple Match', 'Hex Triple Match brings together puzzle challenges, strategic matching and merging experiences. This game consists of clever puzzle-solving and logical manoeuvres, making it ideal for those seeking a brain workout.  You need to consider how to place them to eliminate them faster. Each colour represents an item, giving you a great gaming experience. Beautiful graphics bring you visual enjoyment. Come and join the merging game world.', 'Mouse click or tap to play', 'Puzzle', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/84e6617b278946a89ea081e8ecb6a257-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/84e6617b278946a89ea081e8ecb6a257-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/84e6617b278946a89ea081e8ecb6a257/', '650', '1338', '1player,matching', 0, 0, 0, 'hex-triple-match', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/84e6617b278946a89ea081e8ecb6a257-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/84e6617b278946a89ea081e8ecb6a257-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1497, '2025-04-19', 'Strawberry Shortcake', 'Strawberry Shortcake has big dreams. She wants to be the BEST baker that Big Apple City  has ever seen and that\'s why she packed her bags and went to live with her Aunt Praline to the only place where a baker can go if they want to become the best in the whole world: the BIG APPLE CITY! ', 'Navigate through the app by swiping (touchscreen devices) or clicking (mouse devices) on the screen elements as directed.', 'Cooking,Simulation', 'gamedistribution', 'html5', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/822c7548934c460c8c06d7121f82545b-512x384.jpg', 'https://img.gamedistribution.com/822c7548934c460c8c06d7121f82545b-512x512.jpg', '', 'https://html5.gamedistribution.com/822c7548934c460c8c06d7121f82545b/', '800', '600', 'cook,kidgames,Kids Friendly,No Blood', 0, 0, 0, 'strawberry-shortcake', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/822c7548934c460c8c06d7121f82545b-512x384.jpg\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/img.gamedistribution.com\\/822c7548934c460c8c06d7121f82545b-512x512.jpg\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
