(1547, '2025-04-19', 'Pac Rush Man', 'Pac-Man\" is a classic arcade game originally released by Namco in 1980. It quickly became one of the most iconic and recognizable video games of all time. In \"Pac-Man,\" players control the titular character, a yellow, circular creature with a large mouth, navigating through a maze-like grid filled with dots or pellets.', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U10NH/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/U10NH/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/pac-rush-man/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'pac-rush-man', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/U10NH\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/U10NH\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1548, '2025-04-19', 'Bubble Shot Master', 'Bubble Shooter Master - new classic bubble shooter game in the match 3 genre without the Internet! Play endless free offline bubbles game!\n\nShoot and pop the bubbles to create a combination of three or more balls of the same color. The more bubble balls explode in a combination, the more points you will earn in this offline puzzle game.\n\nIf shooting the balls is unsuccessful and the combination of bubbles does not come together, then you get a strike. After several strikes, a new row of multi-colored bubbles and balls appears. The match-3 game will end if the bubbles reach the bottom of the screen.\n\nThis classic match 3 bubble shooting game features beautiful super levels with unusual patterns of colorful bubbles! Pop, explode, shoot and enjoy the endless bubble shooter for free!\n\nThe puzzle game Bubble Shooter Master will appeal to children and adults, boys and girls of all ages, and those who love free match 3 games with balls and bubbles!\n\nGame Features:\n\n- Free match-3 game without internet\n- Classic bubble shooter pop\n- Unusual patterns of super levels\n- 3 difficulty levels\n- Different skins of bubbles\n- Customizable background color\n- Leaderboard and achievements', '', 'Puzzle,Classics', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HHEAU/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/HHEAU/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/bubble-shot-master-classic-bubble-shooter-match-3-game/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'bubble-shot-master', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/HHEAU\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/HHEAU\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
