(1623, '2025-04-19', 'Physical Balls 2048', 'Your task is to merge the same balls. When two balls with the same number, color and size collide, they merge into one ball with a larger number. The goal is to reach as many numbers as possible by combining the balls. \nThe physics in this game adds an extra level of difficulty. The balls move and bounce realistically. As you progress through the levels, the gameplay becomes more complex, new types of balls and obstacles are added to it. \nThe graphics in this game are amazing, with bright colors and smooth animations that bring the physical balls to life. \nThis physical ball game is perfect for both regular players and puzzle lovers. So what are you waiting for? Start the game right now and start merging these balls!', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B70LS/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/B70LS/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/physical-balls-2048/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'physical-balls-2048', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/B70LS\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/B70LS\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
