(1816, '2025-04-19', 'Tall Fat Man Run', ' Tall Fat Man Run is a fun and addictive hyper casual game where you control a tall and fat man who loves to run. Your goal is to avoid the obstacles that can make you lose your height and weight, such as spikes, saws, and lasers. You also want to enter the gates that can make you gain more height and weight.\nHow tall and fat can you get? Try it now and find out!', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/50935/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/50935/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/tall-fat-man-run/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'tall-fat-man-run', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/50935\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/50935\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1817, '2025-04-19', 'Quiz Trivia Guess The Animal Music Flags', 'Embark on a knowledge-packed adventure with Quiz Trivia: Guess the Animal, Music, Flags! This captivating education game combines the thrill of a quiz with the excitement of guessing animals, identifying flags, and recognizing music.\n\n Challenge your brain with a wide variety of questions spanning the world of animals, flags, and music. Test your knowledge and broaden your horizons as you explore the diverse realms of the animal kingdom, international flags, and the enchanting world of music.\n\n Dive into a global journey as you encounter questions that traverse the continents. Guess animals from different habitats, identify flags from around the world, and groove to the beats of diverse musical genres.\n\n Unlock your achievement as you master the art of guessing! Each question is designed to keep you on your toes, ensuring a fun and engaging experience for players of all ages.\n\n Immerse yourself in the rhythmic melodies of the music round. Can you identify the tunes and artists? Test your musical acumen and become a true maestro!\n\n Unleash your inner zoologist by guessing animals based on intriguing clues. Whether it\'s the roar of the wild or the flutter of feathers, every guess brings you closer to becoming a true animal expert.\n\n Sharpen your focus and recognize flags from countries far and wide. From iconic symbols to vibrant colors, challenge yourself to become a world-class vexillologist.\n\n Seek knowledge, have fun, and enhance your cognitive skills with Quiz Trivia: Guess the Animal, Music, Flags. It\'s not just a game; it\'s an educational journey through the fascinating realms of the world.\n\nDownload now and let the quiz adventure begin! Test your wits, guess correctly, and emerge as the ultimate trivia master!\nquiz, music, world, question, flags, things, logo, trivia, animals, brain, gues', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AMR08/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AMR08/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/quiz-trivia-gues-the-animal-music-flags/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'quiz-trivia-guess-the-animal-music-flags', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/AMR08\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/AMR08\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
