(1838, '2025-04-19', 'BoxBulletCraft', 'There are as many as five unique arenas available in this game, each of which is a unique battlefield full of dangers and opportunities. Choose your favorite arena and get ready for battle!\n\nHere you will find not only an exciting single player game, but also an exciting mode for two players on the same device! Fight with your friend back to back against monsters!\n\nThe game offers you as many as eight types of monsters that use unique attack strategies and have their own special characteristics. Challenge them and develop your own winning strategy!\n\nWeapons are the key to your victory! The game features as many as eight different types of weapons, each of which has its own power and special abilities. Experiment with weapons and find your perfect monster killing kit.', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R57C3/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R57C3/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/boxbulletcraft/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'boxbulletcraft', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/R57C3\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/R57C3\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
