(1841, '2025-04-19', 'Princess Valentine Preparation', 'With valentines day around the corner, the Princess Valentine preparation has become exciting and thrilling. To celebrate Valentines day, the princess has decided to be in their best! Lets check out their closet and look at our options. They have a few dresses in their colors of choice, both long and short, sometimes its more fun to mix it up a bit! You have the additional task of decorating their card and make them geared up for the royal date.', '', 'Junior', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N2C7O/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N2C7O/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/princess-valentine-preparation/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'princess-valentine-preparation', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/N2C7O\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/N2C7O\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1842, '2025-04-19', 'Princess Cheongsam Shanghai Fashion', 'In this new cute game Princess Cheongsam Shanghai Fashion, Princesses want to play and enjoy their time, making cute dress up styles. Being BFFs forever, they have tried all possible outfits. Curiosity helps them to think past the current century. As they grace through history, they decide to adopt Cheongsam Shanghai Fashion in Princess style. Anna and Elsa finally land upon interesting dress-up costumes in Qing-style tops, modern Qipao with high-slit cuts &amp; mini dress. Help them choose the right color, dresses, and present them in majestic imperial fashion.', '', 'Junior', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S8ISA/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S8ISA/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/princess-cheongsam-shanghai-fashion/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'princess-cheongsam-shanghai-fashion', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/S8ISA\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/S8ISA\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
