(1852, '2025-04-19', 'Fruity Quiz Extravaganza', 'Dive into the world of succulent flavors and tantalizing aromas with \"Fruity Quiz Extravaganza,\" the ultimate name-the-fruit game that promises a bountiful harvest of fun and knowledge. Test your fruit IQ, challenge your taste buds, and embark on a juicy journey through a fruity wonderland!\n\nFruit Identification Challenge:\nDelicious Visual Treats:\nEducational Fun for All Age\nChallenge Friends in Multiplayer Mode', '', 'Junior', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z57YZ/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/Z57YZ/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/fruity-quiz-extravaganza/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'fruity-quiz-extravaganza', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/Z57YZ\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/Z57YZ\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1853, '2025-04-19', 'Fruity Memory Challenge', 'Embark on a vibrant journey of memory mastery with \"Fruity Memory Challenge,\" a thrilling make-a-pair game that blends fruity fun with brain-teasing excitement. Immerse yourself in a world of luscious fruits, hidden images, and challenging puzzles that will test your memory skills and leave you craving for more.\n\nFruitful Pairing Adventure\nVisual Feast of Fruits\nProgressive Challenge Levels\nMultiplayer Fruity Showdown', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8L218/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8L218/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/fruity-memory-challenge/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'fruity-memory-challenge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/8L218\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/8L218\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1854, '2025-04-19', 'PollTheFlowers', 'The game is a simple, but very bright arcade game. The game has eight levels, five types of flowers, six types of butterflies, two types of creatures that can eat a butterfly (if the butterfly is eaten, the level progress will not be saved).\n\nButterflies differ slightly in shape and speed of following the mouse or finger (if a touch screen is used).\n\nNew butterflies open as the number of pollinated flowers increases.\n\nIn order to complete the level you just need to fly over the flowers. Here the color is not important - the main thing is the quantity. At the same time, to unlock the next levels, you need a certain number of certain flowers.\n\nTo move the butterfly, you just need to click on it with the mouse or finger (if it is a device with a touch screen) and move it to any desired location. The butterfly will follow the cursor. Simple, intuitive and clear.\n\nYou need to beware of spiders and flycatchers - if the butterfly is eaten, then the level progress will not be saved and all efforts will be in vain.\n\nBeetles just push around, but they can get you into trouble.\n\nBees are useful and can help with pollination. To call them for help, you just need to touch the hive with a butterfly.', '', 'Junior,Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TE2WO/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/TE2WO/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/polltheflowers/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'polltheflowers', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/TE2WO\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/TE2WO\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1855, '2025-04-19', 'Friends Battle Swords Drawn', 'In the third episode of the Friends Battle series, swords have been drawn, and the war is about to begin. The battle starts; sharpen your sword, you need a sharp blade. Together with your friend, the one who captures the flag the most wins. The winner is the one who stays with the flag for 20 seconds. Dont forget, you have a sword and you also need to set up your flag. While setting up your flag, you must reach the enemys flag. Kill your friend with the sword and capture the flag.\n\nThe red player moves using the WASD keys. \nThe blue player moves using the arrow keys.\nStay at the flag for 20 seconds.\nYou can press S and DOWN ARROW to kill the enemy.', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16DS4/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/16DS4/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-swords-drawn/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'friends-battle-swords-drawn', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/16DS4\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/16DS4\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1856, '2025-04-19', 'Friends Battle Tag Flag', 'In the second game of the Friends Battle series, two friends are racing for the flag this time. Whoever holds the flag loses. Avoid the flag for 2 minutes, and win the game. The one who grabs the flag is the loser. Catch your friend and give them the flag. Remember, you should run away from whoever holds the flag. Dont forget, time is running out, and you might lose the game. Join this adventure with your friend.\n\nThe red player moves using the WASD keys. \nThe blue player moves using the arrow keys.\nRun away from the flag; whoever has the flag loses.\nAvoid the flag for 2 minutes.', '', 'Adventure', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I5EEA/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/I5EEA/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-tag-flag/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'friends-battle-tag-flag', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/I5EEA\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/I5EEA\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1857, '2025-04-19', 'Friends Battle TNT', 'Are you up for an intense challenge with your friends? You should compete against your friend. Its the perfect time for a race with your friend. The one who collects flying TNTs the fastest wins. There are two teams, red and blue. The team that collects the most TNTs wins. The first to collect 20 TNTs wins. You must collect them before your friend does. Catch the TNTs flying in the air.\n\nThe red player moves using the WASD keys. The blue player moves using the arrow keys. Collect the TnT and bring it to the chest.', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EDT19/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EDT19/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/friends-battle-tnt/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'friends-battle-tnt', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/EDT19\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/EDT19\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1858, '2025-04-19', 'Lemonade War', 'Would you like to pick lemons and win the race? Collect lemons to defeat your friend. You must help the blue and red players win the lemon race. Grab the lemons from the tree in the middle of the map and take them to the lemon stand. The person who collects the most lemons wins the race. Gather lemons and win the game. The water is slowly rising, and your only chance is to collect lemons as quickly as possible.\n\n*Press WASD keys to move the red player. \n*Press the Arrow keys to move the blue player. \n*Collect lemons from the tree and take them to the lemon stand to score points.', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E57EE/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/E57EE/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/lemonade-war/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'lemonade-war', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/E57EE\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/E57EE\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1859, '2025-04-19', '2Troll Cat', 'In the world of black and white, inhabited by two troll cats, survival is crucial. Gather all the paws and advance towards the portal. To rescue the troll cats, you must successfully complete each level. Collect the paws with your friend. Guide the cats to the portal. Complete the levels and finish all the stages.\n\n*Use the Arrow Keys to move the Black Cat.\n*Use the WASD to move the White Cat.\n*both mobile and desktop playability.', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2728T/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/2728T/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/2troll-cat/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, '2troll-cat', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/2728T\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/2728T\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1860, '2025-04-19', 'Steve and Alex vs Fnaf', 'Steve and Alex need to escape from the FNAF monsters in their adventure. They must evade the FNAF monsters everywhere, or eliminate them all. Collect all the gold and become the owner of the keys. The red player should collect the red key, and the blue player should collect the blue key.\n\n*Played with WASD + Arrow Keys.  \n*Mobile touch control is available.  \n*double jump available  \n*jump on it to kill!', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00120/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/00120/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/steve-and-alex-vs-fnaf/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'steve-and-alex-vs-fnaf', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/00120\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/00120\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1861, '2025-04-19', 'Noob vs Bacon Jumping', 'Hello! An exciting adventure awaits you where you need to escape sharp spikes rising from the ground. The spikes are coming from below, and you must constantly climb higher without stopping. Reach the highest point either alone or with your friend. Be careful of the spikes coming from below. Collect all the coins on the way and buy yourself different costumes.\n\nUse the WASD keys to move and jump in the game.\nUse the Arrow Keys keys to move and jump in the game.\n*Mobile Control Available ', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BA8IP/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/BA8IP/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/noob-vs-bacon-jumping/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'noob-vs-bacon-jumping', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/BA8IP\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/BA8IP\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1862, '2025-04-19', 'Fire and Water Ball', 'Are you willing to help Fire and Water, the adventurous siblings, in the temple? Help them to escape from the temple. Both siblings need to work together to get out of the temple. Collect keys and coins in the temple. To activate the portals, all keys and coins need to be collected. Both siblings need to reach the portal.\n\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys\n*Double Jump available\n*Mobile Touch Control', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ETAIN/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ETAIN/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/fire-and-water-ball/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'fire-and-water-ball', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/ETAIN\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/ETAIN\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1863, '2025-04-19', 'Carrom Play', 'A good old game of Carrom with a great deal of elegance and sophistication thrown in. Play a variety of challenges in Solo, against a Bot or against a real player and never get bored. Choose from a variety of traditional, contemporary or funky Boards, Strikers and Coins. Carrom Play is one of those games that one can get lost into for hours together.', '', 'Board', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4Y33L/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4Y33L/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/carrom-play/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'carrom-play', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/4Y33L\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/4Y33L\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1864, '2025-04-19', 'Island Of Treasures', 'Stuck as Pirate in a forsaken island full of treasures you run for your life while fighting the evil pirates collecting all the treasures on your way. Enjoy a thrilling 3D endless runner experience in Island of Treasures.', '', 'Adventure', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4DR88/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4DR88/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/island-of-treasures/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'island-of-treasures', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/4DR88\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/4DR88\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1865, '2025-04-19', 'Soccer Play', 'Casual Soccer at its best with easy to play pull back and strike controls. Get your strikers formation and aim for the goal post. Soccer Strike is the perfect blend of casual and competitive gameplay appealing to every soccer fan out there. This is our instant game take on the most popular sport in the world.', '', 'Sports', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4O4EP/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/4O4EP/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/soccer-play/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'soccer-play', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/4O4EP\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/4O4EP\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1866, '2025-04-19', 'Tetra Twist', 'Our take on a timeless classic, with a twist, known for its addictive gameplay, with its simple yet challenging gameplay and enduring appeal. Clear lines by fitting various geometric shapes.', '', 'Classics', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R0TTT/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R0TTT/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/tetra-twist/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'tetra-twist', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/R0TTT\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/R0TTT\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1867, '2025-04-19', 'Emoji with Friends', 'Express your way to victory! Dive into an engaging emoji puzzle game that challenges your wit and creativity, all while having a blast with friends.', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H78W7/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/H78W7/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/emoji-with-friends/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'emoji-with-friends', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/H78W7\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/H78W7\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1868, '2025-04-19', 'Solitaire Champions', 'Elevate your solitaire game to legendary status! Solitaire Champions offers a refined experience for those seeking the pinnacle of card mastery  play like a true champion.', '', 'Classics', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENR8A/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENR8A/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/solitaire-champions/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'solitaire-champions', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/ENR8A\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/ENR8A\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1869, '2025-04-19', 'Fruit Chop', 'Embark on a juicy slicing frenzy! Swipe and skillfully cut through a rainbow of fruits, but beware of the bombs  can you master the art of Fruit Chop without a mishap?', '', 'Strategy', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/47CU0/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/47CU0/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/fruit-chop/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'fruit-chop', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/47CU0\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/47CU0\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1870, '2025-04-19', 'Cake Smash', 'Unleash your sweet tooth in a delightful adventure! Join and smash a variety of delectable cakes to create the ultimate confectionery masterpiece.', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/02HME/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/02HME/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/cake-smash/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'cake-smash', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/02HME\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/02HME\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1871, '2025-04-19', 'Guard my Planet', 'Guard my Planet is a game set in the backdrop of interplanetary warfare. At this moment, your planet is facing the danger of invasion, and it needs your help to overcome every challenge posed by the invaders. It\'s time to showcase your leadership skills!', '', 'Strategy', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENPL6/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/ENPL6/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/guard-my-planet/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'guard-my-planet', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/ENPL6\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/ENPL6\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1872, '2025-04-19', 'Crizy Balls', 'Crazy Balls is a new and unique casual game. Try not to lose your temper\nSoar in the sky and survive the dash of balls that are different in color from you\nAvoid balls to survive your life and be a real manipulator\n\nThis game is very easy and needs one finger to play, just tap your phone screen and move your finger\n\nInstructions that will help you:\nWhen you touch a ball of the same color or type as the one you are using as a player, all enemy balls will be killed\n\nWhen you kill all the different balls, you will get money that will help you buy skins\n\nYou have to pick up valuable gems because you will use them to develop the player', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S483C/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/S483C/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/crizy-balls/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'crizy-balls', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/S483C\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/S483C\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1);
