(1925, '2025-04-19', ' CatnRobot Idle TD Battle Cat ', 'Have fun with this entertaining game CatRobot Idle TD Battle Cat is a tower defense game in a magical world which calls to defend your tower from the waves of magical enemies that will come with the intention of destroying you !!! Enjoy', '', 'Adventure', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DR97E/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/DR97E/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/catrobot-idle-td-battle-cat/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'catnrobot-idle-td-battle-cat', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/DR97E\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/DR97E\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1926, '2025-04-19', 'Watermelon Merge', 'What is Watermelon Merge?\nCombine two small fruits to make a new large fruit. Merge fruits is a game that is currently popular, because apart from being able to fill your time when you are relaxed or bored, it can also sharpen your brain with watermelon game.\n\nWatermelon merge cute: with various kinds of fruit such as cherry, strawberry, grapes, pineapple, apple, orange, melon and watermelon, it makes it like a fresh fruit salad. Apart from being very fun, Merge Fruit will certainly train your brain and train your competitive spirit to compete to get the highest score.\n\nHow to play this watermelon game puzzle?\nYou only need to direct the fruit to drop to the position you want, of course make sure the fruit will hit the same type of fruit so that it becomes a big fruit. In this fruit game, make sure not to stack them too high, because if they exceed the maximum limit on the glass tube then the game will end', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/01ERW/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/01ERW/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/watermelon-merge/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'watermelon-merge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/01ERW\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/01ERW\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1927, '2025-04-19', 'Jingle Juggle Merge', 'Dive into the festive world of \'Jingle Juggle Merge,\' where holiday magic meets spherical strategy! Immerse yourself in the challenge of merging Christmas orbs, creating harmonious patterns that dance to the jingle of holiday tunes. Navigate through snowy landscape, mastering the art of matching ornaments.\n\nCan you juggle the ornaments and create the ultimate Christmas spectacle? Embrace the holiday spirit and experience the enchanting fusion of fun and festivities in \'Jingle Juggle Merge\'!', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE01G/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/EE01G/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/jingle-juggle-merge/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'jingle-juggle-merge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/EE01G\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/EE01G\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1928, '2025-04-19', ' Elemental Rescue Adventure', 'Elemental Rescue Adventure is a captivating online platform game that will take you on an exciting adventure in the digital world and provide you with hours of fun and amusement. This game takes its cues from the popular film Elemental and puts players in the role of the heroic protagonist, Wade, as he attempts to free the beautiful Ember from her captors by completing a series of increasingly difficult stages. Elemental Rescue Adventure, a free game, combines ', '', 'Adventure', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/30E4L/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/30E4L/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/elemental-rescue-adventure/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'elemental-rescue-adventure', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/30E4L\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/30E4L\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1929, '2025-04-19', 'Golf Hill', 'Golf Hill is a golf sports simulation game, a very popular game for honing patience and accuracy. The game\'s simple and intuitive controls make it easy for kids to play, while the challenging obstacles and endless levels make it engaging for both kids and adults. A free sports game that offers addictive gameplay and hours of fun for players of all ages.', '', 'Sports', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1HG70/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/1HG70/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/golf-hill/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'golf-hill', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/1HG70\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/1HG70\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1930, '2025-04-19', 'Classic Master Sudoku', 'Classic Master Sudoku is a type of game or number puzzle that is quite popular. Many people, both young and old, play this game just to fill their free time or with the aim of sharpening their brain a little. Even though it is classified as an old school game, in fact up to now sudoku enthusiasts are still emerging and increasing.\n\nSudoku, originally called Number Place, is a logic-based combinatorial number placement puzzle. In classic sudoku, the goal is to fill a 99 grid with numbers so that each column, each row, and each of the nine 33 subgrids that make up the grid (also called squares, blocks, or regions) contains all the numbers from 1 to 9.\n\nIn sudoku there are usually several grids that are already partially filled, which can then be used as a guide to complete the filling. French newspapers featured variations of the Sudoku puzzle in the 19th century, and the puzzle has appeared ', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7452U/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/7452U/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/classic-master-sudoku/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'classic-master-sudoku', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/7452U\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/7452U\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(1931, '2025-04-19', 'Witch\'s Hats', 'Dont be manipulated by the witch, she will do anything to keep your book inaccessible, hiding it between her hats. You must be smart and agile enough not to lose sight of it. Can you really beat the witch?!', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/87C0S/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/87C0S/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/witch-s-hats/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'witch-s-hats', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/87C0S\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/87C0S\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
