(2058, '2025-04-19', 'Save The Cute Aliens', 'In \"Save The Cute Aliens,\" immerse yourself in an intergalactic adventure where your planet is threatened by a devastating meteor, and only you can save the alien population!\n\nThe inhabitants of your home planet, a variety of adorable and colorful aliens, are in imminent danger. The lethal meteor is rapidly approaching, but there is hope: a special spaceship appears on the left side of the screen, indicating the color of the aliens that can reverse time and delay the catastrophe for another minute.\n\nYour mission is to match three or more aliens of the same color to eliminate them from the playing field. But here\'s the crucial challenge: you need to focus on uniting three or more aliens of the exact color that corresponds to the spaceship on the left. When this happens, the countdown timer for the meteor\'s arrival is reset, granting more precious time to save more aliens.', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AI00S/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AI00S/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/save-the-cute-aliens/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'save-the-cute-aliens', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/AI00S\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/AI00S\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
