(2064, '2025-04-19', 'Santa And The Dungeon Of Doom ', 'Santa and The Dungeon Of Doom  is an epic adventure through 100 levels of monsters, traps and danger!!!\nHave you got the brains and fast reflexes to escape all 100 dungeons in this unique action puzzle game?\nBats will chase you, Ghosts will try and trick you, Monsters around every corner, Hazards include Spikes, Guillotines, Poison gas and more...\nHave you got what it takes?\nProduct feature bullets:\n- Xmas Game!\n- 100 epic levels!\n- Cute graphic!\n- Cool Xmas music!\n- Really addictive! \n- Easy to play!\nEnjoy with this great Christmas Puzzle Adventure game!', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/US6EO/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/US6EO/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/santa-and-the-dungeon-of-doom/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'santa-and-the-dungeon-of-doom', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/US6EO\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/US6EO\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
