(2296, '2025-04-19', 'Duo Water and Fire', 'Have you ever participated in the adventure of Stickman Fire and Water before? You need to collect the key and reach the door. As Fire and Water, you must overcome all obstacles. You are two opposite siblings, one with the power of fire and one with the power of water. Collect the red and blue keys. After collecting the keys, gather all the gold and reach the doors. Be careful, sometimes its like a puzzle. It can challenge your intellect.\n\n*Move to WASD + Arrow Keys\n*Double Jump available\n*Mobile Touch Control\n*The red player can pass through red water, and the blue player can pass through blue water. Neither player can pass through green water.', '', 'Adventure', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AW55D/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/AW55D/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/duo-water-and-fire/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'duo-water-and-fire', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/AW55D\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/AW55D\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(2297, '2025-04-19', 'Rainbow Squid Challenge', 'Help! The rainbow friends are invading our world with the Blue Monster leading the charge. They are working together with the Alphabet Monster to take it all. The only hope left is the controller in your hand to defend yourself.\n\nWalk through each level to defeat these rainbow friends or convert them to your cause. Simply press the power button or change their state using the program button.\n\nHOW TO PLAY:\n- Aim your controller at the monster.\n- The laser will turn green when being pointed.\n- Press a button and see how they work.\n- Defeat the monsters or neutralize them.\n- You win when there is no threat left.\n\nNEW FEATURES.\n- Familiar controller scheme.\n- Fun characters design.\n- Featuring the rainbow friends.\n- Exciting gameplay.\n- Cool dynamic.\n- Unlimited game time.', '', 'Arcade', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/961IN/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/961IN/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/rainbow-friends-survivors/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'rainbow-squid-challenge', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/961IN\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/961IN\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
(2298, '2025-04-19', 'Makeup Studio - Halloween', 'Halloween is coming, and you girls deserve a treat! We have created this spookylicious game for all of you so that you can have a professional makeup artist helping you to create unique, sassy, and witchy loos. In the Makeup Studio - Halloween game, we bring you the spookiest Halloween looks inspired by three famous influencers. Just check them out! You can find some trendiest Halloween aesthetics in our makeup game from jaw-dropping villain-inspired makeup looks to Monster High ghouls.', '', 'Junior', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N1NEW/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/N1NEW/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/makeup-studio-halloween/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'makeup-studio-halloween', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/N1NEW\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/N1NEW\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
