(2345, '2025-04-19', 'Fun Colors', 'Fun Colors - game that will help you or your child to realize their creative ideas!\nIn this free game you will find different categories of coloring pages and a drawing mode!\nIn addition to an endless palette of colors and a variety of brushes, Fun Colors has the ability to upload your own images and photos! And so that your eyes don\'t get tired of being in front of the screen for a long time, you can switch the interface to night mode!\nFinished your next masterpiece? - send it to print without leaving the game! (function only available on PC)\n\nFeatures of the game:\n- Upload your own coloring pages (NEW!)\n- Mode for drawing and coloring\n- Coloring pages of different categories\n- Upload your own photos to the game\n- Night theme\n- Save game progress\n- Save drawings to your device\n- Printing drawings from the game\n- Adjusting the size and type of brush\n- Zoom in / out of the canvas\n- Undo the last action', '', 'Junior,Board', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R89C8/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/R89C8/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/fun-colors/embed?sid=1', '480', '320', '', 0, 0, 0, 'fun-colors', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/R89C8\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/R89C8\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
