(2347, '2025-04-19', 'Heart Box', 'Professor Rat loves physics puzzles and games with robots! Therefore, he created Robby, but gave him a weak battery, which is why the little robot has to constantly recharge and participate in crazy experiments.\n\nFeatures of the game:\n\n- Over 180 levels for your brain!\n- Level Editor and Collection of QR Levels\n- Online database \"Community Levels\"\n- Various skins for the robot!\n- 4 fun game modes\n- Realistic physics\n- Lots of cartoons!\n- Leaderboard and achievements', '', 'Puzzle', 'gamepix', 'html5', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8TR8O/thumbnail/small.png', 'https://games.assets.gamepix.com/8TR8O/thumbnail/medium.png', '', 'https://play.gamepix.com/heart-box/embed?sid=1', '320', '480', '', 0, 0, 0, 'heart-box', '{\"thumbnail_source\":{\"thumb_1\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/8TR8O\\/thumbnail\\/small.png\",\"thumb_2\":\"https:\\/\\/games.assets.gamepix.com\\/8TR8O\\/thumbnail\\/medium.png\"}}', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1),
